susy.quest.db.0.title=创世记
susy.quest.db.0.desc=欢迎来到§9§9§9§b§b§b§b§b§b§l§l§l§l§l§lSupersymmetry§r§r§r§r§r§r! %n%n你刚刚降落在一个陌生星球上。这本书将教你如何在短短§k4200§r页内从零开始重建整个文明。%n%n如果你弄丢了这本书，没关系，按下§2§aGRAVE (`) §r键依旧可以查看本书。%n%n某些图标带框的任务（就比如说这个）是生存主线相关内容。%n%n并且现在你还无法跳过夜晚，因为床在EV才解锁（也不会自然生成的）。
susy.quest.db.1.title=是J不是N，但是也差不多。
susy.quest.db.1.desc=如果没有这玩意还是别想着玩格雷科技了，这有一些如何正确使用的小贴士：%n%n本包有非常多非常复杂的处理线，所以必须对JEI很熟。如果你遇到了不认识的东西，在任务界面对着物品按§6R§r，就能看见它的合成配方，或者按§6U§r就能查看使用处（需要该物品的合成配方）。%n%n养成§e添加到JEI书签§r(默认按§aA§r添加)就不需要反复查找物品。%n%n大多数物品在这个包里都有§e多重配方§r！不要望而却步。%n有些材料只能通过§e小搓粉§r合成，有些就必须要处理§e溶液§r了，这些活用则需要一点练习了。本包的石化和核化学的这一方面做的很糟糕。%n%n你可以通过§e前缀@§r来查询一个模组内的物品。例如，如果搜索§c@gregtech§r，就只会看到GT的东西。%n%n而§e前缀$§r则可以查询矿物词典里的东西。例如，§c$logWood§r就是原木。%n%n（来自中文译者的提示：如果你需要物品中文名的拼音查询，请安装Just Enough Characters和Had Enough Characters模组，另外I18）
susy.quest.db.2.title=静谧四季
susy.quest.db.2.desc=现在某些作物只能在特定季节种植了（但你可以改用§a温室§r或者自动化农业）， 而且周围的环境也会随着四季变迁而变化。%n%n§a春天§r在三月一日开始并且在五月三十结束。%n§6夏天§r在六月一日开始并且在八月三十结束。%n§c秋天§r在九月一日开始并且在十一月三十结束。%n§b冬天§r在十二月一日开始并且在二月三十结束。
susy.quest.db.3.title=捡起石块
susy.quest.db.3.desc=§7石块§r可以制作该阶段的工具，%n%n你可以通过§6右键§r地面上的矿脉标识来获取。除了可以获取石块之外，§7地面标识§r也可以§6作为矿脉定位§r。
susy.quest.db.4.title=维基百科
susy.quest.db.4.desc=阿卡什宝典可以自由变换成各种指导书，只需点击一下任务里的复选框即送。
susy.quest.db.5.title=石灰岩
susy.quest.db.5.desc=§7石灰岩§r是一种沉积岩，并且是§8石灰§r的主要来源，是初期一个很重要的材料。%n%n
susy.quest.db.6.title=植物纤维
susy.quest.db.6.desc=可以通过用手打§2草§r获得§a植物纤维§r。%n同时，还会爆一些§4干燥的植物纤维§r，可用于合成§4麻线§r。你过一会就会需要很多§a植物纤维§r的。
susy.quest.db.7.title=木头怎么搞
susy.quest.db.7.desc=好吧，我的意思是你需要一把GT斧，只需要破坏最底下的一个方块就会展开连锁。%n%n
susy.quest.db.8.title=原始武器
susy.quest.db.8.desc=§4耐用麻线§r可以用麻线在浸泡壶里浸泡木焦油获得。这可以合成§6弓§r。%n%n如果你碰巧遇上几头鸡，你可以使用他们的羽毛（如果你拿到纸了，也可以）来合成一点铁箭。甚至§6带火§r！%n%n很（不）幸运的是，这玩意都不符合物理了，还是非常容易损坏。
susy.quest.db.9.title=燧石工具
susy.quest.db.9.desc=使用§6工作台§r就能做§7燧石工具§r。%n%n和石对比，燧石很脆弱；不过，它很锐利，适合做成§6剑§r和其他工具，但是不适合做§7锤§r。%n%n用燧石做的小刀和剑有§c火焰附加§r。
susy.quest.db.10.title=磁铁矿
susy.quest.db.10.desc=地下有很多好资源，记得多找找。%n%n其中之一就是§l§a磁铁矿§r，稍后用于制造磁铁。%n%n磁铁矿可以在地下矿脉矿藏里找到，矿脉大小基本是20 * 20格。%n%n如果你在地面上看见§a小搓磁铁矿粉§r，在那下面就会生成磁铁矿脉。%n%n%n在各个方向上，每前进大约50格就能发现矿藏。如果你位于矿脉上方，会看到地面上有标记，并且屏幕左上角会出现一个提示。
susy.quest.db.11.title=皮革外套
susy.quest.db.11.desc=§6皮革§r需要煮沸来制作§6处理皮革§r，然后与线绑在一起来制作§b捆版皮革§r。%n%n你可以在工作台中用§9捆绑皮革§r制作盔甲。
susy.quest.db.12.title=石制工具
susy.quest.db.12.desc=现在终于可以合成第一套§7工具§r了！优先做一个斧和镐，但大概也需要一个锤和小刀。小刀既可以快速割草，也能充当武器。%n%n注：要查找石制工具的配方，请先查看其铁制工具的配方（或者直接对右边的物品按§6R§r）并且拉到§6最后§r一页。
susy.quest.db.13.title=铜
susy.quest.db.13.desc=铜几乎遍布地壳的各个角落，甚至在更深的岩层中也能找到。没准还能找到点含有铜元素的§6天然铜矿床§r。%n%n你也可以找找§e黄铜矿§r，§8辉铜矿§r，§2孔雀石§r，§6斑铜矿§r和 §4黝铜矿§r矿脉。但无论如何，简易冶炼炉只能提炼出其中的一种金属，意味着§c§l只有§r辉铜矿和孔雀石可以被熔炼。%n%n寻找地面上的§6小搓铜粉§r就可以发现其下的矿脉。如果无法找到某个矿藏，请在JEI中查询，你将看到一个显示该矿脉所在位置的页面。%n%n先搞到30个锭来。%n%n§c§l作为一条非常重要的经验法则，任务顺序是任意的，你可以参考此处的建议，但相信我说的你需要很多铜。
susy.quest.db.14.title=锡
susy.quest.db.14.desc=可以在§6锡石矿砂§r和§6锡石矿§f矿脉，在JEI里查看获取方式。%n%n锡是一种银色金属，质地柔软，只需轻微用力即可切割，一块锡条也只需稍加用力就能弯曲 %n§6%n§l§r矿藏面积为 20x20，每个矿藏最大能产出 5000 个锭。%n%n§0§9§e§d§c§b§l§c§c§l作为一条非常重要的经验法则，任务顺序是任意的，你可以参考此处的建议，但相信我，你需要的锡会很多，还有铜。
susy.quest.db.15.title=研磨机 V0.1 Alpha
susy.quest.db.15.desc=§a研钵§r可以把锭变成§b粉§r或是把沙砾变成§8燧石§r。配合锤使用————锤可以将圆石变成沙砾——这样你就能轻松获得燧石了。%n%n
susy.quest.db.16.title=合金101
susy.quest.db.16.desc=§6青铜§r是75%%铜混入25%%锡的合金。%n%n将锭或粉以三比一的比例放入§7简易冶炼炉§r来制作§6青铜锭§r。%n%n§3完成它来解锁第一章！
susy.quest.db.17.title=未知之物，伏于影中
susy.quest.db.17.desc=在存在生命的大部分行星上，夜晚都是漆黑一片且极其危险，请尽快寻找庇护所。%n%n如果外出，小心周围的敌对生物吧。目前这个阶段还远做不到杀死他们，所以§c你必须藏起来！§r
susy.quest.db.18.title=研磨机 V0.2 Beta
susy.quest.db.18.desc=使用简易石磨可以从矿石中提取更多的金属，但没有那么好用... 不过这只是个开始。它也需要§c手动§r，所以你必须动动手来让它运行。%n%n将一个§6木质曲柄§r放在简易石磨的顶端并且§a右键§r就能使其旋转，转个几圈就能把东西磨好。%n%n两个矿石就能磨出三个粉碎矿石。%n%n粉碎矿石也能烧成锭，或者处理成§b含杂粉§f或§b离心矿石§f来提取出更多价值。
susy.quest.db.19.title=做些木棍
susy.quest.db.19.desc=打§2树叶§r就会掉落木棍。如果在沙漠可以打§4枯死的灌木§r.
susy.quest.db.20.title=焦炉
susy.quest.db.20.desc=§7焦炉§r是一个3x3x3的多方块结构，使用焦炉砖块搭建，并需要将控制器置于中心。%n它可以把§7煤炭§r变为§7焦煤§r，或把原木变成木炭。%n%n焦煤能提供更长的燃烧时间。%n%n焦炉也会产出杂酚油，可以用作液体燃料也可以做§6防腐木§r。
susy.quest.db.21.title=格雷化
susy.quest.db.21.desc=要迈向工业时代，还需要更强力的工具，而工具主要分为六大类。%n%n§6§l做其他材料的工具看起来还不大现实，因此优先推荐青铜工具。§r %n%n§2锤§r无处不在，它用于制作所有其他类型的工具，并可以把锭锻造成板%n§2锉§r可以把锭锉成杆%n§2锯§r可以把木板锯成台阶和把原木变成六个木板。%n§2螺丝刀§r用于大部分配方和设置覆盖板。它还用于制造齿轮和转子等重要部件。%n§2扳手§r可以用于配置管道，也是一种非常重要的工具。%n§2剪线钳§r可以剪线。%n%n§l§c§l无论是在JEI还是在书中，只要涉及工具的使用，都会显示铁制工具。非铁制工具在JEI的搜索结果中不会显示，但青铜工具应优先制作。通常情况下，配方接受任意材料的工具。§r
susy.quest.db.22.title=土高炉
susy.quest.db.22.desc=普通熔炉不能很好地冶炼物品，其最高温度只有1,000 K（730°C），对于烧铁来说温度不够。%n%n土高炉由32个§c耐火砖块§r和1个§4土高炉（控制器）§r搭建而成。这是一个§a3×4×3的结构§r§r，由耐火砖块中空搭建而成。如需更多帮助，请查看JEI中的§c结构预览§r。%n%n土高炉可以制造铁、熟铁和§b钢§r。其最高温度约为1,500 K（1,227°C）。%n%n与大多数的其他结构一样，多个结构间的重复方块可以共用。
susy.quest.db.23.title=锌
susy.quest.db.23.desc=§7锌§r在室温下是一种较脆的金属，外观呈光亮的灰白色。%n%n§7闪锌矿§r矿脉内含§7闪锌矿石§r，锌的一个重要来源。尽管它主要存在于地下较深的位置，例如§8深渊世界§r和§c下界§r，也可以在一些其他矿脉中以副矿的形式出现，例如§5方铅矿§r和§6黄铁矿§r矿脉。检查JEI以获得更多信息。%n%n烧一点来做§e黄铜§r。%n%n锌也用来制作磁铁，如果你找不到，§a磁铁矿§r也可以。
susy.quest.db.24.title=伏打电堆
susy.quest.db.24.desc=要制造磁铁，必须要有一个§b伏打电堆§r。§c%n§r%n伏打电堆由三个部分组成：1个§6铜板§r、1个§7锌板§r和电解质纸。%n%n常见的电解质是§6柠檬酸§r。将柠檬、酸橙或橙子与纸放在一起就能做出电解质纸。酸橙可以在丛林中找到，柠檬可以在丛林边缘和森林中找到，而橙子可以在草原生物群系中找到。%n%n如果你无法制作伏打电堆，可以使用另一种方法来磁化铁杆————§6磁铁矿§r。
susy.quest.db.25.title=重金属
susy.quest.db.25.desc=§7铁§r是地球上最常见的元素之一，它可被精炼成§6钢§r[参见下一个任务]，多用于合成基本工具，无疑是工业时代最重要的材料。%n%n你从上一个任务中获得的§6生铁§r可以使用普通锤或锻造锤锤击成§7熟铁§r，也可以考虑制作§7反射炉§r来走最快的路线。它也可以在§7炉§r中冶炼成§7铸铁§r（普通的铁）。%n%n此外，任务检索编号在这里也是任意的，相信我，你会想要冶炼§o一大堆的§r§7铁§r的。
susy.quest.db.26.title=伏打的复仇
susy.quest.db.26.desc=首先，你需要§c钢板§r————将两个钢锭用锤子做成板，然后放入熔炉中。%n%n制造磁铁有两种方式：%n%n1、将热钢板和一个§c磁铁矿块§r放在工作台里。%n2、使用§c伏打电池§r加上一些§c铜细线§r（不过你需要特殊设备）。%n%n这个过程只做一次§r。§c磁化钢板§r可以用来磁化其他热钢板，所以别扔掉它！%n%n§3这将解锁工业时代。
susy.quest.db.27.title=磁铁矿块
susy.quest.db.27.desc=§7磁铁矿§r矿石可以通过使用工作台破碎成§7磁铁矿块§r，可以用来磁化§6铁杆§r。
susy.quest.db.28.title=格雷工具
susy.quest.db.28.desc=获得§6青铜§r之后你不只能制作些耐久更好的工具，还可以做点高级版。%n%n采矿锤可以挖掘3x3空间（按住§a潜行§r取消）。%n%n铲也一样，但它适用于可用锹破坏的方块，例如泥土和沙子。%n%n§l§c§l无论是在JEI还是在书中，只要涉及工具的使用，都会显示铁制工具。非铁制工具在JEI的搜索结果中不会显示，但青铜工具应优先制作。通常情况下，配方接受任意材料的工具。§r
susy.quest.db.29.title=增强的原始武器
susy.quest.db.29.desc=用你的新合金制作一把§6青铜剑§r。
susy.quest.db.30.title=工业时代的大门
susy.quest.db.30.desc=§6钢§r是铁和碳的合金，与其他形式的铁相比，提高了§6强度§r并且抗断裂性更好。%n%n§c土高炉§f§r可以通过用焦炭冶炼，将§7熟铁§f锭变成§l§e§6钢§r。%n%n制造钢是工业时代的首要任务之一，请确保你的土高炉不会关机，并尝试制作4个共享墙体的土高炉。
susy.quest.db.31.title=§6第一章 // 发起革命
susy.quest.db.31.desc=工业时代的目标是获得蒸汽机器、制造真空管并获得电力。%n%n以下信息对你的生存至关重要，请仔细阅读！%n%n%n§l§n如何获得蒸汽？§r%n%n有不同的方式来生产蒸汽；§c§c固体燃料锅炉§r、§c液体燃料锅炉§r、§c太阳能锅炉§r和§c大型锅炉§r。现在一个不错的选择是固体燃料锅炉，因为它燃烧效率高。锅炉需要一些时间来加热，一旦足够热，它就会§c§r消耗水§r和§c燃料§r，自动输出蒸汽§r到连接的管道中。请记住，锅炉可能会§4§l§n爆炸§r！当锅炉过热时没有水，这时你加一些水，将会引起爆炸。%n%n§l§n蒸汽机器如何工作？§r%n%n§n§l§r蒸汽机器是§6缓慢的§r、§6需要蒸汽管道连接§r并且无法§6自动输出§r。%n还有一个§6排气口§r，一个默认在机器背面的灰色正方形。%n排气口可以用扳手调整位置，但§6必须保持畅通（朝向的第一个方块必须是空气）§r。%n配方完成时，排气口将向空气中射出蒸汽粒子效果，如果你站在排气口附近，你将会被§c§l煮沸§r%n%n§l§n还是不懂？%n§r如果你需要一些帮助，观看这段视频（YouTube）：{Embed}TypeLink；https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CR3KGYtaEtM；256；20；§9§n格雷科技如何通过蒸汽时代§r{Embed}%n------------------------------------%n§3第一章 // 发起革命%n§r------------------------------------%n§r——工业化%n——使用蒸汽的力量%n——开始生产电力%n——创建最基础的电子产品%n%n等级：1%nEU/t：0%n------------------------------------%n
susy.quest.db.32.title=合金冶炼201
susy.quest.db.32.desc=§l§r蒸汽合金炉§r直接将粉或锭烧成§c§l新合金§r。%n%n§r此机器需要相当多的蒸汽才能工作，如果蒸汽用完，可以用§a软锤§r关闭机器。%n%n§6合金炉§r可以直接制造青铜，使用§d锭§o§o§r、粉，甚至粒。§r你也可以制作一个模具（粒），将锭变成粒。%n%n注意：与所有蒸汽机器一样，输出端口在配方完成时兼作蒸汽出口。§c它不能被阻挡§r。另外，蒸汽很热，接触时可能伤害你。用扳手敲击合金熔炉来改变输出侧面。
susy.quest.db.33.title=矿石增倍
susy.quest.db.33.desc=§6蒸汽研磨机§r可用于将矿石转化为粉碎矿，这是一种最简单的矿石处理。%n%n放入蒸汽研磨机的每个矿石变成2个粉碎矿，可以在炉或土高炉中冶炼成两个锭。%n
susy.quest.db.34.title=合金炉模具
susy.quest.db.34.desc=§6模具§o§r可以在合金炉和流体固化器中使用，你需要它们来制造真空管。%n使用合金炉，它们可以将粉变成锭，或将锭变成齿轮。§r%n
susy.quest.db.35.title=蒸汽胶乳收集器
susy.quest.db.35.desc=制作§6橡胶§r是成为技术人员的重要一步。在这之后，你需要橡胶来制作电路。%n橡胶是用§5§6胶乳§r制成的。胶乳是一种液体，通过在橡胶原木旁放置§6蒸汽胶乳收集器§r来收集。%n%n确保橡胶原木放置在收集器的§6白色§r一侧。
susy.quest.db.36.title=LV传送带模块
susy.quest.db.36.desc=The §7LV Conveyor Module §ris the fourth machine component you will need. %n%nIt can be also used as a cover to move items around. %n%nThe Conveyor Module, when placed on a machine, will transfer items to the block adjacent to the face it’s on. You can configure it to import or export items from the machine or item pipe you place it on.%n%nVoltages are irrelevant when placing covers on machines, so, for example, you can safely put an LV conveyor module on HV machines and vice versa.%n
susy.quest.db.37.title=镍
susy.quest.db.37.desc=§d§r镍§r是一种银白色光泽的金属，略带金色色调。它是一种硬的、有延展性的过渡金属。%n%n§e§d镍§r可以在§6硅镁镍矿§r、§6镍黄铁矿§r、§6§r和§6镍矿§r中找到，它们位于地壳第二层，被村民称为"深渊"。%n%n在地壳中开采更深处需要特殊设备，检查探索章节以获取更多信息。%n§r%n生产电力§r需要镍。
susy.quest.db.38.title=蒸汽焙烧炉
susy.quest.db.38.desc=§6蒸汽焙烧炉§r用蒸汽燃烧化学物质，是一种反应炉，这台机器将用于生产§6硫§r。焙烧炉将在LV及以后的许多化学过程中使用。
susy.quest.db.39.title=难以置信的力量
susy.quest.db.39.desc=§a蒸汽压缩机§r压缩物体。它可以将锭变成块，以及将粒变成锭。%n
susy.quest.db.40.title=蒸汽锻造锤
susy.quest.db.40.desc=§l§r§6蒸汽锻造锤§r是一种非常有用的机器，几乎可以做任何需要锤子的事情。%n%n它可以以更好的比例制造§6板§r§l§r，每个板只需1.5个锭而不是2个。这可以让你节省大量锭，直到你获得§6卷板机§r，它处理每个板只需1个锭。
susy.quest.db.41.title=硫化机
susy.quest.db.41.desc=§6硫化机§r将胶乳变成橡胶片，需要§6硫§r。反应可能需要很长时间，但可以通过使用§6菱镁矿或红锌矿§r作为催化剂来加快处理速度。
susy.quest.db.42.title=镍
susy.quest.db.42.desc=§b镍§r是一种早期游戏金属，只能在蒸汽时代的土高炉中制造。%n%n你可以从海拔0到80或在下界找到§a硅镁镍矿§r和§6镍黄铁矿§r，如果你在地表找到这些岩石，意味着下方会有矿床。
susy.quest.db.43.title=玻璃管
susy.quest.db.43.desc=工业时代的主要目标是§e真空管§r，而我们的第一步是制造§a玻璃管§r，用模具（球）和玻璃粉在合金炉里制作。
susy.quest.db.44.title=黄铁矿和硫
susy.quest.db.44.desc=§6黄铁矿§f可以通过在§6方铅矿§f或§6闪锌矿§f矿脉中开采来获得。这些矿脉可以在地壳的前两层中找到。如果你足够幸运，你甚至可能找到纯黄铁矿矿脉！%n%n黄铁矿粉可以焙烧以获得带状铁矿粉和§6硫§f，这将用于处理橡胶。%n%n或者，你可以去地壳第三层找§6硫矿§f，也称为§6硫矿床。§f%n%n要完成这个任务，你可以完成任意检索任务。
susy.quest.db.45.title=蒸汽搅拌机
susy.quest.db.45.desc=§7§6蒸汽搅拌机§r混合多种粉或液体。它将需要用于制造湿空气以处理绿矾和混合三氧化硫和水来创建H2SO4。%n%n如果某些搅拌机配方需要§6编程电路§r，你可以§a左键§r搅拌机底部右角的"G"来改变配置。
susy.quest.db.46.title=硫酸
susy.quest.db.46.desc=要获得硫酸，首先用湿空气氧化一些黄铁矿。绿矾可以在焙烧炉中分解以获得三氧化硫。三氧化硫和水可以混合在一起来制备§6硫酸§r。你可以使用§6蒸汽搅拌机§f来运行该配方。%n%nSO₃ + H₂O -> H₂SO₄%n%n由于§6硫酸§r是一种酸，它将需要§6特殊容器§r来存储它。§c§l青铜/钢桶无法存储酸，§r你必须使用§c§l铅或金桶§r来运输硫酸，因为这两种材料是耐酸的。%n%n有关耐酸桶的完整列表，请查看存储页面。
susy.quest.db.47.title=LV卷板机
susy.quest.db.47.desc=§7LV卷板机§r是一种更好的制造板和箔的机器，它可以把§61个锭变成1个板§r，不像蒸汽锻造锤那样把3个锭变成2个板。
susy.quest.db.48.title=橡胶片
susy.quest.db.48.desc=使用硫化机来制造§6橡胶片§r。
susy.quest.db.49.title=凝固缸
susy.quest.db.49.desc=§6凝固缸§r可以将液体凝固成固体。%n%n凝固缸最少需要：%n§6- 1个凝固缸（控制器）%n- 24个凝固缸壁面§r%n%n可以将液态胶乳凝聚成固体。%n%n要使过程更快，你可以使用一些§6催化剂§r来提升处理速度，或扩展其结构以进行并行处理。%n%n你可以通过向结构添加输入仓和输出总线来§c自动化这个机器§r。
susy.quest.db.50.title=绝缘线缆
susy.quest.db.50.desc=§6导线§r可以用§6橡胶§r绝缘成线缆，线缆没有§6很多能量损耗§r，不像电线，你接触时不会受伤。%n这些将在制造电路时用得到。
susy.quest.db.51.title=LV电动马达
susy.quest.db.51.desc=§6LV电动马达§r是电力机器中最重要的组件之一，也用于制造§6活塞§r。%n%n虽然你在工业时代只需要几个，但一旦进入电力时代，你就会需要数百个活塞。你可以一次批量制作16个或更多活塞，以减轻痛苦。
susy.quest.db.52.title=LV电力活塞
susy.quest.db.52.desc=§6LV电力活塞§r是电力机器的另一个重要组件，但制造蒸汽研磨机和锻造锤需要它。
susy.quest.db.53.title=阴阳极
susy.quest.db.53.desc=§5铅阳极§r基本上是一个§5铅板§r加上一些接线。%n%n要获得§5铅阴极§r，你需要将§5铅阴极浆§r涂于§5铅阴极框架§r。%n%n§5铅阴极浆§r是§2二氧化铅§r和§6稀硫酸§r的混合物，后者是通过在搅拌机中用§9水§r稀释§6硫酸§r制成的。
susy.quest.db.54.title=真空管
susy.quest.db.54.desc=一个§6真空管§o§r是一种控制高真空中电极之间电流流动的设备，它是§6原始电路§r的组件之一。§r%n%n将所有物品组合在一起来制造真空管。
susy.quest.db.55.title=矿石处理
susy.quest.db.55.desc=粉碎仍然是一个矿石加倍工序，就像在其他模组中一样，但有一个转折，它不直接给粉！粉碎矿石用于更高级的矿石处理，一个粉碎矿石将转化为一个粉。%n%n要获得含杂粉§r，锤粉碎矿石即可。%n%n这可以通过在工作台中使用锤工具来完成，也可以使用蒸汽锻造锤。%n%n含杂粉可以在熔炉中冶炼成锭。%n%n含杂粉也可以扔进装满水的原版炼药中来清洗，变成普通的粉，整堆扔进来会消耗更少的水。%n%n§l注意：粉碎、锤击，然后冶炼（有时变成粒）在蒸汽时代真的非常费时！资源使用率现在可以忽略。没有人会因为直接冶炼矿石成锭而责备你。
susy.quest.db.56.title=更好的蒸汽机器
susy.quest.db.56.desc=§2高压§r蒸汽机器需要钢，它们比普通蒸汽机器快两倍，高压§r§e锅炉§r也以两倍的速度生成蒸汽。与他们的名字相反，他们不需要真的高压。
susy.quest.db.57.title=液体燃料锅炉
susy.quest.db.57.desc=某些流体也可以用于制造蒸汽。搜索JEI中的液体燃料锅炉，并检查半流质燃料页面以获取更多详细信息。
susy.quest.db.58.title=太阳的力量
susy.quest.db.58.desc=§6太阳能锅炉§r可以用太阳能来获得蒸汽，%n他们只在太阳升起时生成蒸汽，每天13小时。
susy.quest.db.59.title=桶
susy.quest.db.59.desc=§6青铜§r桶没有太多容量，但也可以存储32,000L的流体。%n%n§8钢§f桶可以存更多，64,000L。§9§b§3§3§1§9§b§3铝§f桶则可以存储128,000L并且 §e§3§f§0§b§c§d§b§3§b不锈钢§f桶可以存储256,000L。
susy.quest.db.60.title=LV线材轧机
susy.quest.db.60.desc=§7LV线材轧机§r是一种自动处理§61个锭§r变成§62根导线§r的机器。它也可以将一根导线处理成§64条细导线§r。它比手动制造§c高效得多§r。
susy.quest.db.61.title=手枪炮
susy.quest.db.61.desc=在工业时代，你可以制造更好的武器。§a手枪炮§r是其中之一。它使用石头子弹作为弹药。
susy.quest.db.62.title=双管霰弹枪
susy.quest.db.62.desc=§a双管霰弹枪§r是你能制造的第一把枪。它使用霰弹作为弹药。%n%n这是一把霰弹枪，这意味着它会一次射出8发抛体。有关更多信息，请查看工具提示。
susy.quest.db.63.title=左轮手枪
susy.quest.db.63.desc=§a左轮手枪§r使用手枪子弹作为弹药。
susy.quest.db.64.title=电阻
susy.quest.db.64.desc=§6电阻§r是一种电子元件，用于限制电子电路中的电流流动。%n%n电阻是§bLV电路§r的另一个主要组件，它由粘性树脂制成，可以在§2橡胶树§r中提取。使用§6胶乳收集器§r来提取液体胶乳。
susy.quest.db.65.title=覆膜电路基板
susy.quest.db.65.desc=§6覆膜电路基板§r是LV电路的另一个组件，由粘性树脂和木板制成。电路基板在电子工程中用于将电子元件连接在一起。%n%n你必须用导线缠绕覆膜电路基板才能使其可用，并将其转变为§6电路基板§r。
susy.quest.db.66.title=这只是开始……
susy.quest.db.66.desc=组装电路部件（§6电阻§r、§b真空管§r、§c线缆§r和§2电路基板§r）可以制造一个原始电路。%n%n电路是所有电力机器的大脑——机器工作需要它们。有10多种不同类型的电路——从原始电路到极其强大的生物处理器。%n%n
susy.quest.db.67.title=地球
susy.quest.db.67.desc=-- §a重要信息§r --%n- 表面重力：1g%n- 白天长度：24小时%n- 大气：可呼吸（1气压）%n    1. 78.084%%氮气%n    2. 20.946%%氧气%n    3. 0.9340%%氩气%n    4. 0.0417%%二氧化碳%n    5. 0.001818%%氖气%n    6. 0.000524%%氦气%n    7. 0.000187%%甲烷%n    8. 0.000114%%氪气%n- 公转周期：365天%n- 卫星：%n    1. 月球%n%n-------------------------%n%n§a地球§r是一颗围绕一颗被称为§6太阳§r（也称为§6太阳§r）的恒星公转的类地行星。它的岩石表面分为各种被称为大陆的地形。它包括广阔的海洋、高耸的山脉、郁郁葱葱的森林、干旱的沙漠和极地冰帽。海洋覆盖了地球表面的约70%%，其余30%%由陆地组成。%n%n地球上的山脉可以达到令人难以置信的高度。地球上的森林很丰富，为许多不同种类的植物和动物提供了栖息地。这些森林是地球生态系统的重要组成部分，在调节地球气候方面起着重要作用。%n%n§c从地球表面向下挖掘，可以遇到三种类型的岩石：沉积岩、火成岩和变质岩。沉积岩（如石灰岩）可以在海拔40以下的地方找到，而火成岩（如辉长岩或花岗岩）可以在0到40之间找到。%n%n地球下面有一个被称为深处的洞穴系统。这个洞穴系统是一个复杂的地下隧道、房间和通道网络，跨越很大的距离。你可以通过向下挖掘到Y级别0并在下方冒险来到达它。%n%n
susy.quest.db.68.title=深渊
susy.quest.db.68.desc=-- §a重要信息§r --%n%n行星：§a地球§r%nID：§a10§r%n深渊：§c64m§r%n%n-------------------------%n%n§4从海平面向下挖掘64米以进入第二层。在穿越深处时请注意周围环境，因为它非常危险。%n%n§r深处是指地球地壳的深层、地下层。这些层由变质岩组成。%n%n深处发现的岩石是由地球地壳深处存在的巨大压力和热量形成的。在深处，你可以找到数百万年来隐藏的矿石。例如：§6无烟煤§r，一种稀有的煤炭。%n%n探索深处需要专门的设备和专业知识。深处还可以找到几个§b§k哭泣天使§r。它们是极其危险的实体，所以探索时要非常小心。%n%n
susy.quest.db.69.title=下界
susy.quest.db.69.desc=-- §a重要信息§r --%n%n行星：§a地球§r%nID：§a-1§r%n深度：§c320m§r%n%n-------------------------%n%n§4向下挖掘至深处底部以进入此维度。§r%n%n§3§4§l警告：水桶在高温下不起作用。可以使用储罐在此处运输液体。
susy.quest.db.70.title=月球
susy.quest.db.70.desc=-- §a重要信息§r --%n%n- 表面重力：0.166g%n%n- 白天长度：30个地球日%n%n- 大气：无%n%n- 公转周期：30个地球日%n%n- 绕星球：地球%n%n- 卫星：无%n%n-------------------------%n%n§3警告：由于技术限制，你在月球上时内部时钟将无法工作。
susy.quest.db.71.title=铅酸电池
susy.quest.db.71.desc=§6铅酸电池§r是有史以来第一种可充电电池。与更强大的电池相比，铅酸电池的能量密度相对较低。但这是一个开始。%n%n将§5阴极§r和§5阳极§r与§6稀硫酸§r结合在§7原始LV电池外壳§r中可以制造一个电池。%n%n你可以使用§cLV组装机§r来获得更好的铅酸电池配方。
susy.quest.db.72.title=灰锑矿和锑
susy.quest.db.72.desc=§6锑§r是一种类金属。在其金属形式下，它呈银色、坚硬且脆弱。%n%n锑存在于§6灰锑矿§r中，位于灰锑矿矿脉中。灰锑矿也可以在§6辰砂§r矿脉中小量找到§r。
susy.quest.db.73.title=原始电池外壳
susy.quest.db.73.desc=使用§7硫化橡胶板§r和一些电线组装§6中型原始电池外壳§r。
susy.quest.db.74.title=石灰
susy.quest.db.74.desc=§6生石灰§r，也叫氧化钙，可通过在§7石窑§r内烧制石灰岩粉获得。%n%n基于目前的科技水平，§6生石灰§r可以用§6浸泡壶§r或§6粘土桶§r合成§6熟石灰§r。它可以用于合成§6耐火砖§r。
susy.quest.db.75.title=蒸汽活塞
susy.quest.db.75.desc=§6活塞§r是构建大多数蒸汽机器所需的，所以获得一些是很重要的。
susy.quest.db.76.title=§c第一天
susy.quest.db.76.desc=§c以下是前几天你应该做的§o优先事项§r§c：§r%n%n§r- 获取一些§a纤维§r和§7石块§r，石质工具很重要%n- 获取§6粘性树脂§r，用于早期合成火把%n- 先做斧，再做其他工具%n- 搞一大堆木头%n- 找一个§8煤矿矿藏§r，这样就不缺燃料了%n- 找§6铜§r和§7锡§r矿脉%n- 石灰岩必不可少%n- 打草获得§a不明GTFO种子§r就能合成所有类型的作物种子%n- 在室内搞一个农场来种你获得的种子%n%n降落时也有一些§4应急口粮§r，一些日子是足够的。%n
susy.quest.db.77.title=真空管组件
susy.quest.db.77.desc=结合一堆§6导线§r和一个§6钢环§r就能制造§6真空管§r组件。这些将被放入玻璃管中，并使用§6真空室§r在极低压力下密封。现在，只需制造组件。
susy.quest.db.78.title=真空室
susy.quest.db.78.desc=§6真空室§r是一个刚性密闭装置，空气和其他气体通过真空泵被抽出。%n%n这会导致极低的压力，例如，真空管需要低于130§6§l微§l§r§6帕斯卡§r才能工作。%n%n制造真空管需要此类环境。
susy.quest.db.79.title=导线101
susy.quest.db.79.desc=§6导线§r可以使用§6剪线钳§r从金属板上剪出。%n%n如果你必须制造§6细导线§r，你必须先将一块金属板变成§6箔§r，然后使用剪线钳。
susy.quest.db.80.title=液体单元
susy.quest.db.80.desc=§6钢§r单元最多可以盛装8升液体或气体§r，它们是分等级的，所以你可以用从钢到钨钢的每个等级的外壳材料制造单元。
susy.quest.db.81.title=你知道怎么做
susy.quest.db.81.desc=制造4个最重要的§6MV部件§r：一个MV电力活塞、一个MV机械臂、一个MV电动泵和一个MV传送带。
susy.quest.db.82.title=更强、更好、更快、更有力
susy.quest.db.82.desc=制造一个§6MV电动马达§r。
susy.quest.db.83.title=原始食物
susy.quest.db.83.desc=你知道什么比普通食物更好吗？切成片的食物。切片番茄和葡萄提供的饱和度比普通的要高一些。
susy.quest.db.84.title=不明种子
susy.quest.db.84.desc=可以通过打草获取§6不明种子§r，使用§6工作台§r可以合成成各种种子。%n%n试试在基地旁边做一个室内§a农场§r - 但是得小心僵尸入侵！§c番茄和葡萄§r则是文明崛起时的绝佳资源。%n%n对着任务里的物品按§aU§r可以获取更多信息。
susy.quest.db.85.title=果树
susy.quest.db.85.desc=你可以在世界上找到许多§6果树§r。一些例子是香蕉树、橙树、芒果树、杏树、柠檬树和莱姆树。%n%n你可以种植它们的§a§2树苗§r来获得稳定的食物来源。
susy.quest.db.86.title=烤肉串
susy.quest.db.86.desc=§6烤肉串§r可以使用烤肉针制造。有几种类型的烤肉串：%n%n§c库比德烤肉串§r - 用碎肉、番茄、动物油脂（用研钵提取）和洋葱制成%n§c巴格烤肉串§r - 用洋葱、柠檬皮（用研钵制造）、橄榄和碎肉制成%n§c钉洋葱烤肉串§r - 用洋葱和烤肉针制成%n§c钉番茄烤肉串§r - 用番茄和烤肉针制成%n§c串烤胡萝卜§r - 仅烤肉针和胡萝卜%n%n§c记住吃之前，这些必须在原始烤箱中烤。
susy.quest.db.87.title=§l§l§l§l§l§l§a§aCHAPTER 0 // Things lurk in the shadows
susy.quest.db.87.desc=Convert 1 log into 4 §6planks§r. %n%nYou can then craft those planks into a §acrafting table§f.%n%n----------------------------------------%n§3WELCOME TO SUPERSYMMETRY!%n§r----------------------------------------%n- Explore your surroundings%n§r- Find or build shelter%n- Prepare for the winter%n- Acquire basic resources%n- Try not to die%n------------------------------------
susy.quest.db.88.title=皮革
susy.quest.db.88.desc=杀死牛来获得§6皮革§r。这可以用来获得原始盔甲。%n%n注意动物不是很常见，但你仍然可以找到它们。
susy.quest.db.89.title=原始水泵
susy.quest.db.89.desc=§3原始水泵§r是获得大量蒸汽用水的第一种方式，手动向锅炉加水被广泛的认为是个坏主意。%n%n查阅JEI了解更多关于结构的信息，也可以通过§aSHIFT + 右键§r主方块来预览结构。%n%n输出仓§r是水被泵出的地方，你可以让它面朝上或下以自动将水输出到你的管道中，可以使用§6扳手§r来旋转GT的方块（§aSHIFT + 右键§r）。%n%n要增加水的输出，使用的输出仓可以升级到§6ULV§r或§6LV§r§r。%n%n原始水泵需要：%n§610个水泵盖板%n10个防腐木框架%n1个水泵输出仓%n1个原始水泵（控制器）§r%n%n请记住，这非常幸运地不需要世界中的外部水源来运作，本质上是一个§e无限水§r。%n%n§r杂酚油是制造防腐木框架所需的材料，所以请确保先制造焦炉。
susy.quest.db.90.title=煤矿矿藏
susy.quest.db.90.desc=§8煤炭§r可以通过§8煤矿矿藏§r获取，一个矿藏方块可以变成八个煤炭。你可以用§6锤§r破坏来直接获得煤炭或在§6石砧§r上处理。%n%n§8煤炭§r可以合成§6火把§r，作为燃料，或者在§6焦炉§r里烧成§7焦煤§r.
susy.quest.db.91.title=木制多方块储罐
susy.quest.db.91.desc=§a木制多方块储罐§r是第一个你能做的储罐。%n%n它有250,000L的容量（也就是250桶），但因为是木制的，所以无法储存热的流体。%n%n该结构需要：%n%n§623x 木制壁面%n2x 木制储罐阀门%n1x 控制器（木制多方块储罐）%n%n§r可以通过阀门或控制器输入流体。%n%n最重要的是，如果想要自动输出但不想用泵，只需让一个阀门的输出面朝下。%n%n关于构建的更多信息请参考JEI。
susy.quest.db.92.title=线（没有程）
susy.quest.db.92.desc=在§5§lSUSY§r中，各种纤维聚合物如棉花、人造丝、凯夫拉等以纤维和纱线的形式存在，可用于编织太空服、盔甲和其他有用工具。纤维可能受潮。干燥成常规纤维，随后与空气纺成更大的纱线，本质上是聚合物纤维束。这在§l§l§6纺线机§r中完成。
susy.quest.db.93.title=被平衡化的桶
susy.quest.db.93.desc=现在还没有铁桶，所以只能用粘土制的。%n%n可以通过用压缩粘土合成一个§6未烧制的粘土桶§r，然后用坑窑烧制来获取一个§c粘土桶§r。%n%n§c粘土桶§r带有12点耐久，所以最好多做几个。
susy.quest.db.94.title=蒸汽马达
susy.quest.db.94.desc=§6蒸汽马达§r需要两个活塞才能工作。
susy.quest.db.95.title=蒸汽泵
susy.quest.db.95.desc=§6蒸汽泵§r泵动液体，制造真空室就需要。%n%n它也可以作为覆盖板，从不自动输出的储罐或设备（如蒸汽机器）中取出液体。%n%n§6覆盖板§r是给机器添加额外行为而不占用额外空间的方法。通过§a右键§r机器的某个面来放置覆盖板，可以使用§6撬棍§r移除。%n%n§6电动泵、机械臂和传送带都是覆盖板§r。%n%n如果你对覆盖板感到困惑，请观看此视频（YouTube）：{Embed}TypeLink;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0RsPoXjUags;256;20;§9§nGregTech覆盖板完全讲解§r{Embed}%n
susy.quest.db.96.title=标准铁轨
susy.quest.db.96.desc=为了使用标准沉浸式铁路风格建造铁轨轨道，你将需要§6铁轨段§r。它们在§7§6锻造锤§r中用钢板锻造。另外，你还需要一小部分§6石头§r。
susy.quest.db.97.title=LV机械方块
susy.quest.db.97.desc=§6LV机械方块§r是所有LV机器的基本部分，每台机器都需要一个§6机械方块§r，而机械方块需要一个机器外壳。
susy.quest.db.98.title=火星
susy.quest.db.98.desc=-- §a重要信息§r --%n%n- 表面重力：0.38g%n%n- 白天长度：1.027个地球日%n%n- 大气：§c不可呼吸§r（0.00628气压）%n    1. 95.97%%二氧化碳%n    2. 1.93%%氩气%n    3. 1.89%%氮气%n    4. 0.146%%氧气%n    5. 0.0557%%一氧化碳%n    6. 0.021%%水蒸气%n%n- 公转周期：687个地球日%n%n- 绕星：太阳%n%n- 卫星：%n    1. 火卫一%n    2. 火卫二%n%n- 稀有资源：%n    - 双锂矿%n%n-------------------------%n%n§.
susy.quest.db.99.title=LV组装机
susy.quest.db.99.desc=§6组装机§r可能是最重要的电力机器。它用于组装用手无法完成的高级部件。%n%n§c§l§n警告！§r制造组装机会吸引武装土匪的注意，通过制造一些热武器来为自己做好防卫准备。
susy.quest.db.100.title=LV电力活塞
susy.quest.db.100.desc=§7LV电力活塞§r是一个非常重要的机器部件。%n%n在制造LV机器时，你将需要大量的机器部件。你应该一次性制造多个电力活塞来减少痛苦。
susy.quest.db.101.title=LV机械臂
susy.quest.db.101.desc=你需要的另一个部件是§7LV机械臂§r，它用于合成组装机。%n%n机械臂是更高级的传送带。它让你能够按特定数量、特定速率转移物品，或在库存中保持一定数量的物品。%n
susy.quest.db.102.title=LV电动泵
susy.quest.db.102.desc=§7LV电动泵§r是LV机器中另一个重要部件，它也可作为覆盖板，像蒸汽泵一样。
susy.quest.db.103.title=LV车床
susy.quest.db.103.desc=§6车床§r是一台机器，可以把§6一个锭§r变成2个§6杆§r。它也可以用来将1个§6螺栓§r变成§6螺丝§r，有效地使工序效率提高2倍。
susy.quest.db.104.title=§7CHAPTER 2 // Locked and Loaded
susy.quest.db.104.desc=You've made it into the electrical age!%n%nDon't throw away your steam machines, you will probably want to use them until we reach CHAPTER 3.%nThe quickest and easiest way to generate EU power is by making LV §6steam turbines§r. They run on steam, so you can use the steam you're making in your boiler to power them.%n%nWe will explain how EU works in the next page.%n%n§3§r---------------------------------------%n§bLOW VOLTAGE HAS BEEN UNLOCKED! GOOD LUCK.§r%n---------------------------------------%n- Setup basic automatic defenses%n- Dig down to the Earth's mantle and face its horrors%n- Find new and better materials%n- Rain fire on your enemies with ICBMs
susy.quest.db.105.title=电气工程速成课程
susy.quest.db.105.desc=§b§l以下信息极其重要！%n继续前请确保理解GTEU的所有特性。%n§r%n%n能量由§6电压§r和§6电流§r组成。把安培想象为从发电机发出的能量包。一个低压发电机将输出§632EU/t§r（即电压）在§61安§r。%n%n如果你有四个发电机，它们将一起输出§632伏特4安§r。32伏特4安不同于MV（中压-128伏特每安）。这可以比作四根电缆各含32伏特或一根4倍电缆。%n%n===============================%n%n我们来谈谈§4爆炸§r。有多种方式使GT电力机器爆炸。%n%n如果雨直接击中了机器或相邻方块（大概是3x3的平面），§9雨§r会让你的电力机器爆炸，所以将你的机器放在遮挡下。无绝缘的导线当接触雨时会着火，§4火§r也会使机器爆炸。%n%n§6如果你给机器过高的电压，也会爆炸。§r为了避免这个问题，我建议你在不同电压级的机器之间留出一些空间。%n%n你也应该对不同电压等级使用不同线缆来避免出现问题。%n这意味着§l不要对LV能源使用MV线缆§r§r，但现在还远达不到那个电压水平。%n%n
susy.quest.db.106.title=耐火砖第1部分
susy.quest.db.106.desc=结合§6熟石灰§r、§7燧石粉§r、§6沙粉§r和§7粘土球（粉末可以用燧石研钵制造）将创建§6耐火粘土混合物§r。%n%n耐火粘土混合物可以通过使用砖形模具转变为压实耐火粘土。
susy.quest.db.107.title=耐火砖
susy.quest.db.107.desc=混合§6熟石灰§r，§6细沙堆§r，§7燧石粉§r和§7粘土粉§r（用研钵就可以磨粉）就能制作出§6耐火粘土粉§r。%n%n压缩并烧制后就可以获得§6耐火砖§r。%n%n耐火砖块多用于搭建§6土高炉§r。
susy.quest.db.108.title=LV两极磁化机
susy.quest.db.108.desc=§6LV两极磁化机§r对物质进行磁化，无需使用伏打电堆。例如，它可以将普通的铁杆磁化为磁化铁杆。
susy.quest.db.109.title=LV搅拌机
susy.quest.db.109.desc=§6搅拌机§r混合不同的液体，它也可以用于混合无法手动合成的混合粉。§6搅拌机§r是制作大多数合金和某些化学线都必须要有的，它也可用于制造§6混凝土§r。
susy.quest.db.110.title=LV连续搅拌釜式反应器
susy.quest.db.110.desc=§6连续搅拌釜式反应器§r是一种化学反应器。有多种类型的化学反应器，每一种都用于不同类型的反应。%n%n§6CSTR§r在§6液体§r和§6气体§r之间进行连续反应，连续过程涉及两种流体或气体缓慢相互反应。这就是为什么它每半秒左右只反应10升液体，而不是一次处理1,000L。
susy.quest.db.111.title=LV涓流床反应器
susy.quest.db.111.desc=§6涓流床反应器§r是一种化学反应器。%n%n§6涓流床反应器§r在涉及§6催化剂§r的§6液体§r之间进行连续反应，催化剂只能是粉的状态。它进行§6连续反应§r的过程，就和CSTR一样。
susy.quest.db.112.title=LV鼓泡反应器
susy.quest.db.112.desc=§6鼓泡反应器§r是一种化学反应器。%n%n§6鼓泡反应器§r可以将§6气体§r鼓泡并进入另一种液体的反应。它进行§6连续反应§r的过程，就和CSTR一样。
susy.quest.db.113.title=LV固定床反应器
susy.quest.db.113.desc=§6固定床反应器§r是另一种化学反应器。%n%n它进行涉及§6催化剂托盘§r的反应。与涓流床反应器不同，催化剂必须放在托盘中，而不仅仅是使用粉。FBR进行连续过程。
susy.quest.db.114.title=LV结晶器
susy.quest.db.114.desc=§6结晶器§r是一种将大量§b液体§r结晶成固体的机器。
susy.quest.db.115.title=LV电解机
susy.quest.db.115.desc=§6电解§r是使用电能驱动化学反应的过程。除了电源，§6电解池§r由一对发生反应的固体导体（§6电极§r）和允许离子在电极之间移动的介质（§6电解质§r）组成。%n%n某些电解池，如用于§6氯碱工艺§r的，使用§6隔膜§r或§6离子交换膜§r来保持产物分离，同时允许离子通过。
susy.quest.db.116.title=集气室
susy.quest.db.116.desc=§6集气室§r从环境中收集§b空气§r。空气可用于§6烧结§r，也可使用§b低温蒸馏§r分离成§b氮气§r和§b氧气§r。
susy.quest.db.117.title=泥砖
susy.quest.db.117.desc=混合§6泥巴球§r，§6细沙堆§r，§6粘土球§r和§a稻草§r（使用植物纤维合成）就可以获得§6泥砖泥料§r。%n%nMudbricks are §6not required §rfor progressing to the Industrial Age, however they can be used for constructing a §6Primitive Baking Oven§r.
susy.quest.db.118.title=泥砖
susy.quest.db.118.desc=混合§6泥巴球§r（泥巴会在沼泽群系生成，也可以用泥土和水制作），一个§6细沙堆§r，§6粘土球§r和§a稻草§r就可以合成§6泥砖泥料§r。%n%n压缩后放入炉子里烧制成§6泥砖§r。%n%n§6土坯砖块§r可以用来搭建§6简易烤炉§r。
susy.quest.db.119.title=烧结炉
susy.quest.db.119.desc=§6烧结§f是通过压力或热量压实和形成固体物质而不使其融化的过程。%n%n需要§6烧结炉§f来制造§6水泥§f等材料。%n%n烧结炉需要：%n§61个烧结炉（控制器）%n1个输入和输出总线%n1个输入和输出仓%n1个能量仓（任何等级）%n1个维护仓%n72个烧结炉砖块%n43个基础结构外壳%n36个钢框架%n%n§c§l重要提示§c：由于烧结炉的运作方式，输出总线和输入仓需要放在控制器的§l同一侧§r§c，而输入总线和输出仓需要放在机器的另一侧。%n
susy.quest.db.120.title=多方块维护
susy.quest.db.120.desc=维护仓维护多方块机器的仓室。%n%n多方块运行时，可能会出现一些新的维护问题。平均来说，每几个月会出现一次新问题。%n%n维护通过携带维护工具并在维护仓中点击维护按钮来完成。以下是多方块可能的问题列表：%n%n§6"管道松动了"§r可以用§6扳手§r修复。%n§6"螺丝没拧紧"§r可以用§6螺丝刀§r修复。%n§6"有什么东西卡住了"§r可以用§6软锤§r修复。%n§6"外壳有些凹痕"§r可以用§6锤§r修复。%n§6"这东西不属于这"§r可以用§6撬棍§r修复。%n%n所有问题都可以用§7胶带§r来修复。%n
susy.quest.db.121.title=合成气
susy.quest.db.121.desc=§6合成气§r可以通过在热解炉中热解§6焦炭§r获得。
susy.quest.db.122.title=热解炉
susy.quest.db.122.desc=§6Pyrolysis§r is the thermal decomposition of materials at elevated temperatures, often in an inert atmosphere. It involves a change of chemical composition. %nThe Pyrolyse Oven is required to process biomass such as §6coal tar§r and §6coke§r.%n%nThe Pyrolyse Oven requires:§7§6%n1x Pyrolyse Oven Controller%n1x Input Bus for inputting Items%n1x Input Hatch for inputting Fluids%n1x Output Bus for outputting Items%n1x Energy Hatch (any tier)%n1x LV Muffler Hatch%n16x Cupronickel Coil Blocks%n10x ULV Machine Casing%n%n§rRemember that these are ULV machine casing and not LV ones. They're different. Also, the Muffler Hatch must not be obstructed by any other block, or it won't work.%n%nIt is recommended to use 2 LV energy hatches while building the Pyrolyse Oven as processing Coal Tar requires 64 EU/t.%n%nCheck JEI for info on how to build the structure.
susy.quest.db.123.title=LV间歇式反应釜
susy.quest.db.123.desc=§6LV间歇式反应釜§r是一种特殊类型的化学反应器，用于在化学过程中§6溶解物质§r、创建固体§6沉淀物§r和执行§6液液抽出§r。它特别适用于在反应中混合不同的化学物质。
susy.quest.db.124.title=原始电极
susy.quest.db.124.desc=将煤焦油蒸馏成§8沥青§r。这可以与焦炭粉混合生成§8碳浆料§r。将其制成§6未烧制的碳电极§r，然后在电阻炉中烘烤以获得§6碳电极§r。
susy.quest.db.125.title=简易烤炉
susy.quest.db.125.desc=§c简易烤炉§r是一个用于烤制食物的3x2x3的多方块结构。%n%n简易烤炉需要：%n§6%n15x 土坯砖块%n1x 简易烤炉（控制器）%n1x 青铜/铁框架§r
susy.quest.db.126.title=艾奇逊工艺
susy.quest.db.126.desc=Graphitization is the process of converting a carbonaceous material into graphite. This requires extremely high temperatures, far beyond what the majority of metal heating element can withstand.%n%nParadoxically, the only suitable material available that would be capable of surviving such temperatures is graphite itself. However, natural graphite cannot be used for the task as it is difficult to shape into electrodes. Thus the solution is to use a sacrificial carbon electrode that can survive long enough to graphitize a separate carbon electrode. This graphite electrode can then be used to produce more without it being destroyed.
susy.quest.db.127.title=LV提取机
susy.quest.db.127.desc=The §6Extruder §ris an extremely fast, flexible, and expensive semi-universal metal shaping machine. A common use of the §6Extruder§r is to craft §6tool parts§r, or to make §6electrodes§r. The Extruder functions by using §6extruder shapes§r. Look them up in JEI for more info.%n%nIt is recommended that you get an §6§eMV §5§6Extruder§r upon reaching §6§eMedium Voltage§r, as the MV extruder unlock recipes to make long rods, pipes and rings without spending the durability of a §bHammer§r.
susy.quest.db.128.title=高级电解
susy.quest.db.128.desc=The §6Electrolytic Cell §ris a multiblock machine that is required for advanced electrolysis reactions, such as making §bAluminium§r or §7Chlorine §rwith the chloralkali process.%n%nThe Electrolytic Cell requires:%n§6- 1 Electrolytic Cell controller%n- 1 Output Bus%n- 1 Input Bus%n- 1 Input Hatch%n- 1 Output Hatch%n- Between 1 and 2 Energy Hatches%n- 41 Solid Steel Machine Casings%n- 12 Steel Pipe Casings§r%n%nEach §cLV Energy Hatch §rtakes 2 Amperes of LV energy. So the final step of aluminium requires 40 EU/t, which is 2 amps of LV voltage, which shouldn't be a problem.%n%n§l§cThe Electrolytic Cell requires a lot of power! Make sure to build a Large Steam Turbine.
susy.quest.db.129.title=生铁锭
susy.quest.db.129.desc=§6Pig Iron§r is the product of smelting iron ore (such as §6Banded Iron§r and §6Magnetite§o§r) with a high-carbon fuel like §6Coal§r, Charcoal, Anthracite, or Coal Coke in a Blast Furnace.%n%nA small amount of §7Limestone§r is required as a flux in order to remove phosphorus, sulfur and silicon impurities.%n%nThe next step is to make §7Wrought Iron§r or normal §7Iron§r out of this Pig Iron, which will be explained in the next quest.%n%nExtracting usable metal from iron ores requires kilns or furnaces (such as a §cBlast Furnace§r) capable of reaching 1,500 °C (1,773K) or higher, about 500 °C higher than that required to smelt copper. %n%n§%n§cIt is recommended to use dusts instead of ores while smelting Iron. You can do that once you craft the Macerator. If you don't have a Macerator yet, look into the Grindstone.
susy.quest.db.130.title=LV机械外壳
susy.quest.db.130.desc=§6§rNow it's time to move forward and create even better machines. Your §6Steam §rmachines are clunky, don't auto-output, and need pumps to be automated.%n%nOur first step is making a §8§8§7LV Machine Hull.§r Pretty simple, it's just steel and some cables.%n%nMachine Hulls§r are the basis of every electric machine. These are simply Machine Casings with proper wiring inside so that they are ready for people to install various electrical components. %n%nMachine Hulls can also be used to transport stuff through a block, where regular Cables won't work. Always use Wires or Cables where you can.
susy.quest.db.131.title=氢气和氧气
susy.quest.db.131.desc=§bWater §rcan be electrolyzed into §bHydrogen §rand §bOxygen §rby using a Nickel anode, Iron cathode, and Asbestos diaphragm. This is a pretty slow process, so be patient. %n%nThe electrolytic cell multiblock can do this faster, but requires sodium hydroxide.
susy.quest.db.132.title=焊锡
susy.quest.db.132.desc=§6§rSome Assembler recipes may require§6 solder§r§r. While Tin can be used to solder stuff, Soldering Alloy is twice as efficient.%n%nSoldering Alloy §ris an alloy made out of 6 Tin, 3 Lead and 1 Antimony in a §6Mixer§r. %n%nIt is required to solder things more efficiently.
susy.quest.db.133.title=GT 镰刀
susy.quest.db.133.desc=A §6Scythe§r is better than a normal Hoe. It can till, and harvest crops in a 3x3 area in just one hit.%n%nEven if the quest requires an iron Scythe, you can make one with §6bronze§r as well.
susy.quest.db.134.title=钓鱼
susy.quest.db.134.desc=You can use a §6Fishing Rod§r to fish. You might even find some hidden treasure!
susy.quest.db.135.title=设置
susy.quest.db.135.desc=在旅程开始之前，先来点小设置。%n%n- 确保你玩的是最新版%n%n- 确保下载的文件没有出现损坏%n%n- 确保下载的整合包来自可信源（Discord服务器，GitHub或CurseForge）。如果通过一些可疑的网站（例如9minecraft.net）下载，你的设备可能不安全%n%n- 确保你使用的是最新版 Java 8 （Java 9 和更新版不适配）%n%n- 确保你没有更改任何内容，添加其他模组或修改配方 %n%n§3§3§3点击复选框继续%n§r%n
susy.quest.db.136.title=植物和动物
susy.quest.db.136.desc=自从§3§k§b§k[剧透]§r出现以来，在野外找到动物变得有点难了。如果你确实找到了，把它们引诱到基地的一个封闭区域，这样你就可以饲养它们了。
susy.quest.db.137.title=屠刀
susy.quest.db.137.desc=使用§6屠刀§r杀死动物比使用普通§6刀§r或§6剑§r略高效。
susy.quest.db.138.title=小麦
susy.quest.db.138.desc=你可以用§e小麦§r引诱动物到你的基地§a繁殖§r它们，或者你可以用它制作§b面粉§r。%n%n如果你找不到种子，你可以尝试§2打草§r。
susy.quest.db.139.title=面粉
susy.quest.db.139.desc=用§c研钵§r研磨§e小麦§r以制作§b面粉§r。
susy.quest.db.140.title=烤面包
susy.quest.db.140.desc=你必须使用木制模具将从上一个任务中获得的面团塑形成面包。%n%n请注意，你需要一个§c简易烤炉§r来烤面包。
susy.quest.db.141.title=氯化钠
susy.quest.db.141.desc=盐可以从地下的§6§c蒸发岩矿床§r中开采。%n%n研磨§6矿床§r并冲洗它以获得你需要的盐。
susy.quest.db.142.title=面包
susy.quest.db.142.desc=你的新§6烤炉§r可以用来制作许多不同类型的面包。普通面包、长棍面包，甚至§c披萨§r。
susy.quest.db.143.title=喷雾盖
susy.quest.db.143.desc=§6喷雾盖§r将液体喷洒在9x9面积的庄稼上。喷雾盖和地面之间必须有3米的空间才能工作。它必须放在包含有效液体的机器或管道的§c下方§r面。%n%n有效液体包括：%n- 水%n- 肥料溶液%n- 血液（使用生物提取器获得）
susy.quest.db.144.title=烹饪组装机
susy.quest.db.144.desc=更高级的烹饪食谱不能手工制作，所以需要一个§6LV烹饪组装机§r。
susy.quest.db.145.title=蒸汽烤箱
susy.quest.db.145.desc=§6蒸汽烤箱§r是一种效率较低的烘烤方式，但不需要煤。%n%n蒸汽烤箱需要：%n%n1个蒸汽烤箱控制器%n1个蒸汽输入总线%n1个蒸汽输出总线%n1个蒸汽仓%n36个加强的土坯砖%n8个钢框箱
susy.quest.db.146.title=自动切片
susy.quest.db.146.desc=§6LV切片机§r可用于将面包、奶酪、肉类和蔬菜切成§b标准切片§r。%n
susy.quest.db.147.title=平行蒸汽研磨
susy.quest.db.147.desc=The §6Steam Grinder§r is a multi machine that can macerate§6 8 items §rat once instead of 1, but the recipe time for each item is multiplied by 150%% This means that the §cSteam Grinder§r is §68/1.5§r, or §65.333§r times faster than the §cLV macerator§r. Also, just like the §6Steam/LV/MV Macerator§r, the §6§cSteam Grinder§r does not output byproducts.%n%nIt runs on steam power.%n%nBuilding a Steam Grinder requires:%n1x Steam Grinder Controller%n1x Steam Input Bus%n1x Steam Hatch%n1x Steam Output Bus%n22x Bronze Machine Casing%n%nCheck JEI for more info on the structure.%n%nItems should be put into the Input Bus, ready to be processed. They will come out of the Output Bus.
susy.quest.db.148.title=蒸汽熔炉
susy.quest.db.148.desc=The §6Steam Oven §ris a multi machine that can smelt 8 items at once instead of 1. It runs on steam power.%n%nBuilding a Steam Oven requires:%n§6%n1x Steam Oven Controller%n1x Steam Input Bus%n1x Steam Hatch%n1x Steam Output Bus%n8x Bronze Machine Casing%n8x Bronze Firebox Casing %n§o§r%nCheck JEI for more info on the structure.%nItems should be put into the Input Bus, ready to be processed. They will come out of the Output Bus.
susy.quest.db.149.title=铅
susy.quest.db.149.desc=§5铅§r是一种比一般金属密度更高的重金属。铅质地柔软且易于塑形，熔点也相对较低。%n%n铅多出自§5方铅矿§r矿藏，也同时会产出§7锌§r§r。%n%n目前32个锭已经足够。
susy.quest.db.150.title=最简单的储存形式
susy.quest.db.150.desc=制作一个§6箱子§r，它可以存储27种不同的物品。
susy.quest.db.151.title=板条箱
susy.quest.db.151.desc=一个§6青铜板条箱§r最多可以存储54种物品，而不是箱子的27种。%n%n钢板条箱可容纳72种，铝容纳90种，不锈钢容纳108种，钛容纳126种，钨钢容纳144种。
susy.quest.db.152.title=动物志
susy.quest.db.152.desc=由于§c§k12§r年前的灾难性事件，野生动物变得稀少。%n%n如果你发现任何温和的动物群，请确保把它们带回你的基地。本章将重点介绍你可能遇到的各种生命形式的潜在好处或危害。
susy.quest.db.153.title=防腐桶
susy.quest.db.153.desc=铅桶和金桶可以处理§6酸§r。酸是腐蚀性的，会破坏普通桶中使用的青铜和钢。%n%n这里我们列出了所有可以处理酸的桶。
susy.quest.db.154.title=吐司
susy.quest.db.154.desc=用刀切§c面包§r制作吐司切片。
susy.quest.db.155.title=工业水罐
susy.quest.db.155.desc=§3工业液体水罐§r最多可以存储100000桶液体，但需要3x3x3的空间。%n工业液体水罐可以垂直堆叠，如果你需要更多容量。
susy.quest.db.156.title=Barrels, Drums, Storages & More
susy.quest.db.156.desc=§6木制§r和§6金属§r桶如果加装足够多的§6储存容量升级§r，可以容纳数千同类物品。
susy.quest.db.157.title=运输集装箱
susy.quest.db.157.desc=§6运输集装箱§r最多可以将§627§r种不同的物品和液体容器压缩成一个2x2x2结构。
susy.quest.db.158.title=LV成形机
susy.quest.db.158.desc=成形机用于使用模具将金属和橡胶冲压成§6板§r。它用于制造§6装甲板§r。
susy.quest.db.159.title=蒸汽盔甲
susy.quest.db.159.desc=§6蒸汽盔甲§r镀层可以用青铜、钢和黄铜（3铜和1锌的合金）在成形机中制造。%n使用LV流体压缩机，你可以用§b高压空气§r填充§7压缩空气罐§r。如果这些罐在你的物品栏或你的Techgun物品栏中，它们将为蒸汽盔甲提供一些升级，如额外2颗心、减少摔落伤害和更高的台阶（每个台阶1.5格）。
susy.quest.db.160.title=LV高压灭菌器
susy.quest.db.160.desc=§6高压灭菌器§r是一台可用于将粉末转换为晶体的机器，例如§6石英岩§r。制造LV传感器和发射器需要它，因为它们需要石英岩晶体。
susy.quest.db.161.title=传感器和发射器
susy.quest.db.161.desc=§6LV传感器§o§r和§6LV发射器§r是在使用无线电频率或激光的机器中所需的部件。它们由电路和§6压电晶体§r制成，在这种情况下是§6石英岩§r。
susy.quest.db.162.title=自动农业
susy.quest.db.162.desc=§6LV农民§r是一台自动在其前面的9x9农场上工作的机器。%n它使用激光，所以需要§6传感器和发射器§r。运行时，它不断消耗16 EU/t。
susy.quest.db.163.title=自动屠宰
susy.quest.db.163.desc=§6LV生物灭绝者§o§r每秒对4个实体造成§c40伤害§r。它对放在其前面9x9正方形中的生物造成伤害。%n%n它需要红石能量来激活。如果用§b氧化亚氮§r增强，它每秒可以杀死最多12个额外的生物。
susy.quest.db.164.title=生物提取器
susy.quest.db.164.desc=§6§6生物提取器§r§e§r自动从生物中提取液体。它也会对实体造成一些伤害。例如，它可以从人类身上取§c血液§r，或从牛身上取§7牛奶§r。
susy.quest.db.165.title=生物年龄分类器
susy.quest.db.165.desc=§6生物年龄分类器§r移动在其前面1x1空间中的动物。你可以将其配置为仅移动幼体或成体。
susy.quest.db.166.title=微波炉
susy.quest.db.166.desc=§6微波炉§r可以使用强大的微波技术煮炖菜。
susy.quest.db.167.title=万用锅
susy.quest.db.167.desc=LV§6万用锅§r可用于在一个步骤中组装§c酱汁§r和§6意面§r。它只需要一点...时间。
susy.quest.db.168.title=找不到矿脉？
susy.quest.db.168.desc=§6LV电动勘探仪扫描器§r列出了你周围48x48米半径内的每个矿床。%n%n记住电动物品必须在电池缓冲区或任何电动机器中充电。
susy.quest.db.169.title=流体钻井平台
susy.quest.db.169.desc=§6流体钻井平台§r是一台从§6地下矿脉§r钻取液体的多方块机器。这需要中压才能运作，所以你需要使用2个LV能量仓来供电。在正常地形中，你可以找到§9§b盐水§r和§6天然气§r，但你可以在沙漠和海洋中找到§c油§r。%n%n你还不能确切地勘探液体（直到HV），所以你只需在随机地方放置它并祈祷你能得到想要的东西。%n%n无论如何，流体钻井平台需要：%n%n§61个流体钻井平台控制器%n1个能量仓%n1个输出仓%n15个钢框箱%n7个固体钢机械方块§r%n%n§r如果你找不到沙漠或海洋，你应该向南走。沙漠应该距离你从跳伞舱被放下的地方约2,000米。
susy.quest.db.170.title=电池缓冲
susy.quest.db.170.desc=§6电池缓冲§r是最早形式的能量存储。它可以存储的电池数量和§6输出安培数§r取决于你选择的缓冲区。例如，16x缓冲区可以容纳16块电池并输出16安培的能量。更多信息，请查看第2章。
susy.quest.db.171.title=Gregic工具V2
susy.quest.db.171.desc=§6GT Electric Tools§r are a good upgrade during your playthrough because they mine much faster compared to their unpowered counterparts such as the Mining Hammer or Wrench. They also consume their durability much slower than their unpowered counterparts too, as long as these tools have energy inside their buffer. Otherwise, the electric tools will consume durability much, much faster. §cSo, REMEMBER TO CHARGE YOUR TOOLS!§%n%n%n§fIf your electric tools run out of durability, it should return the power unit of the same voltage. §6LV tools§5§6§r return §6LV power units§r, §6MV tools return MV power units§r, and so on. You can recraft the retrieved power unit with a new tip to make a new electric tool. Alternatively, you can craft your damaged tool with a fresh new tip to get a new tool with 100%% durability §9§e(this crafting recipe can be done in a 2x2 crafting grid!)§r. You can upgrade your old tool with better drill/wrench tips this way too, so a §6Steel Drill (LV)§r can be combined with Aluminium Drill tip to make §6Aluminium Drill (LV)§r. However, you can't remove the tip from an electric tool.§l%n%n§e§lNote: You can §a[right-click]§r a GT battery to allow the battery to charge items in inventories, which might be useful during a long mining trip. Lead-Acid battery (or any LV battery) should be able to power your LV tools. MV battery can charge MV and LV tools, HV battery can charge HV, MV and LV tools, and so on.§r§r%n%nYou can get higher tier electric tools in §d§bMV§r, §eH§r§7§6§f§eV§r, and beyond. Higher tier tools will have bigger energy buffers, mining area, mining speed, durability.%n%n§l§e§lNote: There is no higher tier for the Chainsaw and Screwdriver, the Wrench skips MV and EV tier, and there are no tier above IV.§r%n%nThe §6Steel Drill §rmines a 3x3x1 area with a single hit. If you §a[right-click]§r while holding it, it will automatically place any Torches that you have. If you §a[sneak+right-click]§r while holding it, a menu will open, which will allow you to configure the mining area of the drill. I recommending testing this feature on your Singleplayer Creative world.%n%nThe §6Steel Wrench §racts as a wrench. (Note: The §bAluminium§6 Drill§r can't break §7§8Steel Pipe Casing§r, so it is recommended that you keep using §8Steel§r Wrench Tip until you get §7Stainless Steel§r)%n%nThe §6Steel Chainsaw §racts as an axe, but it can harvest ice and it can also be used as a weapon which disables shields.%n%nThe §6Steel Screwdriver §racts as a screwdriver.%n%nYou can make these tools using other materials such as bronze, invar, or iron to complete this quest.
susy.quest.db.172.title=自由之地
susy.quest.db.172.desc=建造一个§6钻井平台§r§r来获取任何类型的石油。§c油、轻油和重油都可以。%n§r%n建议在你的油井旁边建立一个基本的电力发电机。油井很可能远离你的主基地（它要么在沙漠中，要么在海上）。%n%n如果任务不起作用，使用复选框来完成它。
susy.quest.db.173.title=稀释油
susy.quest.db.173.desc=在LV混合器中混合任何类型的§6油§r和一些§b水§r来获得稀释油。
susy.quest.db.174.title=蒸馏厂
susy.quest.db.174.desc=§6LV蒸馏厂§r是一台将一种液体蒸馏成其馏分的机器。它是§6石油化学§r或石油加工的重要部分。%n%n需要蒸馏厂将油分割成其馏分，例如§6汽油§r或§6煤油§r。
susy.quest.db.175.title=脱盐油
susy.quest.db.175.desc=将任何类型的§6稀释油§r放在§6LV静电分离器§r中来获得§6脱盐油§r和§6油性盐水§r。
susy.quest.db.176.title=电烤箱
susy.quest.db.176.desc=The §2Electric Baking Oven§r improves on the design of the GTFO Baking Oven, running several times faster and requiring only EU rather than fuel.%n%nIt may also be parallelized up to processing §613§r(!) items at once by extending the structure to the right.%n%nThe EBO, however, has a §ctemperature§r mechanic. Items can only be processed once a specific temperature has been reached within the EBO, which may take a non-negligible amount of time to reach. Power consumption also increases along with the temperature of the EBO, occasionally requiring §6HV§r power for some items like pizzas (which you can just use the normal/steam baking oven for if you wish).%n%nBy default, the EBO is set to §aadaptive mode§r, meaning that it will always attempt to reach the exact temperature that the items inside require to be processed. In this mode, it will also automatically decrease its temperature when not in use. This can be helpful for manual processing, but can also be turned off in the bottom-right corner of its GUI. %nWhen adaptive mode is turned off, you can set the target temperature using the + and - icons, which it will automatically attempt to reach. This can be quite useful if you want to use the EBO within your passive or active automation systems and know a specific item you wish to process.%n%nThe EBO is made out of around a stack of §bBismuth Bronze§r, which does require the §eMV§r Roaster or a Reaction Furnace to obtain.
susy.quest.db.177.title=蒸汽研磨机
susy.quest.db.177.desc=§l蒸汽研磨机§r是一个一次可以研磨8个物品的多方块研钵。%n%n它需要：%n22个青铜镀砖机械方块%n1个蒸汽仓%n1个输入总线（蒸汽）%n1个输出总线（蒸汽）%n1个蒸汽熔炉控制器%n%n这是一个3x3x3结构，控制器在其中一个面的中心。%n输入和输出总线放在控制器的两侧。%n%n祝你好运！%n
susy.quest.db.178.title=原油和硫酸油馏分
susy.quest.db.178.desc=Distill§6 §rany type of §6Heated Oil §rto get a number of oil fractions. Here is a list:%n%n§6- Crude Heavy Gas Oil%n- Crude Light Gas Oil%n- Crude Kerosene%n- Light Atmospheric Overheads Gas%n- Atmosphere Oil Residue§o§r%n%nThe first four can be further distilled into:%n%n§6- Sulfuric Heavy Gas Oil%n- Sulfuric Gas Oil%n- Sulfuric Kerosene%n- Sulfuric Light Naphtha%n- Sulfuric Heavy Naphtha%n- Sulfuric Fuel Gas§o§r%n%nAbout the last one, §cAtmosphere Oil Residue§r, it's a long story. See the Residue quest instead.%n%nYou don't need to submit all the fluids, just click on the check box when you have everything set up correctly.
susy.quest.db.179.title=LV静电分离器
susy.quest.db.179.desc=§e静电分离器§r是一台利用静电的力量来§6从油中去除盐分§r的机器。
susy.quest.db.180.title=处理硫酸馏分
susy.quest.db.180.desc=你的§6硫酸馏分§r必须§6处理§r通过在固定床反应器中与§9氢气§r反应液体。
susy.quest.db.181.title=脱硫
susy.quest.db.181.desc=§6处理的油馏分§r可以蒸馏成正常的§6油馏分§r（如汽油或汽油）和§6酸性气体§r。
susy.quest.db.182.title=压力下
susy.quest.db.182.desc=§6流体压缩机§r§r将液体压缩成它们的§c高压§r变体。它用于获得§c高压氢气§r。
susy.quest.db.183.title=氯碱工艺
susy.quest.db.183.desc=Putting Water and Salt Water in an Electrolytic Cell with a Nickel anode, Graphite cathode, and Asbestos diaphragm will yield §3Chlorine§r, Hydrogen and §3Sodium Hydroxide§r solution. %n%nTip: The diluted salt water produced can be recycled back into salt water either by mixing it with salt or distilling it.
susy.quest.db.184.title=:alkaline:
susy.quest.db.184.desc=§6蒸馏§r氢氧化钠溶液将给出§6氢氧化钠§r粉。
susy.quest.db.185.title=铝酸钠
susy.quest.db.185.desc=You are about to start a long chemical process for obtaining §baluminium§r, a material needed for MV tier. This is the first page.%nIf you ever feel confused, take a look at the §6Chemistry §rtab.%nIt is recommended that you set this up to be an automatic process, with each machine feeding onto the next one. %n%nFirst, you will need to get §6bauxite§r. Bauxite is found in ore deposits from height level 0 to 80.%n%nThe Bauxite Ore must be §6crushed §rinto Bauxite Dust, which is then reacted with §6Sodium Hydroxide Solution§rin an §6LV Roaster §rto get Bauxite Leach.%n%nThe solution is then §ccentrifuged§r with an LV centrifuge to remove Red Mud and get Impure Sodium Aluminate solution.
susy.quest.db.186.title=LV离心机
susy.quest.db.186.desc=The §cCentrifuge §r§rcentrifuges impurities out of solids, and it is also used to get §arare materials§r out of ore dusts.
susy.quest.db.187.title=合成站 V2
susy.quest.db.187.desc=§3合成站§r是个非常高级的工作台，带有工具栏和物品栏。%n%n把物品标记到格子上或使用§2JEI§r里的§a+§r按键来添加配方。%n%n合成时将使用物品栏和工具栏里的材料。还有九个可用于记录合成配方以便无需再次打开§2JEI§r。%n%n§3合成站§r可以访问§6相邻的存储§r（例如箱子/抽屉/板条箱）到其物品栏。
susy.quest.db.188.title=电阻炉
susy.quest.db.188.desc=The §6§d§2Electric Resistance Furnace §e§fis, perhaps, the most important multiblock in GregTech. It is required to make §6§bAluminium §fingots, your main material for the MV age. Most of the ERF's recipes require at least §6120 EU/t§f, so you will need two LV energy hatches.%n%nYou can swap out ERF's coils in the future to make it produce more heat, which will unlock new recipes and §9Overclock §fthe multiblock, making the recipes run faster.%n%nThe Electric Resistance Furnace requires:%n§61x Electric Resistance Furnace Controller%n16x Cupronickel Coil Block%n(9-12)x Heat Proof Invar Machine Casing §f§6(the amount depends on how many different hatches you use)%n§62x LV Energy Hatch§f (you will be able to upgrade the energy hatches to MV and higher voltages later)%n§61x Input and Output Buses (if needed)%n1x Input and Output Hatches (if needed)%n1x Maintenance Hatch%n1x Muffler Hatch (should be placed at the top of the multiblock facing up)%n%n§fPlease note that running ERF requires a lot of power, so you need to either put it on a different power grid or upgrade your power generation.%n%nIf you are confused on how to make the multiblock, either check JEI or §a[right-click]§r on the controller (remember that most hatch placements can be switched around except the Muffler Hatch).%n%nOh, and yes, we are aware that the name might be a little... different from what you're used to. Don't worry about it.
susy.quest.db.189.title=氢氧化铝
susy.quest.db.189.desc=§6Crystallize §rthe Sodium Aluminate solution in a §6Crystallizer §rwith water to get§5§6 Aluminium Hydroxide§r. %n%nObtaining your first aluminium hydroxide dust allows for an alternative recipe that does not require carbon dioxide.
susy.quest.db.190.title=氧化铝粉
susy.quest.db.190.desc=§6Aluminium Hydroxide §r§rcan be reduced to Alumina in an Electric Resistance Furnace.
susy.quest.db.191.title=LV武器工厂
susy.quest.db.191.desc=The §6Weapons Factory §rmakes guns, turrets, ammo, and other weapon-related items.
susy.quest.db.192.title=开放式模块化炮塔
susy.quest.db.192.desc=If you want to make turrets, you'll need turret bases. Let's make some.%n%nThey are a block that acts as the base for turrets. They use §cRF §renergy. You can put Turrets on all sides of the block, just note that each turret requires a minimum tier of turret base to be placed. %n%nAll the settings for a modular turret are stored and set in the base that holds the turrets. In their interface, you should find most descriptions pretty easily.%n%n
susy.quest.db.193.title=炮塔头部
susy.quest.db.193.desc=Turret Chambers and Barrels will be required to make turret heads.
susy.quest.db.194.title=枪炮塔
susy.quest.db.194.desc=The Gun Turret shoots at whatever gets into an 18m radius of it. It needs a Tier 2 or higher turret base. %n%nIt uses §4100 RF§r (25 EU) per shot, and it shoots 2.5 times per second.%n%nIt uses bullets as ammo.
susy.quest.db.195.title=燃烧炮塔
susy.quest.db.195.desc=The Incendiary Turret yeets fire at whatever gets into an 18m radius of it. It needs a Tier 2 or higher turret base. %n%nIt uses §4250 RF§r (14.8 EU) per shot, and it shoots 0.8 times per second.%n%nIt uses flaming clay as ammo.
susy.quest.db.196.title=手枪
susy.quest.db.196.desc=The §6Pistol §ris one of the guns you can make at LV tier. It uses pistol magazines as ammo, and has a reload time of 1.75 seconds.%n%nFor more info, look at the tooltip.
susy.quest.db.197.title=战斗霰弹枪
susy.quest.db.197.desc=The §6Combat Shotgun §ris one of the guns you can make at LV tier. It uses shotgun rounds as ammo, and has a reload time of 2.5 seconds. It's also multishot, which means it will shoot 8 times at once. %n%nCrafting it requires a §6Steel Receiver§r.%n%nFor more info, look at the tooltip.
susy.quest.db.198.title=氟化氢
susy.quest.db.198.desc=§6Fluorite §rcan be found in fluorite and cassiterite deposits, at Y level 0 to 80.%n%nThe ore has to be §6smelted §rand then §6combined with sulfuric acid §rto get §6Hydrogen Fluoride.
susy.quest.db.199.title=氢氟酸
susy.quest.db.199.desc=Water can be §6bubbled §rinto Hydrogen Fluoride to create §2Hydrofluoric Acid§r, an extremely strong acid.
susy.quest.db.200.title=氟化钠
susy.quest.db.200.desc=§6Sodium Hydroxide Solution§r can be reacted with §6Hydrogen Fluoride§r in a bubble column reactor to get §6Sodium Fluoride Solution§r.%n%nThis has to be§b §cdistilled §rto get Sodium Fluoride.
susy.quest.db.201.title=三氟化铝
susy.quest.db.201.desc=§6Alumina §rneeds to be roasted with §6Hydrofluoric Acid§r to make §bAluminium Trifluoride.§r%n%n§rNote: you will need Aluminium Trifluoride as well as Cryolite for the final process. So don't convert all of it into Cryolite right away.
susy.quest.db.202.title=冰晶石
susy.quest.db.202.desc=React §bAluminium Trifluoride §rand §5Sodium Fluoride §rin an §cLV Roaster §rto get Cryolite.
susy.quest.db.203.title=霍尔-埃鲁工艺
susy.quest.db.203.desc=In an Electrolytic Cell, react §610 Alumina Dust§r, 3 §6Coke Dust/Carbon Black Dust§r to get §6576L of Liquid Aluminium §r. The process requires §6Aluminium Trifluoride§r and §6Liquid Cryolite§r, which are not consumed when used.
susy.quest.db.204.title=生命的基石
susy.quest.db.204.desc=You can §cpyrolyze§6 certain carbonaceous sources into carbon black, a very important resource to have since it will be used in various smelting recipes.
susy.quest.db.205.title=LV提取器
susy.quest.db.205.desc=The §cExtractor §rextracts §cfluid §rout of solid materials. For example, you can get §6liquid rubber§o§o§r by putting rubber in. It can also extract §aseed oil §rout of seeds.
susy.quest.db.206.title=疯狂高pH
susy.quest.db.206.desc=Using an alternate version of the §6chloralkali process§r, using a §crock salt §rsolution instead of normal salt water.§r
susy.quest.db.207.title=镓
susy.quest.db.207.desc=You can electrolyze §6§cIMPURE §rSodium Hydroxide Solution in an Electrolyzer to get §6Gallium§r, an important element required for circuits. %n%nThe process gives §6Gallium dust§r.
susy.quest.db.208.title=建筑师的好友
susy.quest.db.208.desc=§7§6建筑师的锯木厂§r允许你从任何立方体非瓷砖实体创建许多不同的形状（§a工作台§f是唯一已知的例外）。这些包括45度角斜坡。%n%n瓷砖实体是能够执行其他操作（如机器）或提供效果（如音符方块）的方块。
susy.quest.db.209.title=建筑工艺工具
susy.quest.db.209.desc=§6建筑师的锤子§r允许你通过§a[右击]§r沿竖轴旋转方块。§a[潜行+右击]§r允许你循环通过所有可能的旋转。%n%n§6建筑师的凿子§r有几个利基用途。一个用途是将方块连接或解散在一起，例如栅栏。另一个用途是通过§a[右击]§r收获玻璃而不破坏它。
susy.quest.db.210.title=小型基本工具
susy.quest.db.210.desc=§2Littletiles§f是一个非常强大的mod，允许你通过其16x16x16子组件（称为§b像素§r）操纵方块。%n%n§6小包§r接收方块并将其转换为具有有限像素数量的形式以供§2Littletiles§r使用。它也接收任何染料，并将其转换为与§bC§dM§d§eY§8K§r减色模型相对应的包中的数量。（§b青色、§d洋红色、§e黄色§r和§8关键（黑色）§f）%n%n§r§6小凿子、小锤子§r、§6小锯§r和§6小手套§r可以通过§a'C'§r默认访问其菜单，你可以设置绘制形状，以及设置将消耗包中颜色的颜色。§e你可能需要将此重新绑定到其他内容，因为Supersymmetry中存在现有的按键冲突。此绑定名为"配置工具"。§r当你手中拿着工具时，你可以通过查看左下角显示的文本来看到其他选项。§e%n%n§f§6小凿子§r可用于对§b像素§r进行加法更改，并通过§a[右击]§r使用。%n%n§6小锤子§r可用于对§b像素§r进行减法更改，并通过§a[左击]§r使用。%n%n§6小锯§r可用于对§b面§r进行挤压更改，并通过§a[右击]§r和§a[潜行+右击]§r使用（左下角§4§c§l对你撒谎§r）！%n%n§6小手套§r有多种模式%n- 放置定义尺寸的像素矩形%n- 复制放置的结构到手中（配方模式）%n- 用其他像素替换你正在查看的面上的像素%n所有这些都可以通过§a[右击]§r访问。
susy.quest.db.211.title=我们做一点工作台
susy.quest.db.211.desc=§6小蓝图§r可以通过§a[左击]§r和§a[右击]§r你的创建边界来使用，类似于Worldedit，按下绑定的菜单键（§a'C'§r默认），并在更改几个参数后保存如果你愿意。你以后可以§a[右击]§r这个蓝图来"粘贴"这个创建到其他地方，给足够的资源。有效地，蓝图是一个ctrl + c，ctrl + v工具。%n%n菜单中上述参数可以用于以不同行为粘贴你的创建，例如它变成§b§d门、存储、梯子或其他各种东西。§r这是§2Littletiles§r被认为非常强大的原因之一。%n%n你可以使用§6小工作台§r来制作你复制的结构并将其生成为库存项目。%n%n§8§m到处垃圾邮件Among Us从未如此简单！
susy.quest.db.212.title=更多工具
susy.quest.db.212.desc=这些是你使用较少的§2Littletiles§r工具。%n%n§6小刷子§r用于使用§6小包§r中的上述油漆来绘制你的结构。与其他工具一样，你可以访问菜单来更改形状，以及颜色。%n§6§r%n§6小扳手§r用于更新遇到图形问题的§2Littletiles§r方块，例如未连接的角/边，或未渲染的边。%n%n§6小螺丝刀§r§e是创意专属物品，不会作为任务包括§r，但它允许你用来自菜单的其他§b像素§r替换来自其他方块的§b像素§r。
susy.quest.db.213.title=百万人必须凿刻
susy.quest.db.213.desc=§2凿子§r因其能将整个仓库的无用圆石变成看起来不错的建筑材料的奇迹工具而闻名。每个原版方块、几个常见金属方块和该特定mod添加的方块都可以凿刻。§e示例如下所示任务中。§r%n%n正常§6凿子§r可以：%n- 直接通过凿子GUI凿刻%n- 当凿子库存为空时通过§a[左击]§r符合条件的方块来循环凿刻%n- 当凿子库存中有相同类型的方块和特定凿子时通过§a[左击]§r设置要凿刻的方块%n%n§e§r§6钢凿子§r也可以在一个区域内凿刻世界内的方块。%n%n§6iChisel§r有2个比钢凿子更多的区域选项，更通用的库存凿刻，以及在不同模式中预览所选凿刻图案的能力。%n%n现在，制造一个正常的§6凿子§r就足够了。%n
susy.quest.db.214.title=反光块
susy.quest.db.214.desc=反光块是颜色鲜艳的方块，完全忽视它们暴露的任何光照效果。§e§r因此，它们可以从漆黑中的数公里外看到。§e请记住它们实际上不会自己发光。§r%n%n它们可能被用作§a色度键§r，用于任何视频编辑。
susy.quest.db.215.title=虚空石
susy.quest.db.215.desc=§8§o这是什么，我怎样才能摆脱它？%n%n§r§d§r§5虚空石§r是"神秘的"和"克苏鲁式的"方块，以不可理解的符号或对不断变化的未知潮汐的瞥见而来。如果你喜欢魔法，你可能认为它们很好。
susy.quest.db.216.title=未来块
susy.quest.db.216.desc=§9未来块§r，尽管块集中可用纹理集很小，但可能是许多人的最爱。它们描绘了炫目屏幕、彩虹，甚至假ME控制器。它们很好地补充了§4§r§cG§6r§ce§6g§ci§6c§r美学。
susy.quest.db.217.title=工厂块
susy.quest.db.217.desc=§9工厂块§r与§9实验室块§r一起对§4§r§cG§6r§ce§6g§ci§6c§r美学至关重要。它们描绘了重型机械、金属镀层、电路、管道和通风口。
susy.quest.db.218.title=实验室块
susy.quest.db.218.desc=§9实验室块§r与§9工厂块§r一起对§4§r§cG§6r§ce§6g§ci§6c§r美学至关重要。它们描绘了无菌瓷砖、通风口、界面和一些钢方块。
susy.quest.db.219.title=漂亮和色彩分离
susy.quest.db.219.desc=§2Xtone§r添加了许多不同的方块。你可以通过按住§a[潜行]§r并在§6Xtone方块§r在你手中时滚动来更改这些方块的纹理/颜色。本质上，§2Xtone§r是没有任何凿子的§2凿子§r，只有更改其添加的方块纹理的能力。%n%n每个§2Xtone§r块配方的基础是§6Xtone瓷砖§r。如果你想使用§2Xtone§r，你需要制造一些。
susy.quest.db.220.title=如何以格雷方式建造
susy.quest.db.220.desc=任何起始文明必须有一个§c基地§r。基地§c§l不是§r随意放在地上的机器组合。%n%n你必须建造和§6组织§r工厂，否则在后来的阶段进展将极其困难。建议你为工厂的不同部分建造几座建筑。
susy.quest.db.221.title=水泥
susy.quest.db.221.desc=水泥是制造§6混凝土§r的关键成分之一。%n%n水泥熟料在烧结炉中通过结合§6粘土§r和§6石灰石§r§r和用空气和合成气烧结制成。%n%n然后必须用空气在混合器中冷却，并粉碎以制造水泥粉。%n%n混凝土对§4§r§cG§6r§ce§6g§ci§6c§r美学至关重要。
susy.quest.db.222.title=混凝土
susy.quest.db.222.desc=§6混凝土§r可以通过混合水、水泥粉和任何砾石、沙子和粘土制成。%n%n混凝土必须然后在§6LV流体凝固机§r中凝固成方块。%n%n你可以通过在§c化学浴§r中向混凝土中添加更多水来制造§8深色混凝土§r。%n%n§l§c混凝土在行走时提供大幅§l加速§r§c。
susy.quest.db.223.title=LV流体凝固机
susy.quest.db.223.desc=§6LV流体凝固机§r是一台将液体凝固成粒块、锭、方块或任何你想要的东西的机器，如果你使用§6模具§r。
susy.quest.db.224.title=线圈绝缘
susy.quest.db.224.desc=像§6热解炉§r和§5§6电阻炉§r这样的机器需要线圈来工作。线圈需要§6矿物羊毛片§r用于绝缘，通过离心§d§c熔岩§r获得。%n%n你可以在Y等级15以下以及下界和末地找到熔岩。
susy.quest.db.225.title=食物切割
susy.quest.db.225.desc=§6水果和蔬菜§r可以用刀§r切割。切片蔬菜比普通蔬菜略好。
susy.quest.db.226.title=三明治
susy.quest.db.226.desc=使用切片面包，你可以制造§6三明治§r。%n%n有几种不同的类型：%n%n§a蔬菜三明治§r - 带有黄瓜、番茄和洋葱片%n§c培根三明治§r - 带有培根，你可以通过切片猪排获得%n§4肉三明治§r - 带有牛排和切达奶酪%n§6吐司三明治§r - 里面有面包%n%n大型三明治可以在烹饪组装器中制造。
susy.quest.db.227.title=建筑魔杖
susy.quest.db.227.desc=§6建筑魔杖§r是为你建造表面的魔杖。有4种主要的魔杖类型：%n%n§7石建筑魔杖§r一次只能放置5个方块，只能垂直放置方块，可以在破坏前放置约130个方块。%n%n铁建筑魔杖一次可以放置9个方块，可以垂直或水平放置，可以放置约250个方块。%n%n§b钻石建筑魔杖§r可以放置尽可能多的方块，即在破坏前约1562个方块。%n%n§d不可破坏建筑魔杖§r一次可以放置库存价值的方块，永远不会破坏。%n%n你可以通过按§6M§r更改建筑魔杖的模式。
susy.quest.db.228.title=火药
susy.quest.db.228.desc=§6火药§r可以通过混合§6硝酸盐§r（在沙漠盐矿中找到）、§6硫磺和§7§6煤§r来获得。%n%n这将是你走向§c更强大武器§r的第一步。更多信息，请参阅§d进攻&防御章任务线§r。
susy.quest.db.229.title=石砖
susy.quest.db.229.desc=所有§6石头§r都可以变成漂亮的砖块。
susy.quest.db.230.title=建筑小工具
susy.quest.db.230.desc=有时建造大型结构可能有点繁琐，需要大量努力。§6建筑小工具§r旨在使建筑变得更容易一点。%n%n§6建筑小工具§r允许你使用一组不同的建筑模式来构建结构。它允许你在远距离建造结构。只需§a[右击]§r放置方块，§a[潜行+右击]§r设置要放置的方块类型。%n%n§6交换小工具§r将交换你正在查看的方块与工具设置的方块。只需§a[右击]§r交换方块，§a[潜行+右击]§r设置要放置的方块类型。%n%n§6复制粘贴小工具§r将允许你复制大块方块的区域并将其粘贴到不同的位置。你可以在工具提示上查看所需的材料。%n%n
susy.quest.db.231.title=工厂必须成长
susy.quest.db.231.desc=§6§r铁§6楼梯§r和§7§6人行天桥§r可以用来补充§4§r§cG§6r§ce§6g§ci§6c§r美学。§r工厂必须成长。%n%n还有§b电围栏§r，一种便宜的保卫基地的方式。要通过，你必须通过§6电门§r。
susy.quest.db.232.title=硝酸
susy.quest.db.232.desc=%n§6硫酸§r可以在批反应器中与§6硝酸盐§r（在盐矿中找到）混合以创建§6硝酸§r。
susy.quest.db.233.title=硝化混合物
susy.quest.db.233.desc=§6硫酸§r和§6硝酸§r可以混合以创建§6硝化混合物§r，用于炸药。
susy.quest.db.234.title=甲苯
susy.quest.db.234.desc=§6甲苯§r可以通过几个处理步骤从§6煤焦油§r生产。首先蒸馏§6煤焦油§r获得§6煤焦油§r。然后将§6煤焦油§r与§6硫酸§r混合以获得§6酸性煤焦油§r，用§6糠醛§r离心§7§6酸性煤焦油§r以获得§6B.T.E.X提取物§r然后用§6蒸汽§r蒸馏§6B.T.E.X提取物§r以获得§6B.T.E.X.§r。蒸馏§6B.T.E.X§r以获得§6甲苯§r。
susy.quest.db.235.title=TNT
susy.quest.db.235.desc=在§c批反应器§r中结合§6硝化混合物§r和§6甲苯§o§r以制造§7§6三硝基甲苯溶液§r。%n%n然后，§c蒸馏§r它以制造§6TNT粉§r。
susy.quest.db.236.title=LV电弧炉
susy.quest.db.236.desc=§6电弧炉§r（EAF）是通过电弧加热材料的炉子。电弧炉需要§b氧气§r才能工作，所以请确保查看水电解。电弧炉可以用于将机器分解成其组成金属。
susy.quest.db.237.title=砷
susy.quest.db.237.desc=§c钡矿、钴矿和毒砂和雌黄§r可以通过带氧气的电阻炉以创建§6小堆三氧化砷§r。%n%n然后可以用一些§6碳§r§6电弧炉§r以创建纯砷。
susy.quest.db.238.title=砷化镓
susy.quest.db.238.desc=结合§7§7§6砷§r和§6镓§r以创建§6砷化镓§r，稍后将有多种用途。
susy.quest.db.239.title=二极管
susy.quest.db.239.desc=§6二极管§r是主要在一个方向上传导电流的电子元件。它们需要用于构造§7§6中压电路§r。%n%n你可以通过在组装器中结合细铜线与§6§6方铅矿§r和§6熔融玻璃§r来制造二极管。使用提取器熔化玻璃。稍后有一种更有效的方式来制造二极管，但它需要聚乙烯。
susy.quest.db.240.title=树脂和胶水
susy.quest.db.240.desc=离心§6粘性树脂§r以获得液体§6树脂§r，然后蒸馏树脂以获得§6胶水§r。
susy.quest.db.241.title=酚醛电路板
susy.quest.db.241.desc=在组装器中结合§6胶水§r和处理过的木浆以制造酚醛电路板。然后用§7银§r线在工作台中涂覆它以完成电路板。%n%n或者你可以在组装器中用§6铜箔§r、§6处理过的木板§r、§6细银线§r和§6胶水§r生产好的电路板。
susy.quest.db.242.title=好的电子电路
susy.quest.db.242.desc=结合§6好的电路板§r、两个§6二极管§r和3个你的旧§cLV电路§r以制造§cMV电路§r。
susy.quest.db.243.title=§6第3章 // 移山倒海
susy.quest.db.243.desc=制造§6MV机器外壳§r。%n%n§r当你设置MV机器时，记住当它们被给予比预期更多的电压时会爆炸。§c建议你的LV和MV机器生产线是分离的。§rMV电缆由§6铜§r制成，不是锡。%n§r%n---------------------------------------%n§b中压已解锁！祝你好运。§r%n---------------------------------------%n- 改变你周围的景观以适应你的需求%n- 对抗你的敌人使用有毒化学品%n- 建造更强大和更远射程的导弹%n- 用自动武器削倒怪物
susy.quest.db.244.title=合成计算
susy.quest.db.244.desc=§6合成计算器§r是一个简单的计算器，帮助你计算你需要为某些物品收集多少资源。%n%n将任何物品放入左上角的槽口将让计算器计算成本。%n%n你需要输入使其工作所需的配方，因为可能有不同的方式来制造一个物品或液体。%n%n%n%n
susy.quest.db.245.title=工业装饰
susy.quest.db.245.desc=§6Engineer's Decor §radds many new blocks and furniture to fit the aesthetic of an Industrial Age base.
susy.quest.db.246.title=Xtone瓷砖
susy.quest.db.246.desc=§6Xtones §radds a lot of blocks that can be used to make a factory aesthetic.
susy.quest.db.247.title=001 | 氢
susy.quest.db.247.desc=§6Element§r: Hydrogen (H)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 1%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 1.008 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 13.81 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 20.28 K%n§6Properties§r: Hydrogen is the lightest §6Element§r, commonly found in the universe. It is used as a fuel, in industrial processes, and is a key component of water and many organic compounds.%n%n§lPrimitive:§9 §r§9Water§r can be electrolyzed to get Hydrogen and Oxygen.%n%nIf you have sodium hydroxide solution, you can speed this up about 7x in an electrolytic cell.%n%n§lUniversal:§r%n§6Steam and Syngas§r can be reformed using an LTS or HTS §6catalyst§r to create §6Reformed Syngas§r, which is then passed through a §bPressure Swing Adsorber§r to make Hydrogen.%n%n§dMethane §rcan be pyrolyzed under a§7 Bismuth catalyst§r at §cEV§r to make Hydrogen.%n%n§lSpecialized:§r%nCerium III Oxide + Water -> Cerium IV Oxide + Hydrogen%nCerium IV Oxide -> Cerium III Oxide + Oxygen
susy.quest.db.248.title=002 | 氦
susy.quest.db.248.desc=%n§6Element§r: Helium (He)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 2%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 4.0026 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 0.95 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 4.22 K%n§6Properties§r: Helium is a noble gas known for its low density and low reactivity. It is used in cryogenics, as a coolant in various applications, and for filling balloons.%n
susy.quest.db.249.title=003 | 锂
susy.quest.db.249.desc=§6Element§r: Lithium (Li)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 3%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 6.94 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 453.65 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 1603 K%n§6Properties§r: Lithium is an alkali metal that is highly reactive and flammable. It is used in rechargeable batteries, ceramics, and in some psychiatric medications.%n%n§lPrimitive: §r§cN/A%n§r%n§lUniversal: §r§r§6Lithium Carbonate §rcan be obtained by processing salar brine. It's then roasted with Hydrochloric Acid to make §bLithium Chloride§r. Molten Lithium Chloride is electrolyzed into Lithium.%n%n§lSpecialized: §r§cN/A
susy.quest.db.250.title=004 | 铍
susy.quest.db.250.desc=§6Element§r: Beryllium (Be)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 4%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 9.0122 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1560 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 2742 K%n§6Properties§r: Beryllium is a lightweight and strong alkaline earth metal. It is used in aerospace applications, X-ray windows, and as a moderator in nuclear reactors.%n%n§lPrimitive: §r§cN/A%n%n§r§lUniversal: §rMelt §2beryl§r (emeralds) with§7 sodium carbonate §rin a reaction furnace in order to obtain §3alkali fused beryl§r.%n%nAlkali fused beryl partially dissolves in §6sulfuric acid§r to release carbon dioxide and leaves behind §6silicon dioxide§r in a batch reactor. (75%% yield)%n%nAluminium is separated from the solution with §6potassium sulfate §rto form a§6 beryllium sulfate solution§r and §bpotassium alum (KAl(SO4)2)§r in a batch reactor.%n%nIron and chromium impurities are removed with calcium carbonate (calcite), forming gypsum, iron (III) hydroxide, and chromium (III) hydroxide in a batch reactor.%n%n§2Beryllium hydroxide§r is precipitated with §9sodium hydroxide§r in a batch reactor. Optionally, add EDTA to boost the yield from 75%% to 100%%.%n%n§lSpecialized: §r%nAt a higher voltage, you can §6directly convert beryl to chlorinated beryl in a reaction furnace§r using carbon and chlorine.%n%nUsing a distillation tower, this mixture of chlorides is separated into silicon tetrachloride, aluminium trichloride, and§a beryllium chloride§r.%n%nThis process has a total yield of 90%%
susy.quest.db.251.title=005 | 硼
susy.quest.db.251.desc=§6Element§r: Boron (B)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 5%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 10.81 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 2349 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 4200 K%n§6Properties§r: Boron is a metalloid with strong chemical resistance. It is used in various industries, including agriculture (as a micronutrient), ceramics, and semiconductors.%n%n§lPrimitive:§r §6Roast ores to form Sodium Tetraborate.%n%n§613 Sodium Tetraborate Dust + 2,000 L Distilled Water   2,000 L Borate Liquor + 1 tiny pile of clay (Mixer)%n%n2,000 L Borate Liquor + 2,000 L Hydrochloric Acid   28 Boric Acid + 2,000 L Salt Water (CSTR)%n%n14 Boric Acid   3,000 L Steam + 5 Boron Trioxide (Roaster)%n%n5 Boron Trioxide + 3 Magnesium -> 2 Amorphous Boron + 6 Magnesium Oxide (Roaster)%n%n2 Amorphous Boron   1 Boron Dust (Centrifuge)%n%n§l§r§lUniversal: §rDirect electrolysis of B2O3 to form elemental boron.%n%n§67 Boric Acid + 4,000 L Hydrofluoric acid   1,000 L Tetrafluoroboric Acid (Mixer)%n%n1,000 L Tetrafluoroborate Solution + 6 Potassium Carbonate   1,000 L Potassium Tetrafluoroborate Solution +  1,000 L Carbon Dioxide%n%n14,000 L Potassium Tetrafluoroborate Solution   12 Potassium tetrafluoroborate + 15,000 L Steam (Roaster)%n%n144 mB molten salt (NC) + 1 Sodium Fluoride (NC) + 1 Potassium tetrafluoroborate (NC) + 5 Boron Trioxide + Iron Rod (NC) + Graphite Anode (NC) -> 2 Crude Boron Dust (Electrolytic cell)%n%n§l§r§lSpecialized: §rProduces ultrapure boron for semiconductor applications. %n%n§62 Crude Boron + 6,000 L Chlorine -> 2,000 L Boron Chloride + 1 tiny MgCl and CaCl dust (Fluidized Bed Reactor) %n%n2,000 L Boron Chloride + 6,000 L Hydrogen -> 6,000 L Gaseous Hydrogen Chloride + 2 High Purity Boron%n%n1 High Purity Boron -> 1 Boron Dust (Centrifuge) %n
susy.quest.db.252.title=006 | 碳
susy.quest.db.252.desc=§6Element§r: Carbon (C)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 6%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 12.01 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 3825 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 4300 K%n§6Properties§r: Carbon is a versatile nonmetal known for its ability to form a wide range of compounds. It is the basis of organic chemistry and is found in all known life forms.%n%n§lPrimitive:§r Pyrolyze §7Coke, Lignite Coke or Sugar§r for Carbon Black Dust.%n%n§lSpecialized: §rPyrolyze§c Methane §r§rwith §6Bismuth Dust§r to obtain Carbon Black Dust and Hydrogen Gas%n
susy.quest.db.253.title=007 | 氮
susy.quest.db.253.desc=§6Element§r: Nitrogen (N)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 7%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 14.01 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 63.15 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 77.36 K%n§6Properties§r: Nitrogen is a diatomic nonmetal and makes up the majority of Earth's atmosphere. It is used in various industrial processes and as a coolant in certain applications.%n%n§lPrimitive: §cN/A%n§6%n§l§r§lUniversal:§r Combine §3Alumina§r and §8Graphite§r in a §cSintering Oven§r to make a §bZeolite Membrane Support§r, which can then be put into in an §cAutoclave§r along with §9Sodium Hydroxide, Sodium Silicate, Sodium Aluminate, and Distilled Water§r to make a §7Zeolite Membrane§r.%n%nPressure Swing Adsorption of Air through this membrane can be used to make industrial quantities of §bNitrogen§r and Oxygen.%n%n§lSpecialized:§r §cCryogenic distillation [WIP]%n
susy.quest.db.254.title=008 | 氧
susy.quest.db.254.desc=§6Element§r: Oxygen (O)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 8%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 16.00 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 54.36 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 90.20 K%n§6Properties§r: Oxygen is a highly reactive nonmetal and a vital §6Element§r for sustaining life. It is used in various industries, including medical applications and combustion processes.%n%n§lPrimitive:§r%nElectrolyze Water to get Hydrogen and Oxygen.%n%n§lUniversal:§r Combine §3Alumina§r and §8Graphite§r in a §cSintering Oven§r to make a §bZeolite Membrane Support§r, which can then be put into in an §cAutoclave§r along with §9Sodium Hydroxide, Sodium Silicate, Sodium Aluminate, and Distilled Water§r to make a §7Zeolite Membrane§r.%n%nPressure Swing Adsorption of Air through this membrane can be used to make industrial quantities of Nitrogen and §bOxygen§r. %n%n§lSpecialized:%n§rCryogenic distillation [§cWIP§r]
susy.quest.db.255.title=009 | 氟
susy.quest.db.255.desc=§6Element§r: Fluorine (F)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 9%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 19.00 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 53.53 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 85.03 K%n§6Properties§r: Fluorine is a highly reactive halogen known for its strong oxidizing properties§r. It is used in various industries, including the production of fluoropolymers and pharmaceuticals.%n%n§lPrimitive: §r%n%n§lUniversal: §r3 Fluorite Dust + 1,000 L Sulfuric Acid → 6 Calcium Sulfate + 2,000 L Hydrogen Fluoride (Batch Reactor)%n1,000 L Hydrogen Fluoride + 1,152 L Liquid Potassium Fluoride (NC) + 1 Platinum Rod (NC) + 1 Nickel Rod (NC) → 1,000L Hydrogen + 1,000L Fluorine (Electrolytic Cell)%n%n
susy.quest.db.256.title=010 | 氖
susy.quest.db.256.desc=§6Element§r: Neon (Ne)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 10%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 20.18 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 24.56 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 27.07 K%n§6Properties§r: Neon is a noble gas known for its bright, colorful light emissions. It is used in advertising signs, as a coolant in cryogenics, and in some specialized lighting.%n
susy.quest.db.257.title=019 | 钾
susy.quest.db.257.desc=§6Element§r: Potassium (K)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 19%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 39.10 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 336.53 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 1032 K%n§6Properties§r: Potassium is an alkali metal highly reactive with water. It is used in fertilizers, soaps, and in the production of some medications and chemical§ls.%n%nPrimitive:§r%nElectrolyzing molten§7 Rock Salt§r under a§7 graphite electrode§r makes§9 Potassium §rand §2Chlorine§r§r.%n%n§lUniversal: §r§c§r§6Wood Ash§r can be centrifuged to make §aPotassium Carbonate Solution§r, which is then distilled to make Potassium Carbonate.%nPotassium Carbonate can be roasted in Hydrochloric Acid to make §7Rock Salt solution§r, which is electrolyzed to make potassium hydroxide.%n%n§lSpecialized: §r§cN/A%n§r§c%n
susy.quest.db.258.title=012 | 镁
susy.quest.db.258.desc=§6Element§r: Magnesium (Mg)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 12%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 24.31 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 923 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 1380 K%n§6Properties§r: Magnesium is an alkaline earth metal known for its lightness and high strength-to-weight ratio. It is used in alloys, pyrotechnics, and as a component in some medication§s.%n%n§lPrimitive: §r§cN/A§r%n%n§lUniversal: §rCarnallite can be obtained by sifting a Halide Evaporite deposit. Evaporite deposits can be found in deserts, mostly.%n%nCarnallite can be leached in a Mixer to make Carnallite Leach.%nCarnallite Leach can be crystallized to make Magnesium Chloride.%nMolten Magnesium Chloride can be electrolyzed to make Magn§l§resium.%n%n§lSpecialized: §r§cN/A§r%n%n
susy.quest.db.259.title=011 | 钠
susy.quest.db.259.desc=§b§6Element§r: Sodium (Na)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 11%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 22.99 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 370.87 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 1156 K%n§6Properties§r: Sodium is an alkali metal known for its high reactivity. It is used in various industries, including the production of chemicals, as a coolant, and in the manufacture of batteries.%n%n§lPrimitive:§r%nElectrolyzing molten§7 Salt§r under a§7 graphite electrode§r makes§9 Sodium §rand §2Chlorine§r%n%n§lUniversal: §r§c§9Sodium Hydroxide §rcan be electrolyzed for Sodium, Oxygen and Hydrogen.%n%n§lSpecialized: §r§cN/A%n§r§c
susy.quest.db.260.title=013 | 铝
susy.quest.db.260.desc=§6Element§r: Aluminium (Al)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 13%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 26.98 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 933.47 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 2792 K%n§6Properties§r: Aluminium is a lightweight and corrosion-resistant metal. It is widely used in construction, packaging, transportation, and various industrial applications.%n%n§lPrimitive: §o§cN/A%n%n§l§r§lUniversal: §rBauxite is dissolved in hot alkali to form sodium aluminate. Gallium is also dissolved in this process, and various metal hydroxides and oxides remain behind as §cred mud§r. Red mud can be further processed to yield base metal oxides such as Fe2O3 or TiO2. %n%nNext, the liquor is returned to neutral pH by bubbling carbon dioxide to precipitate aluminium hydroxide.%n%n§lSpecialized:§r Modern aluminium purification can be accomplished with the Hall-Héroult process. This uses an electrolytic cell with a steel cathode and graphite anode in a solution of alumina in molten cryolite. Check Chapter 2 for more info.
susy.quest.db.261.title=014 | 硅
susy.quest.db.261.desc=§6Element§r: Silicon (Si)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 14%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 28.09 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1687 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 3538 K%n§6Properties§r: Silicon is a metalloid known for its semiconducting §6Properties§r. It is used extensively in the electronics industry for integrated circuits and solar cell production.%n%n§lPrimitive: §r§cN/A%n§r%n§lUniversal: §r§6Silicon Dioxide §rcan be centrifuged from sand or flint.%n%nWhen silicon dioxide is §croasted§r with coke it undergoes a chemical reaction to produce§6 silicon carbide§r. %n%nSilicon carbide can then be §carc-furnaced§r to obtain§6 silicon.%n§r%n§lSpecialized: §6Silicon §rreacts with §3chlorine §rto produce §6silicon tetrachloride §rin a roaster.%n%nThe resulting SiCl4 undergoes §cpurification in a distillery§r, yielding purified SiCl4.%n%nHigh purity silicon is obtained by reacting Zinc dust with the purified SiCl4 in a§c roaster§r.%n%n
susy.quest.db.262.title=015 | 磷
susy.quest.db.262.desc=§6Element§r: Phosphorus (P)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 15%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 30.97 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 317.30 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 553 K%n§6Properties§r: Phosphorus is a nonmetal essential for life and found in DNA, RNA, and ATP. It is used in fertilizers, detergents, and in the production of matches and fireworks.%n%n§lPrimitive:§r §7Bone Meal§r can be autoclaved to make §6Tricalcium Phosphate§r. %nIt's reacted with §6Sulfuric Acid §rto make§6 Monocalcium Phosphate§r, which is then roasted to make §6Calcium Phosphite§r.%nCalcium Phosphite is roasted with Carbon to make §6White Phosphorus§r.%n%n§lUniversal:§r §2Fluorapatite or Chlorapatite §rdusts can be smelted with Sand and Carbon in an ERF to make large amounts of §6White Phosphorus§r.%n§l%nSpecialized: §rPhosphorus can be autoclaved to get a High Purity Phosphorus Vapor, which is distilled and then solidified to get §6High Purity Phosphorus§r.
susy.quest.db.263.title=016 | 硫
susy.quest.db.263.desc=§6Element§r: Sulfur (S)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 16%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 32.07 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 388.36 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 717.82 K%n§6Properties§r: Sulfur is a multivalent nonmetal known for its yellow color and distinct odor. It is used in the production of sulfuric acid, vulcanization of rubber, and in fertilizers.%n%n§lPrimitive: §rRoast §6Pyrite dust§r to get §6Sulfur dust§r and Iron III Sulfate dust%n%n§lAdvanced: §r%n%nHydrogen Sulfide can be reacted with Oxygen or Air in the Reaction Furnace to obtain §6Sulfur dust and Uncatalyzed Sulfurous Gases§r, which can be used in the Reaction Furnace again with §bAlumina Catalyst Bed§r to recover §6Sulfur dust§r. %n%nIt is noted that both of these recipes can be done in the same Reaction Furnace.%n%nSources of §6Hydrogen Sulfide§r are Sour Gas, which is a byproduct of the distillation of treated oil fractions (Diesel, Refinery Gas, Gasoline, Natural Gas, Fuel Oil, Naphtha and Kerosene), and ores that contain §6Sulfur§r.
susy.quest.db.264.title=017 | 氯
susy.quest.db.264.desc=§6Element§r: Chlorine (Cl)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 17%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 35.45 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 171.65 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 239.11 K%n§6Properties§r: Chlorine is a highly reactive halogen used as a disinfectant, in the production of PVC, and in various industrial processes, including water treatment and bleaching.%n%n§lPrimitive:§r Electrolyze§6 Liquid Salt §rto get§3 Sodium Dust§r and§a Chlorine§r§r%n%n§lSpecialized:§r Electrolyze §7Salt Water§r to get §aChlorine §rand various byproducts.
susy.quest.db.265.title=018 | 氩
susy.quest.db.265.desc=§6Element§r: Argon (Ar)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 18%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 39.95 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 83.80 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 87.30 K%n§6Properties§r: Argon is a noble gas known for its inertness. It is used in various applications, including welding, lighting, and as a protective gas in industrial processes.%n
susy.quest.db.266.title=020 | 钙
susy.quest.db.266.desc=§6Element§r: Calcium (Ca)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 20%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 40.08 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1115 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 1757 K%n§6Properties§r: Calcium is an alkaline earth metal essential for the human body and found in bones and teeth. It is used in construction, as a dietary supplement, and in the production of steel.%n%n§lPrimitive: §r§cN/A%n%n§r§lUniversal:§r Ammonia can be combined with Hydrochloric Acid to get §6Ammonium Chloride Solution§r, which is distilled to get §bAmmonium Chloride§r.	%nAmmonium Chloride can be combined with Quicklime to get §7Calcium Chloride§r, which is melted and then electrolyzed to get §bCalcium§r.%n%n§lSpecialized:§r§c §rMake High Purity Calcium by using a §cVacuum Distillation Tower§r.
susy.quest.db.267.title=021 | 钪
susy.quest.db.267.desc=§6Element§r: Scandium (Sc)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 21%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 44.96 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1814 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 3109 K%n§6Properties§r: Scandium is a transition metal with high strength and heat resistance. It is used in aerospace components, high-intensity lamps, and in some sports equipment.%n
susy.quest.db.268.title=022 | 钛
susy.quest.db.268.desc=§6Element§r: Titanium (Ti)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 22%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 47.87 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1941 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 3560 K%n§6Properties§r: Titanium is a transition metal known for its high strength, low density, and corrosion resistance. It is used in aerospace applications, medical implants, and in the production of durable goods.%n%n§lPrimitive: §r§cN/A%n%n§r§lUniversal: §rTitanium has 2 sources at this stage of the game: §6Vanadiferous Titanomagnetite,§f and §cIlmenite.§f Those are sourced from the Mining Drill only.%n%nWhat you'll want to do is process those dusts into Rutile. Both ores have different processing routes to get to Rutile, but Ilmenite is significantly easier to turn into Rutile, needing only 1 fluidized bed reactor step.%n%nNext, you'll want to react the Rutile with Coke Dust/Carbon Black Dust and chlorine in a Fluidized Bed Reactor, for Gaseous Titanium Tetrachloride.%n%nAfter several steps of purification, you should have normal Titanium Tetrachloride.%n%nPutting this normal Titanium Tetrachloride in an ERF with magnesium will give you a Titanium Sponge, which is just a few steps away from Titanium Ingots. You'll need better coils than just Cupronickel Coils for this though.%n%n§lSpecialized:%n%n§6§r§c§r§aTitanium, Zirconium and Hafnium§r all rely on the same process to obtain high purity versions. %n%nFirst, react the metal dust with iodine to obtain the iodide. Next, use the §aCVD Unit§r with a heated tungsten stick to decompose the iodide back into the metal, which has been purified during the process.%n
susy.quest.db.269.title=023 | 钒
susy.quest.db.269.desc=§6Element§r: Vanadium (V)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 23%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 50.94 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 2183 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 3680 K%n§6Properties§r: Vanadium is a transition metal with excellent structural §6Properties§r. It is used in the production of steel, as a catalyst, and in energy storage systems.%n%n§l§lPrimitive:§r React Vanadinite dust and Salt or Soda Ash dust in Reaction Furnace to get Salt Roasted Vanadinite Dust. %n%nCentrifuge the dust with Water to get Leached Salt Roasted Vanadinite Dust (this can be processed for lead) and Sodium Vanadate Solution.%n%nReact Sodium Vanadate Solution with Ammonium Chloride dust to get Ammonium Metavanadate Dust. %n%nRoast the dust to get Vanadium Pentoxide Dust and Ammonia. React Vanadium Pentoxide Dust with High Purity Calcium dust to get Vanadium Dust and Quicklime dust.%n%n§lAdvanced:§r%n%n  §cVanadiferous Titanomagnetite will be abbreviated as V-T.%n          Vanadium/Titanium will be abbreviated as V/Ti.§r%n%nMix V-T dust with Distilled Water to get Impure V-T Slurry. %n%nThe slurry will be separated into V-T Slurry in the Floth Flotation Tank, requiring n-Octylamine and Methyl Isobutyl Carbinol as non-consumable input fluid. %n%nCentrifuge V-T Slurry to get V-T Concentrate Dust. %n%nRoast the V-T Concentrate Dust in a Rotary Kiln with Carbon Black Dust and Dolomite dust to get V/Ti Rich Pig Iron.%n%nSmelt V/Ti Rich Pig Iron with Oxygen in an Advanced Arc Furnace to get V/Ti-Rich Slag and Steel Ingot as a byproduct. %n%nPulverize the slag to get V/Ti-Rich Slag Dust. Roast V/Ti-Rich Slag Dust in a Rotary Kiln with Soda Ash dust to obtain Alkaline V/Ti Slag Dust. %n%nCentrifuge Alkaline V/Ti Slag Dust to get Sodium Vanadate Solution and Titania Slag Dust. Process Sodium Vanadate Solution like Primitive steps. %n%nNote: Titania Slag Dust can be used as a source for Titanium.%n
susy.quest.db.270.title=024 | 铬
susy.quest.db.270.desc=§6Element§r: Chromium (Cr)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 24%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 52.00 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 2180 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 2944 K%n§6Properties§r: Chromium is a transition metal known for its corrosion resistance. It is used in Stainless Steel production, as a decorative coating, and in the manufacturing of alloys.%n%n%n§6Chromite§r can be roasted in the §cRotary Kiln§r with Soda Ash, Oxygen, and Natural Gas to get a§c Sodium Chromate Mixture§r. This mixture is then separated by dissolving Sodium Chromate in Distilled water, leaving behind§7 Iron III Oxide§r.%n%nThe Sodium Chromate Solution can react with §6Sulfur Trioxide§r to make§6 Sodium Dichromate Solution§r. Process the solution in a §cCrystallizer§r to get Sodium Dichromate and Diluted Sodium Sulfate Solution. The solution can be §cdistilled§r and then §croasted§r to fully recycle the §6Sulfur Trioxide§r. The §6Sodium Oxide§r can be processed into §6Sodium Hydroxide Solution§r and combined with Carbon Dioxide in a §cBubble Column Reactor§r to reclaim half of your §6Soda Ash§r.%n%nFrom here, you have two options.%n%nThe first option is to react Sodium Dichromate with Sulfuric Acid to obtain §cChromium Trioxide§r, and Sodium Sulfate Solution. Roast §cChromium Trioxide§r to obtain Chromium III Oxide and Oxygen.%n%nAlternatively, you can roast Sodium Dichromate dust with Carbon to get a Chromium-Soda Ash Mixture. You can then dissolve the Soda Ash in the mixture with water, leaving behind Chromium III Oxide. §cBoth options are viable as either one will allow you to fully recover the other half of your Soda Ash.§r%n%nThen, react the Chromium III Oxide with Aluminium to get Chromium dust and Alumina.
susy.quest.db.271.title=025 | 锰
susy.quest.db.271.desc=§6Element§r: Manganese (Mn)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 25%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 54.94 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1519 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 2334 K%n§6Properties§r: Manganese is a transition metal used for superconductors and as a catalyst. It is also a necessary nutrient for humans and plays a role in various biological processes.%n%n§lPrimitive§r: %nPyrolusite can be smelted with Coke and tiny piles of calcite to create small piles of Manganese.%n%n§lUniversal§r:%nRhodochrosite can be roasted to create Manganese Oxide dust, which can be roasted with Coke to create small piles of Manganese dust.%n%n§lSpecialized§r:%nPyrolusite can be reduced with Natural Gas, CO, Hydrogen or Fuel Oil to create Manganese Oxide in a Reaction Furnace.%nManganese Oxide is leached with Sulfuric Acid to create Crude Manganese II Sulfate solution, which needs to be reacted with Sodium Hydroxide and then put through an Electrolytic Cell to get Manganese.
susy.quest.db.272.title=026 | 铁
susy.quest.db.272.desc=§6Element§r: Iron (Fe)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 26%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 55.85 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1811 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 3134 K%n§6Properties§r: Iron is a transition metal with excellent strength and magnetism. It is used in construction, manufacturing, and as a core component in many alloys.%n%n§lPrimitive: §rWhen iron ores are smelted in a Primitive Blast Furnace with coke, iron with a high carbon content (pig iron) is produced. Pig Iron then needs to be smelted to make iron.%n%n§lUniversal: §rThe same process, but done in an Electric Resistance Furnace.%n%n§lSpecialized:§r Steel needs to be reacted with Carbon Monoxide in a Reaction Furnace to produce Crude Iron Pentacarbonyl, which needs to be distilled to make§6 Iron Pentacarbonyl§r.%n%nIron Pentacarbonyl then goes in the batch reactor to make §7High Purity Iron.%n%n%n%n
susy.quest.db.273.title=027 | 钴
susy.quest.db.273.desc=§6Element§r: Cobalt (Co)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 27%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 58.93 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1768 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 3200 K%n§6Properties§r: Cobalt is a transition metal used in the production of magnetic materials, rechargeable batteries, and as a catalyst in the chemical industry.%n
susy.quest.db.274.title=028 | 镍
susy.quest.db.274.desc=§6Element§r: Nickel (Ni)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 28%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 58.69 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1728 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 3186 K%n§6Properties§r: Nickel is a transition metal known for its corrosion resistance and high electrical conductivity. It is used in alloys, batteries, and in the production of stainless steel.%n
susy.quest.db.275.title=029 | 铜
susy.quest.db.275.desc=§6Element§r: Copper (Cu)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 29%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 63.55 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1357.77 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 2835 K%n§6Properties§r: Copper is a transition metal with excellent thermal and electrical conductivity. It is used in electrical wiring, plumbing, and as a component in various alloys.%n%n§lPrimitive: §rCopper is found in §6Chalcopyrite, Chalcocite, Malachite, Bornite, Tetrahedrite, §ror §6Copper Ore§r deposits.%n%n§lUniversal: §rYou can use §cfroth flotation §rand advanced processing to obtain §l§c§l>100%%§r copper yields from ore and valuable byproducts such as the platinum group metals, §6selenium, tellurium, molybdenum, and rhenium §r(to be implemented)%n%nTo process chalcopyrite, chalcocite, and bornite, use froth flotation with S.E.X. to obtain §6copper concentrate §rto first double the yield from the ore.%n%nSmelt the copper concentrate in an ERF with a §areductant (natural gas)§r and oxygen to produce §6copper matte§r and to remove some sulfur dioxide.%n%nTake the copper matte and smelt again with oxygen to remove the rest of the sulfur from the concentrate to make §6blister copper and remove impurities such as bismuth, antimony, arsenic, and tin§r.%n%nTurn the blister copper into plates to use for electrolysis, which produces nickel and anode slime as a byproduct. The anode slime can be further processed for selenium, tellurium, and the platinum group metals.%n%nFor §2malachite§r, a different flotation agent, octyl hydroxamate is used. Leach the product of froth flotation with sulfuric acid and optionally add hydrogen peroxide to recover some iron and boost yield. This produces copper sulfate, which can be directly electrolyzed to copper.%n§l%nSpecialized: §cN/A
susy.quest.db.276.title=030 | 锌
susy.quest.db.276.desc=§6Element§r: Zinc (Zn)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 30%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 65.38 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 692.68 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 1180 K%n§6Properties§r: Zinc is a transition metal known for its corrosion resistance. It is used in galvanizing processes, as a dietary supplement, and in the production of alloys.%n%n§lPrimitive: §rSmelt §bsphalerite ore §r§rin a furnace to get Zinc.%n%n§lUniversal:§r Sphalerite can be roasted to get Zinc Oxide.%nZinc Oxide is roasted again to get Crude Zinc.%nCrude Zinc goes into the distillation tower to obtain Cadmium Rich Zinc and a variety of other metals. %nCadmium Rich Zinc goes into the tower again to get Zinc and Cadmium.%n%n§lSpecialized: §rUse the §aZinc Cementation Slurry §rprocess to get Zinc.
susy.quest.db.277.title=031 | 镓
susy.quest.db.277.desc=§6Element§r: Gallium (Ga)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 31%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 69.72 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 302.91 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 2477 K%n§6Properties§r: Gallium is a post-transition metal with a low §cMelting Point§r. It is used in semiconductors, LEDs, and as a component in some medical imaging devices.%n%n§lPrimitive: §rGallium can be centrifuged from sphalerite.%n%n§lUniversal: §r§cWIP%n%n§l§r§lSpecialized: §rGallium can be reacted with Chlorine to form Crude Gallium Trichloride.%nCrude Gallium Trichloride needs to be distilled into Gallium Trichloride.%nGallium Trichloride can be reacted with Hydrogen to form High Purity Gallium.%n%nOr, if you don't want to do the whole process, you can use a Vacuum Distillation Tower.
susy.quest.db.278.title=032 | 锗
susy.quest.db.278.desc=§6Element§r: Germanium (Ge)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 32%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 72.63 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1211.40 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 3106 K%n§6Properties§r: Germanium is a metalloid used in semiconductors and fiber-optic systems. It has applications in infrared optics, solar cells, and in some chemotherapy drugs.%n
susy.quest.db.279.title=033 | 砷
susy.quest.db.279.desc=§6Element§r: Arsenic (As)%n§bAtomic Number§r: 33%n§aAtomic Mass§r: 74.92 amu%n§cMelting Point§r: 1090 K%n§5Boiling Point§r: 887 K%n§6Properties§r: Arsenic is a metalloid with both metallic and nonmetallic properties. It is used in certain pesticides, wood preservatives, and in the production of semiconductors.%n%n§c§r§lPrimitive§r: Sperrylite, Cobaltite, Arsenopyrite, and Realgar §rcan be put through an Electric Resistance Furnace with oxygen to create §6small piles of Arsenic Trioxide.%n%nThis can be then §6arc-furnaced §rwith some §6Carbon §rto create pure Arsenic.%n%n§lUniversal: §r%n§6Proustite§r can allow for arsenic separation using an alkaline leach to create Arsenic III Sulfide.%n%n§6Arsenopyrite/Cobaltit§r§6e§r may also be leached with acid to create Arsenic V Oxide.%n%nProustite can be leached with Sodium Thiosulfate to create a leach, which can be reacted with Sodium Sulfate to make Thiosulfate Thioarsenite.%nThis can then be reacted with Iron III Chloride to make Iron Arsenite.%n%n§lSpecialized:%n§r§65 Arsenic Trichloride + 6,500 mB Hydrogen Chloride -> 2,000 L Crude Arsenic Trichloride + 3,000 L Water (roaster)%n%nCrude Arsenic Trichloride -> Arsenic Trichloride (distillery)%n%n3,000 L Hydrogen + 1,000 L Arsenic Trichloride -> 1 High Purity Arsenic + 3,000 Hydrogen Chloride
susy.quest.db.280.title=034 | 硒
