susy.quest.db.850.title=Charon
susy.quest.db.850.desc=No Description
susy.quest.db.851.title=Phobos
susy.quest.db.851.desc=No Description
susy.quest.db.852.title=Deimos
susy.quest.db.852.desc=§aIMPORTANT INFORMATION§r --%n%n- Surface gravity: 0.0003g (0.003m/s^2)%n%n- Day length: 30.3 hours%n%n- Atmosphere: §c§fNone%n%n- Orbital period: 30.3 Earth hours%n%n- Orbits: Mars%n%n- Satellites: None%n%n- Rare resources: [WIP]%n%n-------------------------%n%n§aDeimos§r is the smallest moon of §cMars§f. It has extremely small escape velocity (6m/s), making it easy to throw items into areocentric orbit. %n%nDiscovered by A. Hall in 1877.
susy.quest.db.853.title=Haumea
susy.quest.db.853.desc=No Description
susy.quest.db.854.title=Makemake
susy.quest.db.854.desc=No Description
