susy.quest.db.859.title=Oberon
susy.quest.db.859.desc=No Description
susy.quest.db.860.title=Storage Racks
susy.quest.db.860.desc=§6Storage Racks (Chest) §fcan hold 81 stacks of different items. %n%nA unique feature of them however, is that when they are stacked on top of one another, they share inventories.%n%nThe Chest version allows you to store more than just one item, and it also has a search bar! It's (very) primitive Applied Energistics!%n%nThe Crate version only lets you store 64 stacks of 1 item, but it is useful too.
susy.quest.db.861.title=Camo Bench
susy.quest.db.861.desc=The§a Camo Bench §rcan be used to change the texture of Techguns armor to your favorite one. The bench should work with any Techguns armor with the exception of Ranger armor.
susy.quest.db.862.title=橡胶树
susy.quest.db.862.desc=现在你可以砍断一整棵树了，你应该会找到一些§6橡胶树§f，它会掉落一些§6粘性树脂§f。橡胶树在整个游戏中都非常有用，所以记得留几个树苗。%n%n现在你可以用它合成几个火把（如果你忘了看那些小贴士）。
susy.quest.db.863.title=Gelatin
susy.quest.db.863.desc=To produce §bGelatin§r, either §7Leather§r or §7Bone Meal§r can be dissolved in §7Hydrochloric Acid§r to produce §6Collagen§r. This is then washed with §9Sodium Hydroxide Solution§r to produce §6Treated Collagen§r, which is then dissolved in heated water and allowed to cool.
susy.quest.db.864.title=Ethylene, Ethylene Oxide, and Acetaldehyde
susy.quest.db.864.desc=§aEthylene Oxide§r is produced from Ethylene and Oxygen over a silver catalyst bed. This can be used for thermobaric weaponry, but is also a useful chemical intermediate for the production of §bEthylene Glycol.§r Ethylene Glycol is important for the production of §3Polyethylene Terephthalate (PET)§r, which is required for photomasks in the production of circuitry.%n%n§cAcetaldehyde,§r another chemical required for photomasks, is also derived from Ethylene and Oxygen, but requires a §ePlatinum §rcatalyst.%n%n§nThis is the start of the §c§l§nrubylith§f§n questline. It is recommended to §lbatch craft§f§n the materials listed!
susy.quest.db.865.title=Dimethyl Terephthalate
susy.quest.db.865.desc=To produce §3Dimethyl Terephthalate,§r Xylene is progressively oxidized using Oxygen, p-Toluate, and a Cobalt catalyst in a complicated process (more details in JEI). You should already have §bEthylene Glycol, §rand §cCobalt Acetate §rcan be produced with Acetic Acid and Cobalt Oxide.
susy.quest.db.866.title=Rubylith
susy.quest.db.866.desc=§cRubylith§r is composed of a PET backfilm glued to a red photoemulsion-coated top sheet. This sheet is produced with a thin film of polyethylene, some photoemulsion, and some red dye.%n%n%nOnce you make some rubylith, cut it into the patterns needed for circuits and then expose a silver-halide coated glass plate in a §6UV Light Box§r through the §erubylith stencil§r.
susy.quest.db.867.title=Benzenediazonium Chloride
susy.quest.db.867.desc=§2Benzenediazonium chloride§r is the photoinitiator used in the acrylic photoemulsion. This material dissociates in UV light and initiates a photopolymerization reaction in §aTrimethylolpropane Triacrylate§r. To produce it, take §aAniline§r and react it with Sodium Nitrite (produced by roasting Sodium Nitrate, which comes from NaOH and Nitric Acid) and hydrogen chloride. %n%n§a§rAt LV, the only way to get §aAniline §ris processing Coal Tar Oil, which is probably still the best one.
susy.quest.db.868.title=Acrylic Photoinitiator
susy.quest.db.868.desc=Finally, combine the §a§2TMPTA, §bgelatin, §rand §abenzenediazonium chloride, §rto produce the acrylic photoinitiator for §crubylith.
susy.quest.db.869.title=Trimethylolpropane Triacrylate
susy.quest.db.869.desc=§aTrimethylolpropane Triacrylate (TMPTA)§r is the main chemical used in the photopolymerization of the photoemulsion when §crubylith§r is exposed to UV light, resulting in hardening. %n%nTo produce it, you first must produce §7§6trimethylolpropane§r, which is produced from the aldol condensation of formaldehyde and butyraldehyde, catalyzed with sodium hydroxide solution.%nButyraldehyde may be produced in this voltage through the hydrogenation of crotonaldehyde, which is produced from the aldol condensation of acetaldehyde with itself, also catalyzed with a sodium hydroxide solution.%n§b%nAcrylic acid§r, the other component in TMPTA, is produced from acetylene, carbon monoxide, water, and a cobalt-nickel bromide catalyst.%n%nFinally, combine these two components with sulfuric acid with heating to produce TMPTA.
susy.quest.db.870.title=Benzene
susy.quest.db.870.desc=The most convenient way to produce benzene is to simply react phenol with zinc at this voltage. Later on, BTEX can be produced from naphtha and distilled for benzene.
susy.quest.db.871.title=Aniline
susy.quest.db.871.desc=There are two routes for producing §aAniline§r: §cNitrobenzene§r and §5Pyridine§r purification.%n%nTo produce §cNitrobenzene,§r simply mix §eNitration Mixture§r with Benzene to produce an acidic mixture, which can be further distilled for Nitrobenzene. Aniline§r can then be produced by reacting §cNitrobenzene§r with Hydrogen, catalyzed by §bPalladium§r. Both §cNitrobenzene§r and §aAniline§r are useful intermediates used in a wide array of chemical processes. However, this route requires an HV fluid compressor and Palladium.%n%nIf you don't have that set up yet, you can produce §aAniline§r through §5Pyridine§r purification. Specifically, by making Impure Pyridine with distilled Coal Tar Oil and Furfural, §aAniline§r is produced as a byproduct. This route has relatively low voltage requirements but it is more complicated. You do get §6B.T.E.X.§r from doing this route, at the very least, which will help you with your Benzene and Xylene.%n
susy.quest.db.872.title=Polyethylene Terephthalate (PET)
susy.quest.db.872.desc=The earliest way in which §2polyethylene terephthalate (PET)§r is produced is through the combination of §3dimethyl terephthalate§r and §bethylene glycol§r with a §ccobalt acetate§r polymerization catalyst.%n%nYou should already have §bethylene glycol, §rand §ccobalt acetate §rcan be produced with acetic acid and cobalt oxide.
susy.quest.db.873.title=Xylene
susy.quest.db.873.desc=The earliest way to produce p-Xylene, which is required for §2Polyethylene Terephthalate§r, is to react Benzene with §dChloromethane§r, which can be produced by chlorinating §6Methane§r or §6Methanol§r and distilling it. This is done with an §bAluminium Chloride§r catalyst. The resultant mixture of o/p (ortho/para) Xylene can then be separated by distillation.
susy.quest.db.874.title=Upgraded Lubricants
susy.quest.db.874.desc=There are §63 tiers§r of lubricant upgrades, similar to diesel, kerosene, and gasoline. The first tier requires antifoam, demulsifier, and antiwear additives. The second tier requires pour point depressants, antirust additives, and detergents. The third tier requires chelating agents, corrosion inhibitors, and antioxidants.%n%nUnlike fuel additives, lubricant additives are not their own material.%n%n§9Antifoam additive §rproduction is outlined in the upgrade fuels quests.%n§§Calcium dinonylnapthalene sulfonate and polyethylene glycol is a §1demulsifier.§r%nMolybdenum dialkyldithiophosphate, zinc bis(diethyldithiocarbamate), tricresyl phosphate, and zinc dialkyldithiophosphate are §2antiwear additives.%n§rEthylene-propylene copolymer, hydrogenated styrene-isoprene rubber, hydrogenated styrene-butadiene rubber, polyisobutene, and polyalkyl methacrylate are §3pour point depressants.%n§rCalcium didodecylbenzene sulfonate and 4-nonylphenoxyacetic acid are §4antirust additives.§r%n§rCalcium phenate, calcium dodecylbenzene sulfonate, calcium salicylate, and polyisobutene succinic anhydride (PIBSA) are §4§5detergents.%n§rN,N'-bis(salicylidene)-1,2-propanediamine (SALPN), and N,N'-bis(salicylidene)ethylenediamine (SALEN) are §5§6chelating agents.%n§rBenzotriazole and mercaptobenzothiazole are §7corrosion inhibitors.§r%nN-phenyl-1-naphthylamine, butylated hydroxytoluene, dimethyl-tert-butylphenol, and di-tert-butylphenol are §8antioxidants.%n
susy.quest.db.875.title=The Demon Core
susy.quest.db.875.desc=No Description
susy.quest.db.876.title=Uranium Production
susy.quest.db.876.desc=Uranium can be extracted from pitchblende, carnotite, or in small quantities from rare earth ores. %n%nTo produce uranium from carnotite, dissolve §bcarnotite§r in §d§chot sulfuric acid. §rThe resultant solution is then reduced with iron and calcite to transform the dissolved uranium into a extractable state. This mixture is subsequently contacted with uranium extraction mixture (D2EHPA, TBP, and kerosene).%n%nAfter the liquid-liquid extraction, the resultant solution containing vanadium and §auranium§r is selectively stripped with dilute sulfuric acid to remove the vanadium content. Next, soda ash solution is used to strip the §auranium§r out as §auranyl carbonate§r. The resultant stripped solution contains some particles of aluminium and iron carbonate, which is sifted out. The solution is then acidified with sulfuric acid to produce §auranyl sulfate§r. Ammonia is then introduced to precipitate §eammonium diuranate§r, a form of yellowcake. This is then calcined to produce §2uranium dioxide§r, which is a precursor to uranium metal (used in EV superconductors) and uranium hexafluoride, which is required for U235 enrichment.%n%nTo produce uranium from pitchblende, dissolve the ore in diluted sulfuric acid and oxidize with sodium perchlorate. Next, vacuum separate the leach, then pass it through an ion exchange column. The beads are stripped with sodium sulfate, and extracted with the uranium extraction mixture. The steps to produce yellowcake from here are essentially the same.
susy.quest.db.877.title=Silicon Wafer
susy.quest.db.877.desc=Polish your §6Acid-Treated Silicon Wafer§r to get a §6Silicon Wafer§r. You can now use this wafer to craft §6ICs, CPUs, RAMs,§r etc...
susy.quest.db.878.title=EV Superconductor
susy.quest.db.878.desc=Smelt and assemble the uranium triplatinum dust like you would with §7Manganese Phosphide §rto produce EV superconductors.
susy.quest.db.879.title=Uranium Triplatinum
susy.quest.db.879.desc=Uranium triplatinum is a mixture of uranium and platinum. It's that simple.
susy.quest.db.880.title=Acid-Treated Silicon Wafer
susy.quest.db.880.desc=Bathe your§6 Raw Wafer§r in §2Wafer §2Treatment Acid§r to get an §6Acid-Treated Silicon Wafer§r.
susy.quest.db.881.title=Wafer Treatment Acid
susy.quest.db.881.desc=You need to make §6Wafer Treatment Acid§r to polish your §6Wafers§r. To make §6Wafer Treatment Acid§r, mix §2§a§d§b§a§5§4§3Hydrofluoric Acid§r and §8§7Hydrochloric Acid§r. If you add §d§5§4§3§f§7Acetic Acid§r, the mixing time will go down from 30 seconds to 10 seconds.
susy.quest.db.882.title=Liquid Nitrogen
susy.quest.db.882.desc=§bNitrogen§r becomes a liquid at §c77K§r. This is low enough to activate §bMV§r superconductors.
susy.quest.db.883.title=Monorail Tracks
susy.quest.db.883.desc=If you want to stick to the §6Black Mesa§r inspired style of railroading, you will require §6monorail track segments§r. They are also required in the §6tunnel bore§r.
susy.quest.db.884.title=The Tunnel Bore
susy.quest.db.884.desc=In conjunction with improved logistics, trains also allow you to unleash the glory of tunnel boring onto the very rock you are standing on. Building the tunnelbore requires a hefty amount of resources. In return, it allows you to rapidly excavate giant areas and automatically connect distant places with monorail tracks.%n%nIn order to power the tunnel bore, you need to supply charged batteries. Additionally, you must manufacture monorail tracks that you can put into the specified slots. Lastly, if you want the tunnel bore to automatically bridge over any hole it encounters, you must supply it with concrete in the main area of the inventory.%n%nOnce this is done, it is just a matter of increasing the tunnelbore's throttle and enjoying the glory of digging away at the mountains.
susy.quest.db.885.title=Kitchen
susy.quest.db.885.desc=The §eKitchen§r will probably be your first taste of autocrafting in this entire pack! It doesn't work with multiblocks, only crafts food-related items, and requires cleaning fluid to run, but it is an exceptional way to automate away the tedium of making food every 20 minutes.%n%nThe Kitchen will accept a §eKitchen Recipe§r within the blank slot in its GUI. The Kitchen Recipe item itself, when used, will open a vaguely crafting-calculator-like GUI. If you want to automate a specific item, you place that item in the "final result" slot, and you can then use JEI to select recipes for it and each of its ingredients recursively (using the + icon).%n%nOnce the recipe is set, the Kitchen will look for the required machines directly on top of the porcelain tiles. The Kitchen will provide them with items and fluids to work through the recipe, and it even automatically sets the correct circuit. However, it will §cnot§r provide them with power. It will store the intermediate items and fluids in its input item buses and fluid hatches, so make sure to leave room in them.%n%nAs machines run in the Kitchen, it will get progressively §6dirty§r. Provide a cleaning fluid like §bDistilled Water§r or §bSodium Stearate (Soap)§r to clean it and prevent it from slowing down. The Kitchen never fully stops, but it may slow down to an arbitrary degree, especially above 10 DU (dirtiness units).%n%nThe controller does require a bit of §9Bismuth§r, so make sure you get a way of obtaining that (such as the MV Roaster) before you begin.
susy.quest.db.886.title=Methanol
susy.quest.db.886.desc=§6Wood Vinegar §rcan be distilled to §6Methanol§r, which is crucial in many chemistry productions!%n%nAlternatively, they can be produced from §7Synthetic Gas§r.
susy.quest.db.887.title=The Road to Rubylith
susy.quest.db.887.desc=You may have noticed the rather complicated questline below. It all heads towards §crubylith§r, which is essentially a really chemically complex sheet of plastic that you use to, essentially, stencil stencils.%n%nDo not worry about automating this; you will only need §66§r to get through HV! Even still, we wish you good luck.
susy.quest.db.18799598.title=浸泡壶
susy.quest.db.18799598.desc=§6浸泡壶§r可以用来... 泡点东西。目前的主要用途是把§7生石灰§r变成§7熟石灰（氢氧化钙）§r。%n%n之后还能把§4木浆§r变成§e纸屑§r，可以合成§e纸§r。
susy.quest.db.19817968.title=Shoulders of the Giants
susy.quest.db.19817968.desc=Make your forays into modern electronics fabrication with the §dEV-tier assembling machine§r, 2x faster than your HV assembling machine.
susy.quest.db.22127543.title=Going Supercritical
susy.quest.db.22127543.desc=Supercritical fluids can be produced by compressing an already compressed gas in an HV-tier fluid compressor.
susy.quest.db.24048665.title=More Acetylene
susy.quest.db.24048665.desc=Via the partial oxidation of natural gas, you can produce a mixture of gas which can be further separated into §7syngas§r and §9acetylene§r. To do this, first burn the natural gas in a reaction furnace, then quench the gas with water. Next, the §9acetylene§r is stripped with N-methyl-2-pyrrolidone. This chemical is produced from formaldehyde and acetylene itself, however it is fully recycled in the process. The remaining syngas can either be separated into hydrogen with a PSA or distilled cryogenically using technology from the HV age.
susy.quest.db.25903173.title=Brush and Commutator
susy.quest.db.25903173.desc=You will need §7brushes§r and §6commutators§r to produce LV motors. §7Brushes§r can be made from §8graphite§r (found only in the beneath) and sticky resin. After firing in a furnace, it will be ready for use. §6Commutators§r can be made from copper and stone plates with some sticky resin.
susy.quest.db.32366516.title=Industrial Concrete and Dotted Panels
susy.quest.db.32366516.desc=Does light Concrete sound §7§ounderqualified §ffor your industrial factory?%n%nThen reinforce your walls with §bIndustrial Concrete!%n%n§fYou can make industrial concrete by adding §6steel frames §fto your normal concrete as a rebar. Smooth industrial concrete is made without the addition of stone dust. Cinder blocks can also be made with just liquid concrete. These blocks can be complimented with §eDotted Panels§f, which are craftable with wrought iron.%n%nThese blocks also have variants with §bIndustrial Concrete§,, §bSmooth Industrial Concrete §fand §eDotted Panels§f having §64 §fand §bIndustrial Cinder Bricks §fhaving up to§6 6§f!
susy.quest.db.58115670.title=石炉
susy.quest.db.58115670.desc=§6石炉§r内含一个中空腔室，在燃烧过程中，材料会以受控的方式被暴露在高温环境当中（Oven与Furnace的区别）。%n%n与窑不同的是，尽管工作温度低得多，依旧可以将食物加热到所需温度，因此可用于§6烹饪§r。更好的温度控制也使得可以用来§6烘干§r，比如干燥的纤维（比晾干架快得多）。%n%n要使用石炉，你需要§a右键§r炉的上下部分来放入物品/燃料，然后点火就会开始烧制。
susy.quest.db.82655403.title=Tier 3 Armor Upgrades
susy.quest.db.82655403.desc=The third level of armor upgrades are made from boron nitride and kevlar.
susy.quest.db.90454916.title=Hot Isostatic Press
susy.quest.db.90454916.desc=When it comes to forming §csuperalloys§r, your dinky little bending machine isn't going to cut it anymore. Instead, use the §dHot Isostatic Press§r!%n%nThrough incredible amounts of pressure and resistive heating, it's able to sinter all sorts of ceramic materials.
susy.quest.db.97148971.title=简易冶炼炉
susy.quest.db.97148971.desc=§6简易冶炼炉§r是一个原始多方块熔炉，可以§4熔炼金属§r和§e制造合金§r。%n%n可用于提炼一些主要金属，例如§6铜§r，§7锡§r，§5铅§r，和§7锌§r，通过分解的方式提炼金属并除杂，例如§8气体§r或者§8炉渣§r。%n%n除此之外，还能用原料制造一些基本合金，例如§6青铜§r，§c粗青铜§r和§e黄铜§r。%n%n§6简易冶炼炉§r的速度由其§7还原剂§r决定（也就是§c燃料§r），以及冶炼所用原料的形态。一般来说，§4粉§r的处理速度最快。%n%n检查JEI页面获得更多信息。
susy.quest.db.99714588.title=Wireless Transmission
susy.quest.db.99714588.desc=The §6Wireless Signal Connector§r works as an unlimited range, cross dimensional §cSignal Wire§r. Requires an HV Sensor to craft. §a[left-click]§r with screwdriver to remove, §a[sneak+right-click]§r in air to cancel placing connection.
susy.quest.db.108292354.title=Fission Reactor Components
susy.quest.db.108292354.desc=These are some of the components you'll need for your fission reactors. %n%nThey require Zircaloy, Reactor Steel, and Inconel to produce, the third of which needs to be formed in a §cHot Isostatic Press§r.%n%nYou will probably want at least ten of each of the hatches, 20 fuel rods, coolant channels, and control rod channels, and at least a stack of reactor vessels, but I won't force you.
susy.quest.db.109945351.title=High Enriched
susy.quest.db.109945351.desc=Highly enriched uranium is very reactive and can easily overheat your reactor. Only use this fuel grade if you know what you're doing!
susy.quest.db.123835459.title=Pure Ethanol
susy.quest.db.123835459.desc=Pure anhydrous §cethanol§r can be distilled from the azeotrope with toluene or produced from the hydrogenation of acetaldehyde.
susy.quest.db.188760209.title=Lead Chamber Process
susy.quest.db.188760209.desc=The §5lead chamber process§r is an efficient method to produce §csulfuric acid§r. It is accomplished in three lead lined batch reactors. Here is a basic rundown of the process.%n%nTo start up the process, first produce some sulfuric acid from §agreen vitriol§r. Next, make some diluted sulfuric acid and feed a mixture of nitrogen dioxide, steam, and sulfur dioxide (lead chamber reaction mixture) together with water in a lead-lined chamber to produce some §4chamber acid§r, a mixture of sulfuric acid. %n%nThe resultant §bnitric oxide§r can be fed into a reactor known as the §9Gay-Lussac Tower§r with §csulfuric acid§r and air to produce §6nitrosylsulfuric acid§r. This reactor is a step in the process to help reconvert the nitric oxide back into nitrogen dioxide. The next step is to feed your two acids into the §aGlover Tower§r, which takes in the two acid mixtures and concentrates them into proper §csulfuric acid§r using air. The steam released during concentration is mixed with sulfur dioxide and nitrogen dioxide released from §6nitrosylsulfuric acid§r being oxidized then produces lead chamber reaction mixture ready to produce more §cchamber acid§r.%n%nThe final step in the process is to take some of the sulfuric acid product and divert it into the §9Gay-Lussac Tower§r to continue the cycle.
susy.quest.db.200547830.title=Germanium
susy.quest.db.200547830.desc=§7Germanium§r is a useful semiconductor material that can be used to produce transistors.
susy.quest.db.213706018.title=Rare Earth Reduction
susy.quest.db.213706018.desc=Most rare earth elements are reduced in highly resistant §3tantalum§r crucibles using high purity calcium under a protective noble gas in a reaction furnace. The HREEs typically use helium while LREEs and MREEs use argon.%n%nRare earth elements capable of reducing to the 2+ state (Sm, Eu, Yb) are reduced using lanthanum due to their higher volatilities compared to the other rare earth elements, allowing for efficient separation from lanthanum oxide.
susy.quest.db.221672823.title=Timing Specifics
susy.quest.db.221672823.desc=Most devices in Redstone Control update their state post-tick to ensure reliable timing consistency. Exceptions include: Binary Signal Unpacker, Counter, Oscilloscope, Redstone Write Socket, Signal Splitter, Signal Offset, Signal Scaler and Signal Threshold Latch, all of which update and pass their signal on instantly%nThe §6Signal Delay Line§r delays the signal exactly 1 tick.%nFor more info on timing visit the mods wiki:%n{Embed}TypeLink;https://github.com/CD4017BE/RedstoneControl/wiki/Signal-Timing;128;20;§9§nSignal Timing§r{Embed}
susy.quest.db.239028636.title=Maintaining Hydrogen Balance
susy.quest.db.239028636.desc=§bHydrogen§r is an essential resource in any oil refining operation, as it is required for §9hydrocracking§r, §edesulfurization§r, and the production of high quality fuel & lubricant feedstocks and additives. There are a variety of sources of hydrogen, listed below.%n%n- Coal pyrolysis is an excellent source of syngas, which can then be reformed and separated into hydrogen using a PSA.%n- Partial oxidation of unutilized oil fractions can also be a good source of syngas for hydrogen.%n- Steam reforming fuel gas, natural gas, and methane is another source of syngas.%n- Lastly, the catalytic reforming of heavy naphtha also provides hydrogen directly.
susy.quest.db.245789464.title=Rare Earths Beneficiation
susy.quest.db.245789464.desc=The primary rare earths in the EV age are §6bastnasite§r and §cmonazite§r. To produce a concentrate of rare earths, some beneficiation must be done.%n%nTo process §6bastnasite§r, it must first be gravity separated and floatated with oleic acid, then treated with sodium hydroxide to precipitate the rare earth hydroxides.%n%nProcessing §cmonazite§r also yields §4xenotime§r and considerable amounts of §2thorium§r. This is achieved using electrostatic separation followed by dissolution in hot sulfuric acid. Thorium is separated using ammonia, the rare earths are precipitated with sodium hydroxide, and uranium is separated as ammonium diuranate using ammonia and oxygen.
susy.quest.db.254727108.title=Miniaturized Electronic Circuit
susy.quest.db.254727108.desc=You may find these to be a little easier to craft, especially given how many you can make at a time!
susy.quest.db.261303499.title=Continuous Casting
susy.quest.db.261303499.desc=For some reason or another, you may find yourself using §cimmense§r amounts of basic materials in the near future. In order to supply your needs, you can use a §dContinuous Casting§r (AKA strand casting) system on the following materials:%n%n§7Steel%n§bAluminium (in future versions when Molten Aluminium is obtainable)%n§6Copper (in future versions)§r%n%nThis process simulates a strand of one of these materials being casted in sequence, allowing for incredibly high throughputs. You will need a lot of space for this, however.%n%nFirst, from an industrial arc furnace (or perhaps the arc furnace complex), obtain 2592 liters of §cmolten§r fluid of one of the above materials. Then, along with §9water§r as a coolant, put it into a mold: either a §6billet mold§r or a §eslab mold§r. The billet mold allows you to cast rods and ingots, while the slab mold allows you to cast all forms of plates (you can also reference the §bJEI info page§r for this). These also come with an optional steam output!%n%nNow, you will have a downwards-facing strand of one of these materials: the outside has been solidified by the water, but the internal strand is still molten, making it very malleable. Use a §6turning zone§r to direct the strand sideways. At this point, the strand can be §chot rolled§r. By placing §6rolling mills§r or §ecluster mills§r in sequence, you can compress the strand to reach your desired thickness. Reference the JEI info page to find the exact required thickness for your preferred material! As the strand moves into one of these, you will be able to see the material shape that would be produced at any particular moment in the process.%n%n§6Rolling mills§r take significantly less duration (or, alternatively, energy) than §ecluster mills§r do, but they are more suited to rolling §nthicker§r materials, whereas cluster mills are much better at rolling plates towards thinner thicknesses, such as for foils. §lBuild one at a time to find the optimal balance!§r%n%nFinally, once the strand has achieved the desired thickness, cut it with a §aFlying Shear§r and cool the strands with a §bStrand Cooler§r to receive your product in 18 ingot-equivalents at a time!%n%nTip: note that rods of these materials can actually be drawn into §ewires§r at a much faster rate than their ingots. You can use this to mass-produce wires.%nTip 2: again, build this §lone machine at a time§r. Don't force yourself to break and replace everything! Additionally, make sure you have enough space before you start.
susy.quest.db.262318723.title=Saltpeter and Nitrogen Dioxide
susy.quest.db.262318723.desc=§7Saltpeter§r, a mineral of potassium nitrate (KNO3), is an important early source of nitrogen oxides for use in the §dlead chamber process§r. It can be roasted with sulfuric acid to make nitrogen dioxide. It can be found in large veins in the overworld.
susy.quest.db.271215180.title=The Rarer Gases
susy.quest.db.271215180.desc=§eHelium§r & §cneon§r can be extracted from untreated liquid nitrogen. §aKrypton§r & §bxenon§r can be extracted from untreated liquid oxygen. Do note, the yields from this process is §nextremely low§r, so these gases will be used in moderation in the future until better ways of obtaining these gases are unlocked.
susy.quest.db.277135225.title=More Than Kin, Less Than Kind
susy.quest.db.277135225.desc=But now, my cousin and my son, how is it that the clouds still hang on you? Especially after you made so much of it.
susy.quest.db.280131684.title=RTM Coils
susy.quest.db.280131684.desc=The next tier of ERF coils requires ruthenium, tungsten, and molybdenum. It's not directly needed for §5tungstensteel§r, but it's an option.
susy.quest.db.283422181.title=Lead Dioxide
susy.quest.db.283422181.desc=§2Lead Dioxide§r is made by roasting §5Lead Dust§r in §7Air§r or §bOxygen§r.
susy.quest.db.284433121.title=Graphene
susy.quest.db.284433121.desc=§7Graphene§r is the material used for wires in IV. To produce it, molten salt exfoliation is used. A graphite electrode is broken down into a lithium chloride melt under moist argon. This is then purified into graphene in subsequent steps.
susy.quest.db.289522371.title=Spent Fuel Pool
susy.quest.db.289522371.desc=Nicely cools and stores your depleted fuel rods for you. It must be filled with water to operate. You can do this by supplying some water to an input hatch. You can even increase the size of it to increase the maximum parallel recipe count.%n%nAlso, if you go look inside it, you'll see that it releases §bCherenkov radiation§r!
susy.quest.db.291915692.title=Arc Furnace Complex
susy.quest.db.291915692.desc=Tired of waiting for your superalloys to smelt? Look no further than the §dArc Furnace Complex§r! This bad boy can smelt up to 256 output items at once with §ono§r extra duration or EU costs! %n%nIt's rather big, however.
susy.quest.db.302928877.title=焦炉砖
susy.quest.db.302928877.desc=混合§b粘土§r和§e沙子§r，就能混合出一种新粘土，先塑性再烧制就能造出一种高度气密的砖块，用于制造§6焦炉砖块§r。
susy.quest.db.326901357.title=Steam Cracking
susy.quest.db.326901357.desc=§8§o§o§rSteam cracking is a form of §cthermal cracking §rthat allows you to produce alkenes such as ethylene, propylene, etc. from lighter fractions and molecules such as naphtha.%n%nAdditionally, pyrolysis gasoline can be used as a gasoline blending component or as a source of §l§l§r§6BTEX§r.
susy.quest.db.328732527.title=CHAPTER 6 // Assembly Required
susy.quest.db.328732527.desc=Take your newly casted §5tungstensteel§r and make your first IV Machine Hulls. §ePlatinum§r coated with PVC are the cables required for this tier. §c§lWelcome to the modern age.§r%n%n---------------------------------------%n§eINSANE VOLTAGE HAS BEEN UNLOCKED! GOOD LUCK.§r%n---------------------------------------%n- Conquer the solar system%n- Build more reactors to discover more and more elements%n- Modify life itself to fit your needs
susy.quest.db.336324327.title=Gas Atomizer
susy.quest.db.336324327.desc=The construction of §csuperalloys§r requires incredibly high-quality material. Any defect within the crystal structure can eventually lead to creep, corrosion, or failure! To fix this problem, we can use a §dGas Atomizer§r.%n%nBy heating a crude electrode made of the desired material and then blasting it with an inert gas, an incredibly fine yet perfectly mixed material results.%n%nThis does require a healthy amount of §aBoron Nitride§r, however.
susy.quest.db.357396976.title=Mainframe
susy.quest.db.357396976.desc=With some NAND chips you will be able to craft your first IV tier circuit.
susy.quest.db.358881074.title=Ain't Nobody Gonna Break My Stride
susy.quest.db.358881074.desc=Using §7neodymium§r purified from your rare earths line, make some neodymium alloy magnets. Combine that with §7graphene§r, §9tungstensteel rods§r and §3platinum cable§r to produce the IV Electric Motor.
susy.quest.db.375402176.title=Induction Furnace
susy.quest.db.375402176.desc=The §6Induction Furnace§r is a type of electric furnace that uses electromagnetic induction to generate heat directly within the metal.%n%nThe Induction Furnace requires:%n§61x Induction Furnace Controller %n1x Energy Hatch %n1x Maintenance Hatch %n2x Input Hatch %n1x Output Hatch %n1x Input Bus %n8x Induction Coil Assembly %n46x Solid Steel Machine Casing§r
susy.quest.db.409196029.title=Advanced Electronic Circuit
susy.quest.db.409196029.desc=The §6Advanced Electronic Circuit§r is a cheaper MV circuit, although like before, it is still made out of §6LV§r circuits, along with a voltage regulator.
susy.quest.db.444684218.title=MAN - Steve Cutts
susy.quest.db.444684218.desc=Don't you just love microplastics?%n%nYou might want to check out the §dPhilips Catalyst§r first, though, before you take on the task of making this world a polluted wasteland.
susy.quest.db.456863075.title=点火
susy.quest.db.456863075.desc=§c燃烧§r是一种物质的快速氧化过程。它放出§6热§r和§e光§r，对§6烹饪§r，§6熔炼§r和各种应用来说非常有用。%n%n§6弓钻§r是你的第一个点火工具，按住§a右键§r就能在视点位置点火。%n%n§6耐用弓钻§r的耐久更多，但需要§c皮革§r（现在只能杀牛获得）。%n%n你现在可以点燃§c篝火§r了，它可以照亮周围的环境并且提供一个§2非常舒适§r的环境。你现在可以通过将§6火绒§r放在地面，然后§a右键§r放置原木就可以点火了。
susy.quest.db.477886967.title=Geothermal Power
susy.quest.db.477886967.desc=All of the fluid deposits in the Nether are §clava fluid deposits.§f Using a §afluid drilling rig§f and a §bheat exchanger,§f you can turn water into steam using lava.%n%nThis steam can then be used to generate power.
susy.quest.db.493331537.title=Output Modules
susy.quest.db.493331537.desc=- §6Signal Status Lamp§r: Simple light indicator. Can set both lamp color and threshold signal at which lamp turns on. 1x1 area.%n%n- §6Analog Display Module§r: Simple dial display. Minimum and Maximum scale limits can be configured. Label, Value unit and Unit factor can be set. Comes in 2x2, 2x4, 4x2 and 4x4 sizes.%n%n-§67-Segment Display Module§r: Numeric display. Label, Decimal point and Display color are configurable. comes in 1x1, 1x2, 2x2 and 4x2 sizes.%n%n7-Segment displays have multiple display encodings:%n-§6Signed§r: Displays §3input§r as a decimal numbers%n-§6Unsigned§r: Ignores negative sign §8(You'll probably want this one)§r%n-§6Hexadecimal§r: Displays raw hexadecimal value%n-§6Raw segments§r: Each byte of §3input§r controls one digit, and each bit controlling one segment §8(Hover over encoding button for more info)§r%n-§6Signed raw segments§r: Like raw segments, but only rightmost 3 digits have raw segments control, leftmost is controlled with 2 bits to display a sign%n%n7-Segments can be extended by daisy chaining multiple displays. By aligning multiple in a line, connecting the §3input§r to the rightmost display, and connecting its §2output§r to the §3input§r of the display left of it. All but the leftmost display must be in Unsigned encoding mode to work. Leftmost display can be signed or unsigned.%n%n-§6Oscilloscope Module Module§r: Can graph §3input§r signals over time, comes in 2x2, 2x4, 4x2 and 4x4 sizes. §3Input§r is a 32 bit signal with the 2 most significant 16bits work as a clock with any change causing the display to shift. Each 16 bits after is a separate graph §3input§r, capped between 0 to 100, and displays 50/100 samples depending on the width of the display. Oscilloscope modules can be daisy chained like 7-Segment displays, with the §3input§r going to the rightmost display and Oscolloscopes connected right to left.%n%nSimple Oscilloscope setup: Place a §6Binary Signal Packer§r and configure it to §l4x8bit -> 32bit§r mode (§a[right-clicking]§r the top of the packer), and connect its §2output§r to the §3input§r of the oscilloscope. Attach a Clock Plug configured to a short delay (§a[right-clicking]§r in air) or an external clock to the §3IN 3§r port of the packer, and signals to be graphed to the other 3 inputs. §3IN0§r for the red graph, §3IN1§r for green and §3IN2§r for blue. Use a combination of signal offset and scaler modules to put your §3Input§r signal in the 0-100 range of the scope.
susy.quest.db.498154717.title=Medium Voltage Regulator
susy.quest.db.498154717.desc=§cVoltage regulators§r will help stabilize this next tier of circuits.
susy.quest.db.530373325.title=Just Enough Fibers
susy.quest.db.530373325.desc=Do you want even more §4Dried Plant Fibers§r, or are you simply tired of drying §aPlant Fibers§r on a §6Drying Rack§r? Now that you have acquired §6Stone Ovens§r, you can dry plant fibers in them with a §a2x§r speed bonus! Hopefully, this will provide you with enough fibers for the entire early game.
susy.quest.db.542264610.title=Processing Modules
susy.quest.db.542264610.desc=All three signal modules can be mounted on control panels to modify their input signal. Signals are processed and passed through with no delay.%n%n-§6Signal Offset§r: Adds an offset on top of the §2input§r signal. Value can be adjusted in world by using §a[right-click]§r on left or right side of the module. Configuring lets you set the current offset and the step value the offset is adjusted in world. Units, Unit scale and Label can also be configured. 1x2 size.%n%n-§6Signal Scaler§r: Multiplies or divides the §2input§r signal. Value can be adjusted in world by using §a[right-click]§r on left or right side of the module. Has an internal scale factor §lseparate§r of the factor set externally. Label and scale units can be configured. 1x2 size.%n%n-§6Signal Threshold Latch§r: Turns ON when §2input§r is greater than the enable threshold, and stays in the ON state until the input signal falls below the disable threshold which puts it in the OFF state. §3Outputs§r 0 in OFF state and 65535 in ON state. Both enable and disable thresholds can be configured externally and internally. The step value of the thresholds being changed externally can be adjusted. Label and Units can also be configured.
susy.quest.db.561740681.title=Multiblock Builder
susy.quest.db.561740681.desc=Tired of building multiblocks by hand? Now you can assemble entire structures by simply sneaking and right clicking a controller with the §eMultiblock Builder§f!\n(It is recommended to leave hatches out of your inventory so you can choose their placement.)\n\nIn addition, you can also find out why your multi isn\u0027t forming by right clicking the controller which will give you the information you need in §cchat§e§f.
susy.quest.db.577792334.title=石窑
susy.quest.db.577792334.desc=§6石窑§r是一种窑，比坑窑好很多。带有一个用§8砌砖§r制作的隔热仓，可以维持更高的温度，因此§4煅烧§r现在是可能的（§7石灰岩§r转化为§7生石灰§r的过程）。也可以烧制§6焦炉砖§r和§6耐火砖§r。除此之外，它也有比坑窑更低的失败率。%n%n如使用石窑，需要§a右键§r窑的上下部分来放入物品/燃料，然后点火就会开始烧制。
susy.quest.db.595675883.title=LREE Separation
susy.quest.db.595675883.desc=The Tier 1 LREE separation chain is rather slow and energy intensive. A better tier using §9liquid-liquid extraction§r is unlocked in the IV age.%n%nFirst, §blanthanum carbonate§r is crystallized from the light rare earths using ammonium carbonate. The remaining rare earths are precipitated using sodium hydroxide. §aCerium§r has already been removed so now, only §2praseodymium§r and §7neodymium§r need to be separated. §2Praseodymium§r has an unstable 4+ oxidation state that can be achieved by melting the rare earth hydroxides in potassium hydroxide and oxidizing §2praseodymium§r using potassium chlorate. The neodymium is dissolved away using acid, leaving behind §2praseodymium§r.
susy.quest.db.599345269.title=Copper Line
susy.quest.db.599345269.desc=The §6copper line § is available after froth flotation is unlocked, useful for producing many useful byproducts.%n%n§rBy concentrating copper using §esodium ethyl xanthate§r, copper concentrate can be smelted with natural gas and oxygen to produce a sulfide matte. The flue gas can be used to obtain zinc, lead, and tin oxides. The matte is then further smelted to produce blister copper and another flue gas that contains antimony, bismuth, arsenic, and tin oxides.%n%nElectrolysis of blister copper plates is then performed, yielding some nickel, pure copper, and an anode slime. The anode slime can be further refined into §bselenium§r and §9tellurium§r with some §6electrum§r.%n%nThe zinc, copper, and lead lines produce byproducts that can be used as feeds to each other, so take advantage of this.
susy.quest.db.601210975.title=All My Friends Argon
susy.quest.db.601210975.desc=Upgrade your tier 1 separation plant with some single column plants to produce §2argon§r to speed up some of your processes such as silicon boule or stainless steel production!%n{Embed}TypeLink;https://github.com/SymmetricDevs/QuestbookMedia/blob/main/flowcharts/tier2airsep.png;128;20;§9§nAir Separation Tier 2§r{Embed}
susy.quest.db.603540269.title=Coolant Loops
susy.quest.db.603540269.desc=Before you construct your nuclear reactor, you must choose the §9coolant cycle§r you will use.%n%nA §aPWR§r coolant cycle loops §bpressurized water§r produced by compressing deionized water. When it is passed through the core of the reactor, it is heated to §chot pressurized water§r which can be run through a heat exchanger to produce high pressure steam and deionized water. You will want to route some of the high pressure steam back into the water pressurizer while feeding the rest into a §6high pressure advanced steam turbine§r. The advantage of this cycle is the ability to pipe in water in the secondary loop without reclaiming it.%n%nA §eBWR§r coolant cycle loops §3boiling water§r first produced by heating water or later condensing high pressure wet exhaust steam. When passed through the reactor, it converts it into high pressure wet steam, which can also be run through the high pressure turbine to produce high pressure wet exhaust steam, which is cooled with a §dcooling tower§r back into boiling water. The §dcooling tower§r can also be used to reclaim some water in the §aPWR§r cycle. This cycle has less machines but requires a closed coolant loop.
susy.quest.db.610444332.title=Smart Ways To Live
susy.quest.db.610444332.desc=Hopefully, you have not had your lungs filled yet with the trace toxic gases in the §7Beneath§r like §cCarbon Monoxide, Methane, and Hydrogen Sulfide§r. In either case, you can get away just a little longer using a §eSimple Gas Mask§r!%n%nTo be clear, it isn't very good. It does literally break in ten minutes! However, it's very easy to craft, assuming that you have a little §6charcoal§r from a coke oven, some §7paper§r, some §6sticky resin§r, and some string. String can be easily crafted through §dGTFO cotton§r, assuming you make a quick farm.
susy.quest.db.616673869.title=Counter
susy.quest.db.616673869.desc=The §6Counter§r Increments/Decrements the value of §2Count§r OUT whenever the value of §3Clock IN§r changes. Counts up to the value set at §3Limit IN§r, and rolls back to zero next time §3Clock IN§r changes. Can be set to Decrement mode where the value decrements, and rolls up to §3Limit IN§r after clocking the counter at 0.
susy.quest.db.618527753.title=Carbon Black
susy.quest.db.618527753.desc=Carbon black is an important component of synthetic rubber manufacturing, strengthening the product. It can be produced by partially combusting residues and heavy fractions in a rotary kiln.
susy.quest.db.625044001.title=Planar Process Euphoria
susy.quest.db.625044001.desc=You're now ready to make 512 Commodore 64s.%n%nHonestly, I'm not sure if you'll need the 16384 chips, but it seems fitting.
susy.quest.db.641325952.title=Lipid Pretreatment
susy.quest.db.641325952.desc=There are 3 ways to reduce the §cfatty acid§r contents in your §6lipids§r:%n%n§l1)§r Distillation.%n§l2)§r Neutralization by §9Dilute NaOH solution§r.%n§l3)§r Acid-catalyzed esterification with §bglycerol§r.%n%nThe 3rd method is more complex than the above two, but it allows you to convert all the aliphatic acid contents in your lipids into biodiesel.%n%nWhichever route you choose, you'll get §edeacidified lipid§r as product, which can be used directly for the §3transesterification§r reaction.
susy.quest.db.646655741.title=Nuclear Fuel Rods
susy.quest.db.646655741.desc=You can see the properties of each of these fuel rods within JEI. To summarize:%n%nTotal energy: the amount of energy contained within each fuel rod (all depleted at once).%n%nSlow neutron capture probability: how likely it is for a neutron to be captured, measured in barns (a very small measure of probability)%n%nAvg. neutron lifetime: how quickly the reactor's neutron population changes with Keff
susy.quest.db.649388409.title=Spin Me Right Round
susy.quest.db.649388409.desc=The §agas centrifuge §ris the primary method to enrich isotopes (such as U-235) based on their atomic weight. This machine controller is rather expensive, however you can improve the multiblock's parallelization by increasing the number of columns you add onto your multiblock.
susy.quest.db.651786998.title=Field Programmable Gate Arrays
susy.quest.db.651786998.desc=FPGAs can represent nearly any circuit in a nice compact way. With extra functionality like. To start with you need a Redstone FPGA, there are three versions DIP8, QFP12 and BGA16, with 4, 6 and 8 input/outputs. More IO comes at a cost of reduced size of the FPGA, which needs to be filled with components, so pick the one with the smallest amount of IO necessary.%n%nSecondly, you can plan your circuit in the FPGA Programmer. I/O Ports can (and should) be named. To connect components, §a[right-click]§r an §3input§r to start a connection and then §a[right-click]§r the output of another device/an input into the fpga (you can §a[right-click]§r multiple times to define a specific path). To delete components, select and click delete gate/drag the component off the editor screen. Input sockets are set to clock the circuit by default, but that can be disabled for all but one port to delegate it as an external clock.%n%nAfter your circuit is done, you can save it locally. On bottom right of the FPGA Programmer there are three values for Circuit Complexity, your fpga needs to meet these values to run your circuit. %n%nIn the FPGA Assembler, you can put components to increase the values for max complexity along with timing properties of your FPGA at the expense of remaining size. To see which components increase which stats click the R button inside the FPGA Assembler. %n%nFPGA's have a Redstone Exhaustion mechanic, where the faster the FPGA is clocked, the more it exhausts, and needs to cool off in order to run again. Inserted components affect those stats, distinctly quartz plates and capacitors. The FPGA will not be able to run if its longest tick burst is below 1. FPGAs can also be powered externally using §eEnergy Distributors§r and §eEnergy Wire§r (When the FPGA reaches 100%% Redstone exhaustion, it can try to draw some amount of power from the connected network to reset it to 0%%).
susy.quest.db.688409262.title=EV
susy.quest.db.688409262.desc=Ideal power production methods for §dEV§r.
susy.quest.db.694062778.title=Hydraulics
susy.quest.db.694062778.desc=I mean, the "hydro" has to come from §osomewhere§r. It's not our fault that it comes from things like calcium didodecylsulfonate!%n%nThis is a key material for §7EV§r machinery, used in the §cHot Isostatic Press§r and in §9Continuous Casting§r.
susy.quest.db.702158502.title=Radiator
susy.quest.db.702158502.desc=A §6radiator§r is a device that transfers heat from a fluid or object to the surrounding environment%n%nIt can cool down exhaust steam into water or §chot compressed fluids into a more manageable temperature.§r%n%nFor example, you can cool down Hot High Pressure Hydrogen into normal High Pressure Hydrogen.%n%nThe size of the radiator is not fixed, you can expand the radiator horizontally, vertically, or even both! The larger it gets, the faster it cools down fluids. More info is in the Multiblock Preview page in JEI.%n%nDue to the high cost of steel, it is recommended that you upgrade from just using a PBF setup.
susy.quest.db.702454111.title=Cryolite About It
susy.quest.db.702454111.desc=I mean really, this probably won't even last you through §6half§r of MV age!%n%nAlso, if you're wondering why it's spelled with §l-ium§r, it's because an advertisement literally misspelled it. Also, it's because you suck, you filthy American.
susy.quest.db.707957708.title=Just Like Factorio
susy.quest.db.707957708.desc=§eCoal liquefaction§r is a useful process for quickly producing §6gasoline§r and §a§adiesel§r blending feedstocks directly from coal using hydrogen and a tetralin solvent. This can help augment your power production with excess coal from ore processing.
susy.quest.db.721905821.title=Plugs
susy.quest.db.721905821.desc=Plugs can be connected directly into §3Input§r/§2Output§r ports of devices to provide extra functionality. They can be removed using a screwdriver with §a[left-click]§r%n%n-§6Signal Status Lamp§r: Can be plugged into §2Output§r ports, to show the current value when hovering over the port.%n%n-§6Constant Plug§r: Can be plugged into §3Input§r ports, to set a constant signal into the port. §a[right-click]§r in air to set the value. Use no prefix for decimal (101), b for binary (b101) and x for hex (x101). §a[sneak+right-click]§r in air to change representation.%n%n-§6Clock Plug§r: Can be plugged into §3Input§r ports, works as a configurable clock source. §a[right-click]§r in air to set both clock interval and offset of the clock. All clocks in the world are synchronized. §2Outputs§r 0 when off and 65535 when on. §a[sneak+right-click]§r in air to clear configuration.%n%n-§6Toggle Latch Plug§r: Can be plugged into §2Output§r ports, toggles the §2Output§r between 0 and 65535 whenever the signal of the output changes from low to high when in UP mode, and from high to low when in DOWN mode. low being considered 0 or below, and high being 1 and up.  §a[right-click]§r in air to change modes.%n%n-§6Pulse Generator Plug§r: Can be plugged into §2Output§r ports, Sends a signal of 65535 for one tick whenever the signal of the §2output§r port changes, otherwise sends 0.
susy.quest.db.725745868.title=Keeping Things Organized
susy.quest.db.725745868.desc=§6Wire Tag§r: Lets you label any signal on a network, §a[right-click]§r in air to set the name, and then §a[right-click]§r on any wired port to label it and all currently connected port. §a[right-click]§r in Air to clear name.%n%n§6Wire Anchor§r: Multiple can be placed on any surface, and then §cSignal Wire§r can be attached to them to change the path or extend the wires range.%n%n
susy.quest.db.741794531.title=Latches
susy.quest.db.741794531.desc=§4Project Red§r adds a variety of different types of latches to use in redstone circuits.%n%n- §6RS Latch§r: Stores a signal like digital memory; it holds a state until it is changed by another circuit. Can be changed modes using a §4Project Red §6screwdriver§r. In mode 2, the selector side will not function as output.%n%n- §6Toggle Latch§r: Toggles the output §2ON§r/§cOFF§r every time it receives a pulse and ignores sustained input.%n%n- §6Pulse Former§r: Converts a sustained input into a 1-tick output pulse.%n%n- §6State Cell§r: Holds a redstone signal in a similar way to the §6RS Latch§r, but it does not need separate Set/Reset inputs%n%n- §6Synchronizer§r: Delays a signal until the next redstone tick to prevent timing glitches%n%n- §6Transparent Latch§r: Stores a redstone signal using a lock mechanism. If the lock is §2ON§r, the outputs copy the input but when the lock is §cOFF§r, the outputs are locked to the state they were in.%n%n- §6Multiplexer§r: When the selector input is §cOFF§r, output is determined by right input. When the selector input is §2ON§r, output is determined by left input.%n%n- §6Buffer Gate§r: Works as a one sided input. Input side will power the 3 outputs but a signal from the output sides will not power the rest.%n%n- §6Repeater§r: Works the same as a vanilla §6Repeater§r but with more options for delay.
susy.quest.db.744003683.title=坑窑
susy.quest.db.744003683.desc=§6坑窑§r是一个可以把粘土变成§4红砖§r或把圆石变成对应§7石头§r的原始窑。然而，它的隔热性能不足导致无法处理某些配方。%n%n如果要做一个坑窑，需要四个稻草和三个原木。请注意，坑窑的所有面（顶部除外）都应该用方块封住以保持隔热效果（记得保持干燥）。%n%n1. §a右键§r任意方块放置一层稻草，会出现一个坑窑方块。%n%n2. §a右键§r坑窑放入你想烧制的物品。%n%n3. 添加三个稻草和三个原木（手持稻草必须大于等于三）。%n%n这样坑窑就已完成，点燃它就可以开始加热。一个坑窑一次最大可以处理§a8§r个物品，并且§4失败率§r根据配方变化。烧制完毕后，直接破坏就可以获得产物。
susy.quest.db.745182757.title=Acetic Acid and Ethyl Acetate
susy.quest.db.745182757.desc=§eAcetic acid§r can be obtained from further fermentation of ethanol. Take some impure ethanol fermented from grain solution and let it ferment. The resulting vinegar can be distilled into dilute acetic acid. Unfortunately, since acetic acid and water form an §cazeotrope§r, conventional distillation cannot produce concentrated §eacetic acid§r without an entrainer such as §aethyl acetate§r. %n%nTo obtain ethyl acetate, esterify dilute acetic acid (from vinegar or wood vinegar) with ethanol (which can be obtained from azeotropic distillation with toluene or acetaldehyde).
susy.quest.db.752427679.title=Refractory Gunning Mixture
susy.quest.db.752427679.desc=To run the §6Industrial Arc Furnace§r, the innards of the machine must reach §c1800°C§r. This does not typically bode well for the lining of the vessel.%n%nTo fix this issue, a §dRefractory Gunning Mixture§r is applied to the surface of the vessel, helping maintain its lifespan.%n%nMaking it requires some §bAlumina§r, §8Silicon Carbide§r, clay, and water, but it's not terribly expensive if you have all of that automated. Right?
susy.quest.db.762134374.title=Asbestos Fiber
susy.quest.db.762134374.desc=§6Asbestos fibers §fcan be made into §9§k§eblocks§f, which will be a great choice to use for your buildings that tend to §ccatch fire§f because they are §n§9§n§9§nfireproof!§f
susy.quest.db.768746703.title=Upgraded Steam Turbines
susy.quest.db.768746703.desc=After unlocking superalloys, you can produce turbine blades suitable for better steam turbines. The §9low pressure§r advanced steam turbine takes in regular steam and produces 1.5x more power. the §6high pressure§r advanced steam turbine can produce power from high pressure steam, useful for nuclear reactors and will power you through the §dLuV Age§r.%n%n3L of high pressure steam equates to 1,024,000 EU.
susy.quest.db.777592558.title=It's As Shrimple As That
susy.quest.db.777592558.desc=It only takes, like, 20 steps.
susy.quest.db.789439587.title=Tools of the Trade
susy.quest.db.789439587.desc=The Screwdriver and Signal Probe are essential tools for the mod.%n%n§6Screwdriver§r: Lets you remove, configure and copy configuration of modules from Control Panels, rotate blocks.%n%n§6Signal Probe§r: Hovering over any device shows the signals coming in and out of that device in both Hexadecimal and Integer representation. Hovering over any port highlights the signals on that port. Also doubles as a Screwdriver.
susy.quest.db.792019455.title=Lead Line
susy.quest.db.792019455.desc=The §5lead line§r is a method to produce byproducts such as antimony, arsenic, bismuth, indium, silver, zinc, copper, and more.%n%nFirst, smelt your lead ore in a rotary kiln to produce a sintered concentrate, then smelt to obtain §7lead bullion§r.%n%nThere are two methods to approach the next step:%n- The electrolytic method: electrorefine the bullion to produce an anode slime and pure lead.%n- The pyrometallurgical method: melt the bullion and process.%n%nWhichever method you choose, most useful byproducts can be obtained.%n%nThe zinc, copper, and lead lines produce byproducts that can be used as feeds to each other, so take advantage of this.
susy.quest.db.796249166.title=Input Modules
susy.quest.db.796249166.desc=- §6Lever Module§r: Works as a simple lever, both on and off signal values can be configured to any value, label can also be altered. Takes 1x1 area.%n%n- §6Slider Module§r: Works as a variable input. Both minimum and maximum signal values can be configured. Can also be given a label. 2x4 area.%n%n- §6Lamp-Switch Module§r: Works just like the lever module, but with built in indicator light, which can be set to a variety of colors. 1x1 area.%n%n- §6Lamp-Button Module§r: Works as a button. Can configure Maximum signal value but not minimum (outputs 0 by default), ON interval can also be configured between 0.05s to 1 minute. Indicator light color is also configurable. 1x1 area.%n%n- §6Clock Plug§r: can be placed on Control Panels. Label can be configured, §a[right-click] §rleft/right side of module to adjust the period, with range of 0.05s to 1 minute. Needs a non 0 input to run (including negative values, input value doesn't affect period or timing).
susy.quest.db.797571327.title=ETERNAL SUFFERING
susy.quest.db.797571327.desc=The §cShell Higher Olefin Process§r is a method to produce linear alpha olefins. The catalyst is the main hassle in the process, and requires multitudinous steps to synthesize. Good luck, you will need it.%n%nThese linear alpha olefins are essential for producing extraction agents for ore processing in the EV age, and are also useful for producing lubricant base oils and additives.
susy.quest.db.802655963.title=Combustion Generators
susy.quest.db.802655963.desc=Unlocked in MV, these combustion generators are a compact way to produce power from refined fuels without the need for an oxidant and a large multiblock! These are rather expensive and require 2 palladium each to start.
susy.quest.db.853441196.title=The Big One
susy.quest.db.853441196.desc=We knew the world would not be the same. A few people laughed, a few people cried, most people were silent. I remembered the line from the Hindu scripture, the Bhagavad-Gita. Vishnu is trying to persuade the Prince that he should do his duty and to impress him takes on his multi-armed form and says, “Now, I am become Death, the destroyer of worlds.” I suppose we all thought that one way or another. -J. Robert Oppenheimer
susy.quest.db.899643298.title=Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
susy.quest.db.899643298.desc=§bSolid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs)§r are electrochemical devices that directly convert fuels into electrical power without the need for a thermodynamic cycle (think steam boiling and turbines). As a result, these are more efficient than their multiblock counterparts, but are rather expensive, making them suitable for portable power generation. Once you have obtained §dgadolinium§r and §alanthanum§r, by combining these elements with manganese, nickel, and strontium, you can produce a fuel cell.%n%nTo operate a §bSOFC§r, it first must be preheated with air to the correct operating temperature. For EV fuel cells, this is 500C while for IV fuel cells this is 800C. Afterwards, it will begin producing power.
susy.quest.db.927023403.title=Fischer-Tropsch Synthesis
susy.quest.db.927023403.desc=The §6Fischer-Tropsch§r process is a method of obtaining oil fractions from syngas. There are two varieties, a low temperature and a high temperature process. The high temperature process is quicker but requires a fluidized bed reactor.
susy.quest.db.933270194.title=Cells or Gates?
susy.quest.db.933270194.desc=While cells and gates are similar in function, there are a few differences.%n%n1. Cells are much more basic, making them less versatile, unlike gates, which can usually be modified with a §6screwdriver§r.%n%n2. Cells allow for passthrough, which means that the input for the cell can continue after it, whereas gates need the input to be fed into them.%n%nThis includes%n-§6 Null Cells§r%n- §6Invert Cells§r%n- §6Buffer Cells§r%n- §6And Cells§r%n- §6Data Cells§r
susy.quest.db.943634333.title=Hydrocracking
susy.quest.db.943634333.desc=§9Hydrocracking§r is a costly process that uses hydrogen to break heavier fractions into lighter fractions at high efficiency. It is best used in combination with §6catalytic cracking§r to convert cycle oil into aromatics (BTEX) and lighter fractions.
susy.quest.db.954006870.title=Cadmium
susy.quest.db.954006870.desc=Useful for batteries!
susy.quest.db.954692491.title=Bundled Plates
susy.quest.db.954692491.desc=§6Bundled Plates§r are the base for crafting all bundle-related circuits.
susy.quest.db.969248866.title=Bundled Circuits
susy.quest.db.969248866.desc=Using §6bundled plates§r, the following circuit components can be crafted.%n%n- §6Segment Display Gate§r: Takes a bundled cable as input and will display the number of channels that are currently §2ON§r.%nInput colors 1-8 control the right segment while 9-16 control the left.%n%n- §6Bus Randomizer§r: Takes a redstone signal as input and while the input is §2ON§r, it will randomize the output and once the input is §cOFF§r, the randomly selected configuration will lock. There are 2 modes to the randomizer: §aexclusive (default)§r and §enon-exclusive§r.%n§aExclusive mode§r: the randomizer will select 1 channel to output as §2ON§r and the rest will be §cOFF§r.%n§eNon-exclusive mode§r: every channel has a 50-50 chance of being §2ON§r or §cOFF§r.%n%n- §6Bus Converter§r: This gate has 2 modes: §aanalog to digital§r and §edigital to analog.§r%n§aAnalog to digital§r: Takes an input redstone signal and outputs a specific channel based on signal strength (white = 0, orange = 1, ...)%n§eDigital to analog§r: takes the bundled cable as input and will output redstone signal with strength corresponding to the highest §2ON§r channel.%n%n- §6Bus Input Panel§r: This gate has a button for every channel on the top, and any button switched §2ON§r will output §2ON§r for that channel.
susy.quest.db.977680348.title=Platinum Group Metals 2: Electric Boogaloo
susy.quest.db.977680348.desc=The §9platinum group metals§r are a series of metals prized for their rarity and chemical inertness. You have already produced §eplatinum§r and §7palladium§r, but the rarer metals (§bruthenium§r, §airidium§r, §9osmium§r, and §crhodium§r) have remained out of reach until now.%n%nIn general, these metals are extremely important in catalysts. Ruthenium is used in RTM alloy and iridium is used for inert electrodes and spark plugs.
susy.quest.db.987632600.title=The Interstate
susy.quest.db.987632600.desc=A good empire needs plenty of roads.
susy.quest.db.988736631.title=Filtered Tank
susy.quest.db.988736631.desc=By using a proper filter to remove §atoxic§r chemicals from the §cNether§r and §7Beneath§r's air, the §dFiltered Tank§r gives you effectively infinite oxygen in terrestrial environments!%n%nIf only there was a way to solve that durability problem, though...
susy.quest.db.1051748281.title=MREE Separation
susy.quest.db.1051748281.desc=The first step in separating MREEs uses §beuropium's§r 2+ oxidation state. It is reduced using zinc and separated using sulfuric acid. The remaining gap between Sm and Gd allows for efficient §9liquid-liquid extraction§r using §6P507§r.
susy.quest.db.1056118460.title=Residues
susy.quest.db.1056118460.desc=§6Atmospheric Oil Residue§r can be further separated to more oil fractions through §3vacuum distillation§r. However, there are other methods to process the residue, including §3cracking§r and §3combusting§r. Check the quests for those.%n%nIt can be also blended with Heavy Gas Oil to produce §6Fuel Oil§r! %n%nBe sure to check the JEI tab for all possibilities.
susy.quest.db.1064746016.title=The Rare Earths
susy.quest.db.1064746016.desc=The §6rare earth elements (REEs)§r are a series of elements with very similar chemical properties, possessing a preferred 3+ ionization state and almost identical atomic and ionic radii. Contrary to popular belief, the §6rare earths§r are not actually very rare. Instead, they are very difficult to separate based on their similar chemistries. This group contains:%n%nThe lanthanides: La, Ce, Pr, Nd, Pm (unstable), Sm, Eu, Gd, Tb, Dy, Ho, Er, Tm, Yb, Lu.%nThe group 3 transition metals: Sc, Y.%n%nDue to the overexploitation of scandium from the §aEarth§r by the Federation, scandium-bearing minerals are no longer found here. You must travel to the §7Luna§r to obtain it.%n%nThere are three main sources of §6rare earths§r on Earth: bastnasite, monazite, and xenotime. Bastnasite can be mined from magmatic hydrothermal deposits and are especially enriched in the light rare earths (LREEs) La, Ce, Pr, and Nd, with the heavier REEs having much smaller concentrations. Monazite is derived from alluvial deposits and is similarly enriched in LREEs but possess ~5x more MREEs (Sm, Eu, Gd) and ~34x more HREEs (Tb-Lu, Y). Yttrium, though lighter, chemically behaves similarly to the HREEs under most extraction procedures. Xenotime, also an alluvial ore, is a HREE-enriched mineral, especially enriched in yttrium, useful for the production of YBCO superconductors.%n%nThe HREEs and Yttrium are locked to IV. Focus on producing the LREEs and MREEs in this age.
susy.quest.db.1079109244.title=Large Steam Hammer
susy.quest.db.1079109244.desc=The §6Large Steam Hammer§r is a huge version of Steam Forge Hammer, capable of processing §6 8 items§r in parallel, but the recipe time for each item is multiplied by 150%% %n%nBuilding a Large Steam Hammer requires:%n1x Large Steam Hammer Controller%n1x Steam Input Bus%n1x Steam Hatch%n1x Steam Output Bus%n24x Solid Steel Machine Casing%n1x Anvil%n1x Steel Block (hammer head)%n%nCheck JEI for more info on the structure. Note that the area surrounding the hammer head must be empty.
susy.quest.db.1090881854.title=Operational Amplifiers
susy.quest.db.1090881854.desc=The §9Operational Amplifier§r (or just Op Amp) is a §6differential amplifier§r which outputs a voltage proportional to the difference of its inputs. These will be the foundation for the next generation of circuits.%n%nNote that you may unlock more efficient potting recipes using §7silicone rubber§r and §7ECN§r, which you may get through oil processing.
susy.quest.db.1091063286.title=Molybdenite Froth Flotation Conditioners
susy.quest.db.1091063286.desc=§6Sodium dithiophosphate§r (Nokes reagent) is consumed during the flotation of molybdenite ore. Produce it by reacting phosphorus pentasulfide with sodium hydroxide and distilled water.
susy.quest.db.1103231810.title=Circuit Plates
susy.quest.db.1103231810.desc=§6Circuit plates§r are the bulding block for all §4Project Red circuits§r, made with §6fine red alloy wires§r and §6stone plates§r.
susy.quest.db.1107188354.title=石砧
susy.quest.db.1107188354.desc=§6石砧§r和石头没太大区别，但它的光滑平面可以用来§4s捣碎东西§r。%n%n你需要这个来制作§7砌砖§r.
susy.quest.db.1110551649.title=Multiplexing Signals
susy.quest.db.1110551649.desc=A pair of binary packer-unpacker lets you combine multiple signals onto the same wire, and unpack them at a different location. Both devices can pack/unpack 1/2/4/8 bits.%n%n- §6Binary Signal Packer§r: Takes X amount of rightmost bits from each §3input§r signal and combines them into into the §2output§r signal. Amount of bits taken from each §3input§r signal is configured by using §2[right-click]§r or §2[sneak+right-click]§r on top of the packer. Any bits from each input outside the range are discarded.%n%n- §6Binary Signal Unpacker§r: Splits rightmost bits of the §3input§r signal into 4 even chunks of X amount of bits. Amount of bits the input is split into can be configured by using §2[right-click]§r or §2[sneak+right-click]§r on top of the unpacker. Any bits outside the 4*X range are discarded.%n%n§8(To transmit 4 unaltered redstone signals, a single pair of packer-unpacker in 4x4bit->16bit mode is enough, but up to 8 redstone signals can be transmitted over one line, 32 if signal strength is not important)
susy.quest.db.1112000445.title=Gas Mask v2.0
susy.quest.db.1112000445.desc=So you don't really want your gas mask to last a maximum of §c10 minutes§r. That's hardly enough to even get anthracite! %n%nFortunately, you've advanced a little since then. You can make your suits out of actually durable materials like §8rubber§r!
susy.quest.db.1125132124.title=Bundled Cable
susy.quest.db.1125132124.desc=§6Bundled cable§r is made using §6insulated wires§r and §6string§r. They are used to bundle redstone signals allowing to pass up to 16 different signals in one block. This helps make redstone circuits more compact. These can also be framed.
susy.quest.db.1131298338.title=Evil Chloralkali Process
susy.quest.db.1131298338.desc=By running the chloralkali solution with §crock salt§r instead of regular salt, you can obtain §dpotassium hydroxide§r, which can be used to make the next tier of batteries!
susy.quest.db.1133349266.title=Fuel Cladding
susy.quest.db.1133349266.desc=You're going to need a lot of these. Also, you don't get them back once your fuel is depleted either.
susy.quest.db.1172548885.title=Fuel Cells
susy.quest.db.1172548885.desc=Fuel cells are a type of energy source that directly extracts electrical energy from fuel oxidation using solid-state electronics. These are single-blocks that can provide 1A of EV (Low Temperature) or IV (High Temperature) power. These reactors require preheated air to keep them well heated.
susy.quest.db.1177038065.title=Heated Oil
susy.quest.db.1177038065.desc=Put any type of §6Desalted Oil§r in an §6LV Fluid Heater§r to get §6Heated Oil§r, and it is ready for distillation!
susy.quest.db.1185089564.title=Metallurgical Converter
susy.quest.db.1185089564.desc=This machine replaces the §7Reverberatory Furnace§r, if you were still using it. This multiblock parallelizes up to §d64§r output items, making it an excellent option for steel and copper making.
susy.quest.db.1188697175.title=The Heavy Rare Earths
susy.quest.db.1188697175.desc=Now that you have reached the IV tier, you can use your blender to produce §6P229§r or di(2-ethylhexyl)phosphinic acid. When combined with §6P507§r, this produces a mixture capable of separating the heavy rare earths, a tough endeavor. Additionally, §9Aliquat 336§r or methyltrioctylammonium chloride is unlocked, useful for quick and efficient separation of the LREEs and §4yttrium§r.%n%nThe most useful ore for the HREEs is §4Xenotime§r, which is processed using electrostatic separation and roasting with soda ash. Further processing is done using these extraction mixtures in a complex process which eventually yields every HREE.
susy.quest.db.1193199034.title=The Gates of Oil Processing Hell
susy.quest.db.1193199034.desc=The §bsieve distillation tower §ris a slightly cheaper version of the regular distillation tower used in oil processing, which allows for more inputs. These will be ubiquitous in petrochemical processing.
susy.quest.db.1203267647.title=High Temperature Distillation
susy.quest.db.1203267647.desc=This §4high temperature distillation tower§r is plated with refractory ceramics to enable the distillation of molten metals. This is used for the purification of selenium and separation of cadmium, copper and lead from molten zinc.
susy.quest.db.1220908734.title=The Bigger Mixer
susy.quest.db.1220908734.desc=The §dblender§r is a bigger version of the mixer that perfectly overclocks and has access to some recipes the mixer cannot run, including improved lubricants & fuels, as well as some liquid-liquid extraction mixtures.
susy.quest.db.1228117936.title=Kaminsky Catalyst
susy.quest.db.1228117936.desc=With the Kaminsky Catalyst you will be able to make polyethylene, polypropylene, polyisoprene and UHMWPE at a greater efficiency. This catalyst also unlocks ethylene propylene copolymer which can be used in upgrading lubricants.
susy.quest.db.1234205834.title=Tier 2 Armor Upgrades
susy.quest.db.1234205834.desc=The second level of armor upgrades are made from steel and polycaprolactam (nylon).
susy.quest.db.1235452977.title=New Quest
susy.quest.db.1235452977.desc=No Description
susy.quest.db.1241306929.title=切开木头
susy.quest.db.1241306929.desc=如果你缺木头或者单纯想充分利用，试试在§6砧板§r上处理，会给25%%的额外木板产出。%n%n§8但为啥不直接住森林里...§r
susy.quest.db.1277844953.title=Signal Splitters
susy.quest.db.1277844953.desc=§6- Signal 4x Splitter§r: Can be placed in world, any signal going into its §3Input§r will be copied to the 4 §2Output§r ports.%n%n- §6Signal Splitter Plug§r: Can be applied to §2Output§r ports directly, allowing you to connect multiple §4Signal Wires§r to a port. After the first splitter is applied, Additional splitters are automatically used from the inventory when attempting to attach extra wires. A maximum of 8 wires can be connected to one port.
susy.quest.db.1285370028.title=Drone Pad
susy.quest.db.1285370028.desc=Do you §4hate§r finding cows? Are you very annoyed that the pack developers turned down the rate of animal spawns?%n%nLook no further than the §dDrone Pad§r! By putting in a fully charged drone, you can acquire these resources:%n%n- Bones%n- Meats%n- Leather (needed for exploration of the §cmantle§r)%n- Wool%n%nAnd many more! Just charge up a §7drone§r in a charging slot and place it in the drone pad with the right recipe. The pad itself just needs:%n%n- 9 Drone Pads%n- 9 Solid Steel Casings%n- 1 Drone Pad Controller%n- 1 Input Bus, Output Bus, and Energy Hatch (LV+ works)
susy.quest.db.1319048907.title=Graduated Cylinders
susy.quest.db.1319048907.desc=While holding any item which can contain fluids in your main hand (i.e. §7buckets§r, §7fluid cells§r, or §7drums§r, etc.), §a§2punch§r any placed block which can also hold fluids (i.e. §7drums§r, §7fluid hatches§r, or §7GregTech machines§r, etc.) to open the §6transfer GUI§r. Here, you can choose the amount in millibuckets to transfer and the direction.%n%nYou can also transfer fluids §2between two items§r, by §a[right-clicking]§r one on top of the other in an inventory.%n%nThis will help a lot for batch crafting with fluids.
susy.quest.db.1319198702.title=Jet Wingpack
susy.quest.db.1319198702.desc=The §3Jet Wingpack§r represents an advancement in §6Jetpack§r technology. By integrating a §eWingsuit System§r with four kerosene-powered §4Turbojets§r, this device enables users to achieve flight faster than ever before.%n%nTo begin gliding, simply press §6[Space]§r once you are off the ground. If the §4Turbojets§r are running, you can take off with a single press of the §6[Space]§r key. The §4Turbojets§r themselves can be toggled with a hotkey. They can provide thrust in the direction you are facing. Additionally, you can press §a[sneak]§r to activate the brake.%n%nUnlike the simple liquid-fueled jetpack, the §3Jet Wingpack§r has some §crestrictions§r to the fuels it can use. Check JEI for more info.%n%n§7§o§lMind your head during the flight.§r
susy.quest.db.1322263999.title=Air Separation Mark II
susy.quest.db.1322263999.desc=§bCryogenic air separation§r is a technique to produce massive volumes of liquid and gaseous atmospheric elements for use in your base. It is also the only method to produce the stable noble gases heavier than §ehelium§r, which can also be produced from natural gas. This will prove useful for superconductor manufacturing and eventually fueling your rockets to head off into space.%n%nBefore you can separate air, you must remove heavier components such as §dcarbon dioxide§r first using a molecular sieve. If you are obtaining air from the §4nether§r, you can also obtain hydrogen sulfide and sulfur dioxide in this step.%n%nYou will need many machines used to produce enough liquid decarburized air and cold high pressure decarburized air for this process, which is most of the energy cost. §l§nNote: if you just want gaseous oxygen and nitrogen, a pressure-swing adsorber would be better, as this setup produces mostly liquid products.§r %n%nCryogenic air separation setups typically require a §blow pressure column §rand a §1§9high pressure column§r. If you are trying to produce noble gases, §dsingle-column cryogenic distillation plants§r are required. §bThe low pressure columns§r and §dsingle-column plants§r have a free space inside where you can place §abath condensers§r, which rely on the low temperature of the column to condense gases into liquid. To access a bath condenser inside the multiblocks, use §3Passthrough Hatches§r. You may find it helpful to share the bottom and top of the low and high pressure columns.%n{Embed}TypeLink;https://github.com/SymmetricDevs/QuestbookMedia/blob/main/flowcharts/tier1airsep.png;128;20;§9§nAir Separation Tier 1§r{Embed}
susy.quest.db.1329442186.title=The Purity of the Blessed Machine
susy.quest.db.1329442186.desc=From the moment I understood the §cweakness§r of my §6flesh§r, it §adisgusted§r me. I craved the strength and certainty of §1tungstensteel§r. I aspired to the purity of the §dBlessed Machine§r.%n%nYour §4kind§r cling to your flesh, as if it will not §2decay§r and fail you. One day the §2crude biomass§r that you call a temple will §7wither§r, and you will §bbeg§r my kind to save you. But I am already saved, for the §lMachine§r is immortal...%n%n...even in death I serve the Omnissiah.
susy.quest.db.1337107364.title=Low Enriched
susy.quest.db.1337107364.desc=This is the first §aU-235§r enrichment grade that can be used with light water reactors. If you want to use natural uranium as a fuel, §9heavy water§r is required. To convert the hexafluoride into uranium dioxide for fuel pellets, react it with dense steam and ammonia, then reduce with hydrogen.
susy.quest.db.1338245952.title=Thorium
susy.quest.db.1338245952.desc=No Description
susy.quest.db.1341084380.title=Alluvial Gold
susy.quest.db.1341084380.desc=Alluvial metallic §6gold§r may be obtained from alluvial deposits found near shorelines and rivers. Unlike §eelectrum§r, alluvial gold deposit extraction can be automated. To refine it, first crush the deposit, then oxidize/leach the gold out using air and §asodium cyanide§r. The resulting solution can be loaded onto §8activated carbon§r to remove it from solution. Next, redissolve it using §9gold elution solution§r, which elutes (removes) the gold from the carbon. This solution may then be electroplated onto fine steel wires. The steel can then be removed with nitric acid.
susy.quest.db.1341242396.title=Rubber Plates (Hard)
susy.quest.db.1341242396.desc=The §7Ebonite§r is a highly vulcanized hard rubber with excellent dielectric properties and corrosive resistance. These properties make Ebonite an excellent material for early battery hulls.%n%nPrepare the vulcanization mixture by combining equal amounts of Latex Dust and §6Sulfur§r with the addition of §7Coal Dust§r filler, then use the §6Vulcanizing Press§r to produce the §7Ebonite Plate§r.
susy.quest.db.1344588484.title=Silicon Chips
susy.quest.db.1344588484.desc=Silicon Chips are another type of §4Project Red§r plate that allow for more complex circuits. These have 2 variants: §6silicon chips§r and §6energized silicon chips§r.
susy.quest.db.1355947275.title=Sodium Cyanide
susy.quest.db.1355947275.desc=§aSodium cyanide§r is an important extractant for precious metal extraction due to its ability to selectively dissolve §6gold§r. To produce it, first react sodium metal with ammmonia to obtain sodium amide. This can then be further reacted with carbon to produce §asodium cyanide§r.
susy.quest.db.1365346037.title=早期游戏自动化
susy.quest.db.1365346037.desc=也许手动操作窑和炉比较枯燥？你是不是也想在机器上跳来跳去来消磨时间？来试试§6机械漏斗§r吧。和原版漏斗相差无几，但需要§6齿轮§r来工作。%n%n可以先合成漏斗再安装齿轮，或是在合成时加入齿轮。
susy.quest.db.1371604013.title=Zinc Line
susy.quest.db.1371604013.desc=The §bhydrometallurgical zinc line§r is the next step up from the primitive smelter in terms of zinc processing. While not necessarily better in terms of yield, it allows for the extraction of useful byproducts such as §5indium§r, §9thallium§r, and §agermanium§r.%n%nLooking forwards, the zinc, copper, and lead purification lines generally can produce similar products but at different ratios. It is recommended to build all of them in order to obtain reasonable amounts of the rarer useful elements such as §5indium§r, §agermanium§r, and §2bismuth§r. The lead line unlocked in HV yields other elements such as selenium and tellurium.
susy.quest.db.1399178319.title=Fiber-Reinforced Epoxy
susy.quest.db.1399178319.desc=To produce fiber-reinforced epoxy, a special formulation of glass known as §4e-glass§r is interspersed with §bkevlar§r to produce high-strength glass fibers. Set this in fire-resistant epoxy made from brominated bisphenol A to obtain fiber-reinforced epoxy.
susy.quest.db.1402916517.title=High Voltage Regulator
susy.quest.db.1402916517.desc=Don't forget to make an §6MV Vacuum Ejector§r for this one.
susy.quest.db.1403511944.title=Gas Mask v3.0 (Lung Cancer Edition)
susy.quest.db.1403511944.desc=Your pitiful gas masks (if you made them) aren't going to save you in the incredibly hot §cNether§r. In fact, you're going to die ten times as fast without the proper §mPPE§r equipment.%n%nFortunately, thanks to §7Asbestos§r, everyone's §ofavorite§r ore, along with a little bit of §eMineral Wool§r, you can survive the journey! You're going to need to bring some §bAir§r with you, however. (Maybe use an air intake?)%n%nYou can find your favorite ore in a §aTalc§r vein on the surface crust.%n%nIf you're going exploring, consider making §dtwo§r Asbestos Tanks, so that you can swap them out without dying. You could also check out the §bExploration§r tab to see what upgrades you can apply to this!
susy.quest.db.1411082549.title=Fission Reactor
susy.quest.db.1411082549.desc=A fission reactor isn't all that complicated, really.%n%nWhenever a fuel rod is struck by a low-energy neutron (called a §6thermal neutron§r), it has a chance to absorb it and cause a fission event. This fission event, in the case of U-235 neutrons, emits three more higher-energy neutrons called §cfast neutrons§r, along with a large amount of heat.%n%nA fast neutron, unfortunately, does not interact with other fuel rods like thermal neutrons do. But, when a fast neutron reaches a §7moderator§r, such as §3distilled water§r, it loses some energy and converts into a thermal neutron! That water also absorbs heat, acting as a coolant for the reactor. As it heats up, it also turns into high-pressure steam, which turns a turbine and can then be turned back into energy.%n%nSo, in essence, the job of designing fission reactors comes down to putting water between as many fuel rod pairs as possible.%n%nThe rate of neutron generation can't be observed directly, but one can measure the exponential increase in neutron output known as §cK_eff§r, the effective multiplication factor. Over the lifetime of each neutron released (represented as "Avg. neutron" in JEI), the number of neutrons will roughly be multiplied by K_eff. If K_eff is greater than one, reactor power will increase over time; if it's less than one, it will decrease.%n%nOf course, keeping K_eff greater than one forever will eventually cause a §cmeltdown§r! Unless you like corium, the rate of fission must be controlled by §7control rods§r. As they are inserted, they block more neutrons from reaching their targets, helping to keep K_eff in check. Preferably, K_eff remains around one at peak power demand. Please make sure to test your reactors before leaving them on!%n%nThe fission reactor comes preinstalled with control software (the §eSmiley§r button in the corner). This software will control the insertion of the control rods depending on K_eff, attempting to keep the temperature, although it is not necessarily perfect. If you want any more power out of your reactors, you'll have to use §5OpenComputers§r!%n%nIn order to actually build a reactor, first select a size based on those seen in JEI's multiblock previews. Then, select spots in the internals of the reactor to place fuel rods, coolant channels, and control rods based on the internal geometry of the reactor. Each fuel rod and coolant channel require input and output hatches along with §6special container blocks to hold them the rest of the way§r, while control rods just need containers and a single control rod hatch to be placed next to the input hatches. Air may also be used on the inside.%n%nOnce it is built, place at least one fuel rod in each fuel rod hatch and fill up all of the coolant channels with the coolant you want. Then, §clock§r the reactor to begin! You will be unable to change the fuel rod type or the coolant type once it's locked.%n%nMore information is available in the JEI information page for the fission reactor.%n%nTip: the graphite-tipped control rods you see in JEI are not supported by Smiley, and are mostly meant to simulate Chernobyl, so don't use those unless you know what you're doing.
susy.quest.db.1417877385.title=Acetone
susy.quest.db.1417877385.desc=§7Acetone§r is an important solvent for a huge variety of processes. The most convenient way to produce it is via the distillation of §6wood vinegar§r.
susy.quest.db.1422303937.title=Gas Mask v4.0 (Shiny Version)
susy.quest.db.1422303937.desc=With the power of some intensely-sprayed §bAluminium§r dust onto your armor, it now reflects light at a much higher rate, preventing §cinfrared§r light from being absorbed. This allows your suit to resist heat damage for thrice as long! You just have to resist your teammates calling you "captain sparkles" in the mean time.%n%nAlso, if you upgraded to the §5Rebreather Tank§r, you can still turn that into the §bReflective Tank§r, although it will not continue to use lithium hydroxide. You can immediately move on to the next upgrade, however: the §dFiltered Tank§r!
susy.quest.db.1424901168.title=Making Goodyear Cry
susy.quest.db.1424901168.desc=At this point, you are set to start §dautomating§r certain materials you encounter. If you manage to get §aeight whole stacks§r of them, you may be entitled to one of these special trophies! You can check out the §eAutomation§r tab to see all of these.%n%nYou can immediately start on this by just connecting your source of latex to the coagulation tank and vulcanizing it, although maybe you could use one of the special §6catalysts§r to make this faster.%n%nYou know, Goodyear didn't even actually invent rubber vulcanization. He deserves it.
susy.quest.db.1427511961.title=Heat Exchanger
susy.quest.db.1427511961.desc=A §6heat exchanger §ris a device that transfers heat between two or more fluids, without them mixing.%n%nFor example, the Heat Exchanger can transfer heat between §chot§o§r compressed hydrogen and §bwater§r, to turn them into §cwarm water §rand §anormal-temperature compressed hydrogen§r§r.%n%nYou can cool down High Pressure Hydrogen into Cold High Pressure Hydrogen.%n%n§6The Heat Exchanger requires:%n- 1 Heat Exchanger Controller%n- 2 Output Hatch%n- 2 Input Hatch%n- 1 Maintenance Hatch%n- 20 Steel Frame Box%n- 56 Solid Steel Machine Casing%n- 8 Steel Pipe Casing
susy.quest.db.1458175841.title=Kovar
susy.quest.db.1458175841.desc=Kovar is an alloy of iron, nickel, and cobalt that has a very similar thermal expansion coefficient as glass, making it suitable for metal to glass bonds for vacuum tubes.%n%nMaking Kovar directly with §cCobalt Matte§r is §cinefficient§r. Later on, it is better to produce §7Kovar Dust§r first, then smelt it into ingots in the §6Electric Resistance Furnace§r.
susy.quest.db.1468576597.title=Indium
susy.quest.db.1468576597.desc=Stock up on §5indium§r as a byproduct from the zinc line as this will be an important material in semiconductors later!
susy.quest.db.1481636455.title=Ore Quadrupling
susy.quest.db.1481636455.desc=Using §amanganese steel§r, new crushing multiblocks can be made to further increase yields and speed from ores (hopefully sourced from automated mining drills!) First, the §9eccentric roll crusher§r is used to produce crushed ore from the raw ore. Next, feed the crushed ore into the §2ball mill§r to produce the dust very quickly. The §2ball mill§r requires preheated air to remove internal moisture released or introduced during operation and grinding balls, which lose durability during operation.
susy.quest.db.1520504426.title=Ethylene Glycol
susy.quest.db.1520504426.desc=§bEthylene glycol§r is an important chemical which is incorporated in coolants and is required as an intermediate for §9triethylene glycol§r, which is used to purify crude natural gas.
susy.quest.db.1529184698.title=Lubricating Oil
susy.quest.db.1529184698.desc=§6§lLubricating oil§r is a useful feedstock for lubricant production, derived from residue distillation. It can either be produced by directly hydrotreating the crude feedstock or dewaxed with §bMIBK§r and §1§3Butanone§r to improve yield. The slack wax can be turned into more lubricating oil, turned into resin, or produce treated wood.
susy.quest.db.1532373030.title=Panel and Panel Accessories
susy.quest.db.1532373030.desc=§6Control Panels§r are modular §3input§r/§2output§r devices. They have a 4x4 grid which can be fitted with §6Modules§r for performing Input/Output/Scaling operations. they can also be placed in any orientation, with the front of the panel facing towards the Player.%n%n§6Modules§r are placed on the panels grid and their §3Input§r/§2Output§r ports of installed modules are available on the back. You can §a[right-click] §rmost modules in air to alter their size. To remove modules from panels §a[left-click] §rwith a screwdriver in hand. (Won't work if screwdriver has module configuration copied, §a[sneak+right-click] §rto clear).
susy.quest.db.1556412238.title=Acetic Anhydride
susy.quest.db.1556412238.desc=Acetic anhydride is a strong acetylating reagent necessary for many organic syntheses. Its uses range from explosives to medicine to polymers. To produce it, oxidize acetaldehyde in ethyl acetate solution with a mixed §6copper§r-§9cobalt§r acetate catalyst and distill the product.
susy.quest.db.1561113894.title=Fischer-Tropsch
susy.quest.db.1561113894.desc=Too much syngas? Use the §cFischer-Tropsch synthesis§r to convert syngas into higher hydrocarbons and oxygenates to augment your fuel and petrochemicals production.%n%nThe low-temperature version is slower and produces a different product distribution than the high-temperature version, but does not require a fluidized bed reactor.
susy.quest.db.1564988135.title=Advanced Homogeneous Catalysis
susy.quest.db.1564988135.desc=Unlocking the remainder of the platinum group metals unlocks an array of processes which use PGM complexes as homogeneous (dissolved) catalysts. %n%nFor example, the Cativa (§bIr§r-catalyzed) and Monsanto (§dRh§r-catalyzed) processes can be used to make §3acetic acid§r from §6methanol§r and carbon monoxide while the Monsanto process can also produce acetic anhydride directly from §amethyl acetate§r and carbon monoxide.
susy.quest.db.1565439564.title=Pristine
susy.quest.db.1565439564.desc=Definitely build your floor out of blocks of this.
susy.quest.db.1571195686.title=Gathering Input
susy.quest.db.1571195686.desc=§6There are many §4Project Red§r circuits used to gather forms of input or data. These include%n%n- §6Light sensor§r: Outputs a redstone signal of strength corresponding to current light level.%n%n- §6Rain sensor§r: Outputs a redstone signal if rain is falling on it (must have access to the sky).%n%n- §6Timer§r: Emits a pulse at a specified interval.%n%n- §6Sequencer§r: Like the timer but has 4 outputs each of which are sent a pulse at a separate time.%n%n- §6Counter§r: Keeps an internal counter which can be increased or decreased with plus and minus inputs. When it reaches the max or min levels, the corresponding output will be §2ON§r. Settings can be changed by §b[sneak+right-click]§r.%n%n- §6Comparator§r: Works the same as a vanilla §6Comparator§r. but needs a §4Project Red§6 screwdriver§r to toggle modes.%n%n- §6Randomizer§r: Takes a redstone signal as input. While the input is §2ON§r, it will randomize the output; once the input is §cOFF§r, the randomly selected configuration will lock. Use a §4Project Red§6 screwdriver§r to enable/disable certain output sides.%n%n- §6Dec Randomizer§r: Works the same as the randomizer, but only 1 input will be §2ON§r at a given time.
susy.quest.db.1571792530.title=High Assay
susy.quest.db.1571792530.desc=HALEU is an enrichment grade that is intermediate between LEU and HEU. It is quite reactive; however, it is still reasonably controllable in a reactor.
susy.quest.db.1573249623.title=Kevlar
susy.quest.db.1573249623.desc=§bKevlar §ris a high strength polyaramid fiber used for the manufacturing of armor and reinforced epoxies. Produce it by copolymerizing terephthaloyl chloride, which can be obtained from §a§r§aterephthalic acid§r used for polyethylene terephthalate (PET), and p-phenylenediamine in dimethylacetamide.
susy.quest.db.1580653524.title=石头
susy.quest.db.1580653524.desc=在坑窑里烧制§7圆石§r就能获得对应的§7石头§r，你需要很多石头来合成§7砌砖§r。
susy.quest.db.1586872556.title=Place in the World fades away
susy.quest.db.1586872556.desc=What? Who put this here?%n%nYou don't even need this many! You will, even in the final version of this pack, probably need less than a dozen of these §oever§r!%n%nNo! STOP!
susy.quest.db.1602093300.title=可热™
susy.quest.db.1602093300.desc=§7焦煤§r是一种碳含量高的煤基燃料。主要用于炼§7铁§r，也可以作为§6简易冶炼炉§r的燃料。
susy.quest.db.1604101222.title=Polybenzimidazole
susy.quest.db.1604101222.desc=With fiber-spinning technology, you are now able to produce §8Polybenzimidazole§r (PBI), a flame-resistant polymer that is used in high-performance terrestrial and §bastronomical§r applications.%n%nThis would normally be seen as a major milestone in the other packs this polymer finds itself in, but by this point you're hopefully used to this.
susy.quest.db.1609925762.title=Glue
susy.quest.db.1609925762.desc=While not useful yet in the steam age, you can distill §cresin§r into §6glue§r, which can be used in useful components to make circuitry in the LV age once you obtain the assembler.
susy.quest.db.1610061980.title=夹板锤
susy.quest.db.1610061980.desc=§6夹板锤§r可以帮你挥动锤子！%n%n夹板锤需要§6齿轮§r和§6锤§r来工作。你最大可以放置§a4§r个到石砧的旁边来获取最高效率。%n%n可以用管道或漏斗将物品输入石砧，产物将直接掉落出来或输出到夹板锤旁边的存储设备（确保不是放了齿轮的那一侧）。
susy.quest.db.1617418058.title=Eco-friendly Petrochem? Nooooooooo!
susy.quest.db.1617418058.desc=By treating lipids with §9Hydrogen§r in the presence of certain catalysts, you can turn them into §7Alkanes§r, which are basically the main component of oil fractions. This gives you a way to turn those §eLipids§r into something equivalent to §7Oil Fractions§r: the §2Green Diesel§r chain.%n%nThe §2Green Diesel§r chain can produce §apropane§r §7(from glycerol)§r, §eNaphtha§r, §6Kerosene§r, and §cDiesel§r. The chain itself is quite straight-forward as shown below:%n§l1)§r First, decolorize the lipid with aluminium silicate with phosphoric acid as a catalyst.%n§l2)§r Heat the lipid up and react it with hydrogen in a trickle bed reactor.%n§l3)§r Separate the reaction outlet, and neutralize the acid produced in the reaction as a by-product.%n§l4)§r Distill over light-ends, which are mostly propane and naphtha.%n§l5)§r Isomerize the remaining paraffins and distill it again to separate kerosene and diesel.%n%nIntermediate products are listed on the right, check JEI for more info.%n%nYou can also see the whole flowchart of biodiesel chain here:{Embed}TypeLink;https://github.com/SymmetricDevs/QuestbookMedia/blob/main/flowcharts/hvo.png;128;20;§9§nGreen Diesel Chain§r{Embed}
susy.quest.db.1634463815.title=Nomex
susy.quest.db.1634463815.desc=With fiber-spinning technology, you are now able to produce Nomex, a flame-resistant polymer that is very useful for suit-making. Much of its setup is quite similar to that of Kevlar's.
susy.quest.db.1640585420.title=Steam Distillery and Batch Reactor
susy.quest.db.1640585420.desc=Looking to do some more advanced chemical automation in the steam age? Use these machines to make sulfuric acid quickly.
susy.quest.db.1646718435.title=Neodymium Magnets
susy.quest.db.1646718435.desc=Neodymium magnets are required for progression into the IV tier. They are produced from §7neodymium§r, §ciron§r, and §aboron§r. To protect the magnet from oxidation, they are coated with nickel using electroplating.
susy.quest.db.1676461834.title=Your First MV Battery? Already?
susy.quest.db.1676461834.desc=Although you might not have §6MV power§r yet, it is still possible for you to craft §6MV batteries§r. %n%nThis pattern continues in future voltage tiers, allowing you to craft batteries §6one tier ahead§r of your current one. %n%nFurthermore, starting in §6MV§r you will also be able to craft a better §6higher-capacity battery§r for the preceding tier.
susy.quest.db.1677924297.title=Better Oven
susy.quest.db.1677924297.desc=The §6Refractory Oven§r is an upgraded version of the §7Stone Oven§r, which has §a2.5x§r the processing speed and a lower chance of failure.
susy.quest.db.1703733058.title=Do Not Eat
susy.quest.db.1703733058.desc=but what if I want to eat the silica gel
susy.quest.db.1706791533.title=Activated Carbon
susy.quest.db.1706791533.desc=§8Activated carbon§r is a high-surface area form of carbon used for catalyst supports and various filtration and purification processes. It's high surface area allows it to absorb particles and chemical species from solution, like in water filtration and §6gold§r production. To produce it, simply roast carbon black with nitrogen.
susy.quest.db.1710745200.title=Negative Kelvin
susy.quest.db.1710745200.desc=512 is too easy if you get 8 wires at a time!
susy.quest.db.1733167550.title=Reverberatory Furnace
susy.quest.db.1733167550.desc=This specialized machine has a few applications in ferrous and copper metallurgy. It particularly helps in producing §6Wrought Iron§r more efficiently.%n%nMake sure to use primitive buses on this machine if you're doing this before §6steam§r tier.
susy.quest.db.1742975876.title=Induction Coil
susy.quest.db.1742975876.desc=The §6Induction Coil§r is the central component of an induction furnace. When electrical current flows through the coil, it creates an electromagnetic field that induces eddy currents in the metal charge, heating and eventually melting it. It surrounds the furnace crucible, with cooling water pumped through it continuously to avoid overheating. %n%nInduction coils are primarily made from hollow copper tubing formed into a helical coil. They are often coated with a ceramic layer to provide thermal and electrical insulation and wrapped in a flexible secondary insulating material that also mechanically reinforces it by absorbing vibration and thermal-expansion stresses.
susy.quest.db.1754821293.title=Rebreather Tank
susy.quest.db.1754821293.desc=Although JEI may initially seem to say otherwise, the §6Rebreather Tank§r is a significant upgrade to the asbestos version, given that it allows you to §ltriple§r your oxygen reserves! (Look at the recipes if you don't believe me.) %n%nIt uses §elithium hydroxide§r, which reacts with carbon dioxide to make lithium carbonate and oxygen. This allows you to sustain a constant supply of breathable air for §ojust§r as long as your suit will actually last you anyways.
susy.quest.db.1766162782.title=Extenders & Bridges
susy.quest.db.1766162782.desc=§3§6Bridges§r and §6extenders§r are §cdelegators§r; they can delegate one face of your §bmachine§r or §bpipes§r onto one or more equivalent faces.%n%nBoth bridges and extenders have four variants: §3inv§r, §3tank§r, §3invtank§r, and §5universal§r. As their names suggest, they allow automation of items, fluids, items plus fluids, and, for universal ones, energy as well. §oNone§r of them, however, can attach to other §cdelegators§r.%n%n§6Bridges§r will allow §bpipes§r or §bcables§r from different directions to pass through each other in one block without turning, which will be very useful for compact logistic designs.%n%n§6Extenders§r can expand one face on your §bmachine§r to five faces. An extender has three kinds of faces: §4primary§r, §4secondary§r, and §4normal§r faces. All import/extract actions on the §4normal§r or §4secondary§r faces will be delegated to the §bmachines§r or §bpipes§r adjacent to the §4primary§r face, and the actions on the §4primary§r face will be delegated to the §4secondary§r face.%n%nApart from the §5Universal Delegators§r that require aluminium, you can now craft all §cdelegators§r for your automation.
susy.quest.db.1767849062.title=切勿低估花岗岩的魅力
susy.quest.db.1767849062.desc=在地下挖矿时也许会经常遇见§d花岗岩§r，§d花岗岩§r是一种非常坚硬的§c火成岩§r，是一种合成§7研钵§r的非常理想的材料。所以别忽略它！
susy.quest.db.1773092756.title=Misc Modules
susy.quest.db.1773092756.desc=- §6Text Module§r: Simple text display. Can be resized between 1x1 to 1x4 with 4 lines of text each. 8 characters wide at 1x1 to 26 characters wide at 1x4. Can use Minecraft Formatting Codes for §dS§1P§2E§3C§4I§5A§6L §7F§9u§an§bk§cy §l§m§n§oText%n§r%n- §6Panel Signal Socket§r: Lets you pass a signal through a Control Panel. Direction can be set by aiming at a specific corner of the grid space. Place on bottom left of a grid space to put the §3input §ron the front of a panel, and top right to put the §2output§r on the front.
susy.quest.db.1786950658.title=Zener Diode
susy.quest.db.1786950658.desc=A special kind of diode that lets current flow backwards above a certain voltage, helping to stabilize power supplies. They're named after Clarence Zener, if you're wondering.
susy.quest.db.1796662362.title=Redstone Logic
susy.quest.db.1796662362.desc=Project Red Guide.
susy.quest.db.1807049983.title=Methanol To Gasoline
susy.quest.db.1807049983.desc=§6Methanol§r, which can be synthesized from syngas, can be converted to naphtha and other useful hydrocarbon gases using a ZSM-5 catalyst. This is a useful route for producing fuel fractions with lighter gases or residues.
susy.quest.db.1818221999.title=PGM Separation Mixtures
susy.quest.db.1818221999.desc=In order to separate the PGM concentrate into its components, a few extractants are required:%n- §6Dibutyl carbitol§r is required to remove gold%n- §9Di-n-hexyl sulfide§r is required to remove palladium%n- §eTributyl phosphate§r is required to remove iridium%n%nIn addition to this, be sure to have ammonium chloride automation!
susy.quest.db.1821654157.title=Project Red Wires
susy.quest.db.1821654157.desc=The main foundation for §4Project Red§r is the §6red alloy wire§r which act like vanilla redstone dust with a few differences:%n- They experience power loss at a much slower rate than redstone%n- Their placement is restricted a lot less%n%nThe insulated version can be crafted using §6red alloy cable§r instead of §6red alloy wire§r, and it comes with the benefit of being dyeable to help with circuit organization. Different coloured cables will not connect to each other, allowing for more compact circuits.
susy.quest.db.1837809262.title=Thermal Cracking
susy.quest.db.1837809262.desc=§cThermal cracking§r is a process that converts residues into lighter fractions using heat. It can be carried out in a roaster at lower efficiency and longer duration or in a cracker. There are three forms of this process: steam cracking, visbreaking, and coking.%n%n- Visbreaking is a milder form of thermal cracking which does not produce pure coke, but leaves behind a residue that can be used as a fuel oil blending component.%n%n- Coking is a severe form of thermal cracking that removes carbon from the fractions as coke, which can be used for metallurgy or as a fuel source.%n%n- Steam cracking is used mainly for lighter fractions to produce olefins (alkenes).
susy.quest.db.1853087488.title=Better Plates
susy.quest.db.1853087488.desc=By combining the §6circuit plates§r with a §6red alloy plate§r, you get a §6conductive plate§r. These are a more advanced plate used to make a variety of redstone components.%n%nAdditionally, §6circuit plates§r can be combined with §6redstone plates§r, §6red alloy bolts§r and §6red alloy plates/wires§r to make §6anodes§r, §6cathodes§r and §6wired plates§r respectively.
susy.quest.db.1856931279.title=Advanced Circuit Boards
susy.quest.db.1856931279.desc=Modern PCBs utilize a substrate made of fireproof glass fibers and epoxy resin known as §cFR-4§r. On this substrate, high purity copper is added and patterned with photolithography. Holes for through-hole devices are drilled in and plated using §6electroless copper plating§r followed by subsequent electroplating. This requires formaldehyde, palladium chloride, and copper sulfate. Next, a green §2soldermask§r is applied and cured with UV light, with residues washed off using an alkaline solution.
susy.quest.db.1867050010.title=You Aren't in the Stone Age Anymore
susy.quest.db.1867050010.desc=The §6Refractory Kiln§r and §6Refractory Oven§r are upgraded versions of the §7Stone Kiln§r and §7Stone Oven§r, with both having a §a2.5x§r processing speed and a lower chance of failure.
susy.quest.db.1878108637.title=填坑焚烧
susy.quest.db.1878108637.desc=进行填坑焚烧时，可将目标方块放入窑中，确保其四周均被不可燃方块覆盖，仅留一个方块的开口。点燃方块后迅速封口，待烟雾散尽即完成。%n%n合成柴堆并将其焚烧就可获得木炭。在柴堆下放置砌砖制作的石收集器就可以获取到木焦油。
susy.quest.db.1898866549.title=Framed Cables
susy.quest.db.1898866549.desc=By framing §6red alloy cables§r or §6insulated wires§r, they can now be stacked vertically on themselves without the need of a support block.
susy.quest.db.1902566957.title=Not Enough 纤维
susy.quest.db.1902566957.desc=§6晾干架§r可以把§a植物纤维§r变成§4干燥的植物纤维§r。如果打草掉落的不够，记得合成一些。%n%n§6晾干架§r在§e干燥的§r群系里速度更快，在§b湿润的§r群系里速度更慢。天气也会影响到效率。此外，如果把晾干架放在§c篝火§r旁边速度会变更快。
susy.quest.db.1905847691.title=Incinerator
susy.quest.db.1905847691.desc=The incinerator is a pretty simple machine: supply it with power and it will §cdelete any block §rinserted. %n%n§eNote: The GregTech incinerator requires 8 blocks of air above it or it won't work. %n%n§rAlternatively, you may use the incinerator from Engineer's Decor. This option does not require power to work, nor does it delete your items right away. It holds 14 stacks of items §ebefore §rthey get deleted. However, it is quite a bit slower and may not keep up with a large throughput. Choose for yourself.
susy.quest.db.1906842139.title=Thinking Rocks
susy.quest.db.1906842139.desc=Your first steps into the §2Information Age§r begin by unlocking modern integrated circuit fabrication. The huge variety of resources required to produce chips will be a test of your automation capability!
susy.quest.db.1913677484.title=Cellulose Acetate Membrane
susy.quest.db.1913677484.desc=§eCellulose acetate§r membranes are the first kind of reverse osmosis membrane used to purify water. To produce §ecellulose acetate§r, first source cellulose from cotton or from autoclaving wood in white liquor (sodium sulfide/hydroxide solution). The raw cellulose must next be washed then acetylated with acetic anhydride and §csulfuric acid§r. The §ecellulose acetate§r can then be removed from solution by washing with water and some acetic acid.%n%nTo produce the membrane, the §ecellulose acetate §rmust first be dissolved in acetone with a pore former such as polyethylene glycol, then precipitated out with water in a process known as phase inversion. This produces a porous structure fit for reverse osmosis.
susy.quest.db.1920511558.title=HEI自动合成
susy.quest.db.1920511558.desc=在这趟旅行中，你会遇到§4越来越复杂的§f配方。%n这时候§bHEI自动合成§f就派上用场了。%n§6%n如何使用？§f%n按§6§bR §f打开物品的一个特定配方。§b你也可以直接把配方加入书签§f或者将其加入偏好配方§f来让HEI处理自动合成链。将配方加入书签，你就能在左边看到一个§a绿色§f括号。%n%n加入书签之后，你可以§bCTRL§f和使用§b滚轮§f要合成的物品数量。%n%n也可以用§bCTRL+左键§f为主配方里的物品添加一个附加配方书签，然后拖动配方到括号里（作为偏好配方的替代）。%n%n最后，如果你已经准备好所有原料和工具，只需要对绿色括号按§bSHIFT + C§f就可以开始合成。物品会在你的背包里开始合成。§8%n%n目前该功能只能在原版工作台上使用，但确实是合成站的一个替代方案。
susy.quest.db.1923587932.title=Rare Earth Separation Mixtures
susy.quest.db.1923587932.desc=The separation of the rare earths requires many liquid-liquid extractants. In the EV age, only two are required:%n%n- §6P204§r (or di(2-ethylhexyl)phosphoric acid), which is used for the initial coarse separation of the LREEs.%n- §6P507§r (or 2-ethylhexylphosphonic acid mono 2-ethylhexyl ester), which is used for the separation of MREEs from the HREEs and the separation of gadolinium and samarium.%n- §6TBP§r, which is used for the separation of cerium from the other rare earths.%n%nBe sure to have the proper petrochemicals required! A little §5iodine§r is also needed.%nThese separation mixtures are §bsaponified§r via the addition of sodium hydroxide to improve separation, however, when extracts loaded with rare earths are stripped of their REE content with acid, this process is reversed. Thus, sodium hydroxide will need to be continuously readded to these mixtures.%n%nIt is recommended to produce a decent quantity of these mixtures as the recipes require a sizable amount of extraction mixtures, and machines need to be constantly stocked with these mixtures for maximum efficiency.
susy.quest.db.1934888714.title=Commando Gear
susy.quest.db.1934888714.desc=You can craft the Commando Gear using UHMWPE and some Boron Nitride, it makes you mine faster underwater and gives you a speed boost, knockback resistance, and fall damage reduction.
susy.quest.db.1950025834.title=Logic & Arithmetic Gates
susy.quest.db.1950025834.desc=Arithmetic Gates:%n%n- §6Analog Signal Combiner§r: Outputs the highest §3Input§r signal, respecting signed numbers.%n%n- §6Arithmetic Signal Combiner§r: Adds all §3Input§r signals, each §3Input§r can be set to subtract from the total instead.%n%n%nLogic Gates:%n%n- §6XOR-Gate§r: Performs the exclusive-OR operation between inputs. Each input can be set to x>0 and bit-wise mode. in x>0 mode the entire input is considered either true or false, in bit-wise mode the operation is performed between each bit of the input.%n%n- §6Logic Signal Combiner§r: Performs the OR operation between §3Input§r inputs. Both §2outputs§r and §3inputs§r can be inverted to get any logic operation. Each §3Input§r can be set to x>0 and bit-wise mode.%n(for basic gates, Invert inputs for NAND, Output for NOR and Input+Output for AND, leaving unused inputs uninverted)%n%n§8(Specifically, the gate always runs in bit-wise mode, but In x>0 and x<=0 modes, when the condition on the input is met, the actual input to the gate is set to 65535, and 0 otherwise, so it's possible to combine with bit-wise operations, e.g. Decimal value going in a bit-wise inverted port + Lever connected to a  X <= 0 port, with output in NOR mode, to only let the decimal value to the output when the lever is toggled, otherwise output 0)
susy.quest.db.1955643643.title=Basic Gates
susy.quest.db.1955643643.desc=Each of these logic gates plays a different role in making complex redstone circuits. Here are all of their functionalities:%n%n§6OR gate§r Outputs §2ON§r if at least one of the input sides are §2ON§r%n%n§6AND gate§r: Outputs §2ON§r if all of the input sides are §2ON§r%n%n§6NOT gate§r: Outputs the opposite of the input signal%n%n§6NOR gate§r: Outputs §2ON§r if all inputs are §cOFF§r%n%n§6NAND gate§r: Outputs §cOFF§r if all inputs are §2ON§r%n%n§6XOR gate§r: Outputs §2ON§r if inputs are different (one §2ON§r and one §cOFF§r)%n%n§6XNOR gate§r: Outputs §2ON§r if inputs are the same (both §2ON§r or both §cOFF§r)
susy.quest.db.1958019111.title=砌砖
susy.quest.db.1958019111.desc=§7砌砖§r本质上是一种砖型的石头，可以用来做砖块或隔热材料，例如§6窑§r，§6炉§r和§6简易冶炼炉§r，或者单纯用于建筑方块。%n%n要获取一些§7砌砖§r，只需在石砧上破碎石头。
susy.quest.db.1962935316.title=Cerium
susy.quest.db.1962935316.desc=Cerium will be important for the production of highly resistant crucibles for the production of §anuclear weapons§r.
susy.quest.db.1973878836.title=Rare Earth Coarse Separation
susy.quest.db.1973878836.desc=The first step to separating the rare earths is the removal of §acerium§r, which is possible as it has a 4+ oxidation state. By roasting the hydroxides under oxygen, cerium hydroxide is converted to cerium IV oxide. The mixture is then dissolved in nitric acid and §acerium§r is separated using §6TBP§r.%n%nThe next step is to separate the LREEs, which is done by extracting the MREEs and HREEs using §6P204§r. The HREEs are subsequently extracted from the MREEs using §6P507§r. While unusable now, be sure to stockpile the HREEs for the IV age!
susy.quest.db.1994804951.title=2nd Grade Lipids
susy.quest.db.1994804951.desc=§4§6Lipids from animals§r contains a high amount of §cfatty acids§r in them, which is §4harmful§r to the §3transesterification§r process. Thus to use them for §6biodiesel§r production, it is essential to reduce the §cfatty acids§r content in them.%n%nFor above reasons, the following lipids are considered 2nd grade lipids:%n - Liquid Fat (Stearin)%n - Fish Oil%n%nCheck the next quest for available §3pretreatment§r methods.
susy.quest.db.1996974870.title=Transesterification Reaction
susy.quest.db.1996974870.desc=§6Bio Diesel§r, also known as Fatty Acid Methanol Ester §c(FAME)§r or Fatty Acid Ethanol Ester §c(FAEE)§r, is produced by the §3transesterification§r reaction between §6lipids§r and corresponding §ealcohols§r in a §6batch reactor§r.%n%nYou can use either methanol or ethanol for this, depending on your existing production lines (if you don't have either yet, I would recommend that you use ethanol from farming, since it needs very little power).
susy.quest.db.1997511526.title=Natural Gas
susy.quest.db.1997511526.desc=§7Natural gas§r can be extracted from fluid veins in the Overworld. To use them in combustion engines, they must first be purified via dehydration with §9triethylene glycol§r followed by desulfurization in §bethanolamine§r, then liquefied using a standard refrigeration loop.
susy.quest.db.1998778304.title=Air Vent
susy.quest.db.1998778304.desc=§cAir Vent§r, when placed on a machine or a drum, can collect surrounding §7Air§r into it, if it's not blocked by other block.%n%nAs a Cover, it can be removed with a §bCrowbar§r.
susy.quest.db.1999167293.title=IR Transformers
susy.quest.db.1999167293.desc=You can use Industrial Renewal's Ultra-HV transformers to economically transfer energy over long distances.
susy.quest.db.2003682896.title=MV Extruder
susy.quest.db.2003682896.desc=The §6MV extruder§r unlocks metal forming and shaping operations which can be used to reduce the cost for various shaped components such as rotors and screws.
susy.quest.db.2008568067.title=Platinum Group Concentration
susy.quest.db.2008568067.desc=To produce the §bplatinum group metals§r, §6pentlandite§r must first be processed into a matte and enriched into a PGM concentrate. This concentrate is subsequently separated into the platinum group metals using a variety of redox reactions and liquid-liquid extractions. %n%nIn addition to PGM concentrate and nickel, you can also extract some §6copper§r, §9cobalt§ §r, §2nickel§r, §bselenium§r and §atellurium§r.
susy.quest.db.2028966995.title=Tier 1 Armor Upgrades
susy.quest.db.2028966995.desc=The first level of armor upgrades are made from steel.
susy.quest.db.2039298687.title=And They Just Keep Coming
susy.quest.db.2039298687.desc=And they don't stop coming.
susy.quest.db.2053239479.title=Redstone Control 101
susy.quest.db.2053239479.desc=Redstone control is a versatile mod with functionality beyond standard redstone or ProjectRed.%n%nDevices are connected through Ports instead of block to block interactions, §2Read §rfor outputs and §3Write §rfor inputs. Ports are wired together using §cSignal Wire§r, with a max range of 16 blocks (Measured from centre of the block, Radially). §a[left-click]§r with a screwdriver to remove connection, §a[sneak+right-click]§r in air to cancel placing connection.%n%n§2Redstone Read Socket §rcan be placed on a block to read the redstone its redstone value, outputting it to the §2Read §rport.%n%n§3Redstone Write Socket §rcan be placed on blocks to send a redstone signal from its §3Write§r port into the block it's attached to.%n%nThe two Sockets can now be connected with §cSignal Wire§r for an easy + lossless redstone connection.%n%nSignal Sockets can also be placed inside blocks while placed in offhand and empty main hand.%n%n§8While vanilla redstone uses signals of 4-bit integers, signals in Redstone Control are transmitted as signed 32-bit integers, with range of -2,147,483,638 to 2,147,483,647. In terms of interaction between Write Sockets and other redstone inputs, e.g. Lamps/Machine Controller Covers/ProjectRed Gates, any >0 signal strength works as a positive signal, including signals outside the standard 1-15 range.
susy.quest.db.2076838302.title=Furfural
susy.quest.db.2076838302.desc=§1Furfural§r is an organic compound which can be used to separate BTEX. It is formed from the acid-catalyzed dehydration of pentoses in lignocellulose, which is the primary building block of wood. By treating wood dust with sulfuric acid, you can produce this chemical.
susy.quest.db.2081939483.title=红砖
susy.quest.db.2081939483.desc=用§6木制砖模具§r来压缩§3粘土球§r就能获得§3压缩粘土§r，再放入坑窑里烧制获得§4红砖§r。
susy.quest.db.2096017803.title=Fuel Feedstocks
susy.quest.db.2096017803.desc=There are a variety of petrochemical productions that can be blended into gasoline. Below is an overview:%n%n- §e§e§6Naphtha §rand §eLight Naphtha§r, produced directly from the distillation of oil can be used at a low efficiency.%n- §6§cReformate§r and §cReformate Raffinate §rare produced by reforming heavy naphtha into aromatics. These are high performance and have high gasoline yields. Raffinate produces less gasoline, but allows for the extraction of BTEX for petrochemicals.%n- §aPolymerate §rcan be produced from catalytic cracking byproducts in a simple process, with a medium yield.%n- §4Isomerate§r is produced from light na§6§rphtha and a small quantity of hydrogen. This is a high performance feedstock with high yields.%n- §6Alkylate§r is produced from catalytic cracking byproducts, isobutane, and hydrofluoric acid in a slightly more complex process than polymerate. It has a higher performance and thus yields more gasoline, however.%n- §6Pyrolysis Gasoline §rand §6Pyrolysis Raffinate §rare byproducts of steam cracking and yield relatively low amounts of gasoline. Raffinate allows for the production of BTEX, similar to reformate.%n%nDiesel can be produced from Light Gas Oil (LGO) and Light Cycle Oil (LCO), however light cycle oil typically lowers performance and can only be added in small amounts. As such, LCO is better used with hydrocracking to produce BTEX.%n%nFuel oils are heavier, energy dense fuels that are produced from heavier fractions and residues. These are best used for off-site power generation and marine applications due to the low yields of residua from oils and their high density, allowing for ease of transport.
susy.quest.db.2097328808.title=Acetaldehyde
susy.quest.db.2097328808.desc=Acetaldehyde can be manufactured from a variety of feedstocks including §9acetylene§r, ethylene, and §cethanol§r.%n%nTo produce acetaldehyde from §9acetylene§r, a HgCl2 solution catalyzes the hydration of §9acetylene§r to acetaldehyde. To produce from ethylene, a palladium chloride solution catalyzes the oxidation of ethylene in the Wacker process. To produce from §cethanol§r, you can either choose to dehydrogenate it over a copper catalyst (more energy intensive) or oxidize it over a silver catalyst bed and distill water out.
susy.quest.db.2110846801.title=Large Combustion Engine
susy.quest.db.2110846801.desc=This relatively large multiblock is the preferred way of generating electricity through late MV. It eventually produces up to 16A §eHV§r power.%n%nA variety of fuels, including §6Bio Diesel, Natural Gas and Gasoline§r, may be used.%n%nAt this point, you should know how to use JEI to construct the multiblock.
susy.quest.db.2114289290.title=Gas Mask v5.0 (OP Version)
susy.quest.db.2114289290.desc=The zenith of all terrestrial armors. Using the power of heat-resistant fibers like §5Nomex§r and §8Polybenzimidazole§r and an active cooling system made from §9Polyethylene Vinyl Acetate§r piping, you are now able to live §einfinitely§r in three dimensions! Woohoo!%n%nI mean, even though the materials you need for this are very expensive, you §owill§r need them soon enough. This is also a decently strong armor set for combat as well.
susy.quest.db.2127123573.title=Proliferation
susy.quest.db.2127123573.desc=At last, we reach 90%% U-235 enrichment. This is the enrichment required to obtain a §4critical mass§r needed for a nuclear weapon.%n%n§4§l§nWelcome to MAD.
susy.quest.db.2127737218.title=Lithium
susy.quest.db.2127737218.desc=There are a variety of methods to obtain §7lithium§r:%n- §cSpodumene§r%n- §dLepidolite§r%nWhen derived from lepidolite, §9caesium§r and §4rubidium§r can also be separated from lithium. Whichever ore you source lithium from, lithium carbonate is the main final product, which is useful for batteries and as a sneaky additive into food. Other lithium compounds and lithium metal can be used for graphene or organic syntheses such as for synthetic rubber or polybenzimidazole.
